webpackJsonp([35],{272:function(e,t){e.exports=[{id:115009772648,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115009772648-What-is-a-paper-key-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115009772648-What-is-a-paper-key-",author_id:23725737767,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!0,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-06-29T18:44:45Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T21:44:21Z",name:"What is a paper key?",title:"What is a paper key?",body:"<p>A paper key consists of 12 randomly generated words. The app creates the paper key for you automatically when you start a new wallet. The paper key is critically important and should be written down and stored in a safe location. In the event of phone theft, destruction, or loss, the paper key can be used to load your wallet onto a new phone. The key is also required when upgrading your current phone to a new one. </p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:paper-key"],locales:{"zh-cn":{id:115002804093,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"什么是纸钥匙？",body:"<p>一个纸钥匙包含 12 个随机生成的词。此应用会在您新建钱包时自动为您创建纸钥匙。纸钥匙非常重要，应当记下来并妥善保管。如果手机失窃、损坏或丢失，可使用纸钥匙将您的钱包载入新手机。当前手机升级更新后也需要用到纸钥匙。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:33Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:50Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-tw":{id:115002804113,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"什麼是紙金鑰？",body:"<p>一個紙金鑰由 12 個隨機生成的單字組成。當你創建一個新錢包時，app 會自動為你生成一組紙金鑰。紙金鑰非常重要，請把它寫下並存放在安全的地方。當手機被偷、損壞或遺失時，紙金鑰可以將你的錢包載入新手機中。當升級至新手機時也需要使用到此金鑰。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:33Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:51Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002804053,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Wat is een papiersleutel?",body:"<p>Een Papiersleutel bevat 12 willekeurig gekozen woorden. De app maakt automatisch de Papiersleutel voor jou wanneer je een nieuwe portemonnee start. De Papiersleutel is erg belangrijk en moet opgeschreven worden en bewaard worden op een veilige plek. Als je telefoon gestolen, vernietigd of verloren raakt, kan de Papiersleutel gebruikt worden om je portemonnee op een nieuwe telefoon te herstellen. De sleutel is ook nodig wanneer je je huidige telefoon upgradet naar een nieuwe.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:32Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:49Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002804073,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Что такое бумажный ключ?",body:"<p>Бумажный ключ состоит из 12-ти случайных слов. Приложение автоматически создает для вас бумажный ключ после создания нового кошелька. Этот ключ крайне важен, поэтому его нужно записать и хранить в надежном месте. В случает кражи, выхода из строя или потери телефона бумажный ключ можно использовать для загрузки вашего кошелька на новый телефон. Ключ также необходим, если вы хотите начать использовать новый телефон вместо текущего. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:32Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:50Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002792374,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"O que é uma chave de papel?",body:"<p>Uma chave de papel consiste em 12 palavras geradas aleatoriamente. A aplicação cria a chave de papel para si automaticamente quando cria uma nova carteira. A chave de papel é de extrema importância e deve ser anotada e guardada num local seguro. Em caso de roubo, destruição ou perda do telemóvel, a chave de papel pode ser usada para carregar a sua carteira para um telemóvel novo. A chave também é necessária quando troca de telemóvel.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:32Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:50Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002792394,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Vad är en pappersnyckel?",body:"<p>En pappersnyckel består av 12 slumpmässigt genererade ord. Appen skapar automatiskt pappersnyckeln åt dig när du startar en ny plånbok. Pappersnyckeln är ytterst viktig och bör skrivas ner och lagras på ett säkert ställe. I händelse av att telefon stjäls, förstörs eller förloras kan pappersnyckeln användas för att ladda din plånbok på en ny telefon. Nyckeln är också nödvändig när du uppgraderar din nuvarande telefon till en ny.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:32Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:50Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002803993,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Qué es una clave de papel?",body:"<p>Una clave de papel consiste en 12 palabras generadas al azar. La aplicación crea la clave de papel automáticamente cuando creas un nuevo monedero. La clave de papel es muy importante y debe apuntarse y almacenarse en un lugar seguro. En caso de robo, destrucción o pérdida del teléfono, la clave de papel se puede utilizar para cargar tu monedero en un teléfono nuevo. La clave también se requiere al cambiar y actualizar tu teléfono.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:31Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:48Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002804013,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Qu'est-ce qu'une clé papier ?",body:"<p>Une clé papier se compose de 12 mots générés aléatoirement. L'appli crée automatiquement la clé papier pour vous lorsque vous créez un nouveau portefeuille. La clé papier est extrêmement importante et doit être écrite et conservée dans un endroit sûr. En cas de vol, de destruction ou de perte du téléphone, la clé papier peut être utilisée pour charger votre portefeuille sur un nouveau téléphone. La clé vous sera aussi demandée si vous remplacez votre téléphone actuel par un nouveau téléphone. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:31Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:49Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002804033,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ペーパーキーとは?",body:"<p>ペーパーキーはランダムに生成された12単語により形成されるキーです。ペーパーキーは新しいウォレットをスタートさせた時に、自動的にアプリにより作成されます。ペーパーキーは非常に重要ですので、キーは書き留めて安全な場所に保管しておいてください。携帯電話が紛失、破損または盗難されてしまった場合には、ペーパーキーを使用して新しい携帯電話であなたのウォレットを取り込むことができます。お手持ちの携帯電話を新しい機種にアップデートする際にも、ペーパーキーが必要となります。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:31Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:49Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002792354,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Cos'è una chiave cartacea?",body:"<p>Una chiave cartacea contiene 12 parole generate a caso. Quando crei un nuovo portafoglio, l'app genera in automatico una chiave cartacea. Questa chiave è importantissima e dovresti scriverla su un foglio da conservare in un posto sicuro. Se il tuo telefono venisse rubato, fosse smarrito o si rompesse, potrai usare la chiave cartacea per ripristinare il tuo portafoglio su un nuovo telefono. La chiave sarà necessaria anche nel caso in cui decidessi di cambiare telefono. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:31Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:49Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002792314,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvad er en papirnøgle?",body:"<p> En papirnøgle består af 12 tilfældigt genererede ord. Appen opretter automatisk papirnøglen for dig, når du opretter en ny tegnebog. Papirnøglen er kritisk vigtig og skal skrives ned og opbevares et sikkert sted. I tilfælde af telefontyveri, ødelæggelse eller tab, kan papirnøglen bruges til at indlæse din tegnebog på en ny telefon. Nøglen er også nødvendig, når du opgraderer din nuværende telefon til en ny.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:30Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:48Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002792334,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Was ist ein Paper Key?",body:"<p>Ein Paper Key besteht aus 12 zufällig generierten Wörtern. Die App generiert den Paper Key automatisch für Sie, wenn Sie eine neue Geldbörse erstellen. Der Paper Key ist von bedeutender Wichtigkeit und sollte aufgeschrieben und an einem sicheren Ort verwahrt werden. Falls Ihr Handy gestohlen oder zerstört wird oder Sie es verlieren, kann der der Paper Key dazu verwendet werden, Ihre Geldbörse auf ein neues Handy zu laden. Der Key ist außerdem erforderlich, wenn Sie Ihr aktuelles Handy durch ein neueres ersetzen. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:30Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:48Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115016608208,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009772648/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115009772648",source_id:115009772648,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"What is a paper key?",body:"<p>A paper key consists of 12 randomly generated words. The app creates the paper key for you automatically when you start a new wallet. The paper key is critically important and should be written down and stored in a safe location. In the event of phone theft, destruction, or loss, the paper key can be used to load your wallet onto a new phone. The key is also required when upgrading your current phone to a new one. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-06-29T18:44:45Z",updated_at:"2017-07-21T00:12:59Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:23725737767}}},{id:115000526148,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000526148-Why-did-my-bitcoin-address-change-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000526148-Why-did-my-bitcoin-address-change-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!0,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977707,created_at:"2016-12-27T02:16:40Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T21:43:43Z",name:"Why did my bitcoin address change?",title:"Why did my bitcoin address change?",body:"<p>Whenever you receive a payment to the address shown, a new address is automatically generated for you. By using a unique address for every transaction, you can increase privacy and security. Old addresses will still continue to work, even if they are no longer displayed in your app.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:[],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002792734,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"為何我的比特幣位址改變了？",body:"<p>每當你要收款至顯示位址時，都會為你自動生成一個新位址。在每個交易中使用獨特位址將增加隱私及安全性。舊的位址還是可持續使用，就算它們已不再顯示於你的 app 中。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:42Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:59Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002792714,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Varför ändrades min bitcoin-adress?",body:"<p>När du får en betalning till den visade adressen genereras en ny adress automatiskt för dig. Genom att använda en unik adress för varje transaktion kan du öka integriteten och säkerheten. Gamla adresser fortsätter att fungera, även om de inte längre visas i din app.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:41Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:58Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002804493,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我的比特币地址为什么会变化？",body:"<p>每当您收款至您出示的地址，系统就会为您自动生成一个新地址。通过为每笔交易配用一个唯一地址，您可以加强隐私和安全。旧地址虽然不再显示于您的应用中，但依然有效。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:41Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:58Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002792694,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Porque é que o meu endereço de bitcoin mudou?",body:"<p>Sempre que recebe um pagamento no endereço mostrado, é automaticamente gerado um novo endereço para si. Ao usar um endereço único para cada transação, pode aumentar a sua privacidade e segurança. Os endereços antigos continuarão a funcionar, mesmo que já não sejam exibidos na sua aplicação.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:41Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:58Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002804473,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Почему мой биткоин-адрес изменился?",body:"<p>Каждый раз, когда вы получаете оплату на показанный адрес, для вас автоматически создается новый адрес. Использование уникального адреса для каждой транзакции помогает повысить конфиденциальность и безопасность. Старые адреса продолжат работать – даже если они больше не отображаются в приложении.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:41Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:58Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002804413,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Pourquoi mon adresse bitcoin a-t-elle été modifiée ?",body:"<p>À chaque fois que vous recevez un paiement à l'adresse affichée, une nouvelle adresse est générée automatiquement pour vous. En utilisant une adresse unique pour chaque transaction, vous pouvez augmenter la confidentialité et la sécurité. Les anciennes adresses fonctionneront toujours, même si elles ne s'affichent plus dans votre appli.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:40Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:57Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002804433,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Perché il mio indirizzo bitcoin è cambiato?",body:"<p>Ogni volta che riceverai un pagamento presso l'indirizzo mostrato, verrà generato in automatico un nuovo indirizzo personale. Usando un indirizzo univoco per ogni transazione si migliora la privacy e la sicurezza del processo. Gli indirizzi precedenti continueranno a funzionare, anche se non verranno più mostrati nella tua app.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:40Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:57Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002792674,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"私のビットコインアドレスが変わったのはなぜでしょう?",body:"<p>表示されたアドレスから支払いを受領した際には、毎回新しいアドレスが自動的に生成されます。各取引ごとにユニークなアドレスを使用することにより、プライバシーとセキュリティがより強固になります。アプリ内には表示されなくなりますが、古いアドレスも継続して利用することは可能です。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:40Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:57Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002804453,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Waarom is mijn bitcoin-adres veranderd?",body:"<p>Wanneer je een betaling ontvangt op het weergegeven adres, wordt er automatisch een nieuw adres voor jou gemaakt. Doordat er voor elke transactie een uniek adres gebruikt wordt, worden privacy en beveiliging vergroot. Oude adressen blijven werken, zelfs wanneer ze niet langer worden weergegeven in je app.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:40Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:57Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002804393,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Warum hat sich meine Bitcoin-Adresse geändert?",body:"<p>Wann immer Sie eine Zahlung an die angezeigte Adresse erhalten, wird automatisch eine neue Adresse für Sie generiert. Durch die Benutzung einer einzigartigen Adresse für jede Transaktion können Sie die Privatsphäre und Sicherheit verbessern. Alte Adressen funktionieren weiterhin, auch wenn Sie in Ihrer App nicht mehr angezeigt werden.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:39Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:56Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002792634,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvorfor ændrede min bitcoin-adresse sig?",body:"<p> Når du modtager en betaling til den viste adresse, genereres en ny adresse automatisk for dig. Ved at bruge en unik adresse for hver transaktion øges privatlivet og sikkerheden. Gamle adresser vil fortsat fungere, selvom de ikke længere vises i din app.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:39Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:56Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002792654,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Por qué cambió mi dirección de Bitcoin?",body:"<p> Siempre que recibas un pago a la dirección mostrada, se generará automáticamente una nueva dirección para ti. Al utilizar una dirección única para cada transacción se puede aumentar la privacidad y la seguridad. Las direcciones antiguas seguirán funcionando, aunque ya no se muestren en tu aplicación.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:39Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:57Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115000841068,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000526148/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000526148",source_id:115000526148,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"Why did my bitcoin address change?",body:"<p>Whenever you receive a payment to the address shown, a new address is automatically generated for you. By using a unique address for every transaction, you can increase privacy and security. Old addresses will still continue to work, even if they are no longer displayed in your app.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-12-27T02:16:40Z",updated_at:"2017-04-08T17:41:11Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000763394,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000763394-How-do-I-receive-bitcoin-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763394-How-do-I-receive-bitcoin-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!0,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977707,created_at:"2017-07-21T18:53:13Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T21:43:05Z",name:"How do I receive bitcoin?",title:"How do I receive bitcoin?",body:'<p>If you would like to receive bitcoin from someone, you will need to give them your bitcoin address. There are a few ways to do this:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Show them the "Receive Money" screen in your Bread app, and let them scan your QR code.</li>\n<li>Press the "Share" button under the QR code to send them your address via email or text message.</li>\n<li>Tap the QR code to copy your address to your device\'s memory. You can now paste your address into a website or other app.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The bitcoin address shown on your receive address will change every time you receive money, but old addresses will continue to work.</p>\n<p><strong>Important: </strong>If bitcoin is sent to the wrong address, it can not be refunded. When sharing your address, always check to make sure the address you give out is the same as the one shown under your QR code (comparing the first 5 or 6 digits is usually sufficient to make sure you are using the correct address).</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:receive-bitcoin"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002803153,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何收到比特幣？",body:"<p>如果你想要由其他人那邊收到比特幣，你需要給他們你的比特幣位址。有幾種做法：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>給他們看你 Bread app 中的「收款」畫面，並讓他們掃描你的 QR 碼。</li>\n<li>點擊 QR 碼下方的「分享」鍵經由郵件或簡訊將你的位址傳給他們。</li>\n<li>點擊 QR 碼來複製你的位址至裝置記憶體中。現在你可以在網站或其他 app 中貼上位址。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>你收款位址上顯現的比特幣位址在每次收款時都會改變，但舊位址會持續有效。</p>\n<p><strong>重要：</strong>如果比特幣送至錯誤的位址，將無法退款。當分享你的位址時，一定要檢查給出的位址和 QR 碼下的一模一樣（比對前 5 或 6 碼通常就得以確認你正使用正確的位址）。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:09Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:29Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002803113,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como recebo bitcoin?",body:'<p>Se quiser receber bitcoin de alguém, tem de lhes dar o seu endereço de bitcoin. Existem algumas formas de fazer isto:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Mostre-lhes o ecrã "Receber Dinheiro" na sua aplicação do Bread e deixe-os ler o seu código QR.</li>\n<li>Pressione o botão "Partilhar" debaixo do código QR para enviar-lhes os seu endereço por e-mail ou SMS.</li>\n<li>Toque no código QR para copiar o seu endereço para a memória do seu dispositivo. Pode agora colar o seu endereço num website ou noutra aplicação.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>O endereço de bitcoin mostrado como endereço de recepção irá mudar sempre que receber dinheiro, mas os endereços antigos continuarão a funcionar.</p>\n<p><strong>Importante: </strong>Se for enviado bitcoin para o endereço errado, não poderá ser reembolsado. Ao partilhar o seu endereço, confirme sempre se o que dá é o mesmo que é mostrado debaixo do seu código QR (normalmente basta comparar os primeiros 5 ou 6 dígitos para garantir que está a usar o endereço correto).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:08Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:28Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002803133,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как я могут получить биткоины?",body:"<p>Если вы хотите получить от кого-то биткоины, то вам нужно передать свой биткоин-адрес. Есть несколько способов сделать это:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Покажите этому человеку свой экран «Получить деньги» в приложении Bread и дайте ему отсканировать свой QR-код.</li>\n<li>Нажмите кнопку «Поделиться» под QR-кодом, чтобы отправить свой адрес по эл. почте или СМС.</li>\n<li>Нажмите на QR-код, чтобы скопировать адрес в буфер обмена. Теперь вы можете вставить свой адрес на сайт или в другое приложение.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>При каждом получении денег биткоин-адрес, отображаемый на этой странице, будет меняться, но старые адреса продолжат действовать.</p>\n<p><strong>Важно: </strong>если биткоины были отправлены на неправильный адрес, то их нельзя будет вернуть. Когда вы делитесь своим адресом, всегда проверяйте, совпадает ли он с адресом, который показан под вашим QR-кодом (обычно достаточно сравнить первые 5 или 6 символов, чтобы убедиться, что адрес верный).</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:08Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:28Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002791374,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe ontvang ik bitcoin?",body:'<p>Als je bitcoin wilt ontvangen van iemand anders, moet je je bitcoin-adres geven. Hier zijn een paar mogelijkheden voor:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Laat hen het "Geld ontvangen" scherm zien in je Bread-app, en laat ze jouw QR-code scannen.</li>\n<li>Druk op de "Delen" knop onder de QR-code om hen je adres via e-mail of sms te sturen.</li>\n<li>Klik op de QR-code om je adres te kopiëren naar de opslag van je apparaat. Je kunt je adres nu plakken in een website of andere app.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Het bitcoin-adres wat getoond is op je ontvangst-adres zal elke keer dat je geld ontvangt veranderen, maar oude adressen zullen blijven werken.</p>\n<p><strong>Belangrijk: </strong>Als bitcoin naar het verkeerde adres is gestuurd, kan er geen vergoeding gegeven worden. Wanneer je je adres deelt, zorg er dan voor dat je hetzelfde adres geeft als wat onder de QR-code staat (het vergelijken van de eerste 5 of 6 nummers is normaliter voldoende om te weten of je het juiste adres gebruikt.)</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:08Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:28Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002791394,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur tar jag emot bitcoin?",body:'<p>Om du vill ta emot bitcoin från någon, måste du ge dem din bitcoin-adress. Det finns ett antal sätt att göra detta på:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visa dem skärmen "Ta emot pengar" i din Bread-app, och låt dem skanna din QR-kod.</li>\n<li>Tryck på "Dela"-knappen under QR-koden för att skicka din adress till dem via e-post eller textmeddelande.</li>\n<li>Tryck på QR-koden för att kopiera adressen till enhetens minne. Du kan nu klistra in adressen på en webbplats eller i en annan app.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Bitcoin-adressen som visas på din mottagaradress ändras varje gång du får pengar, men gamla adresser fortsätter att fungera.</p>\n<p><strong>Viktigt: </strong> Om bitcoin skickas till fel adress kan de inte återbetalas. När du delar din adress måste du alltid kontrollera att den adress du ger ut är densamma som den som visas under din QR-kod (att jämföra de första 5 eller 6 siffrorna är vanligtvis tillräcklig för att säkerställa att du använder rätt adress).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:08Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:28Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002791414,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何收取比特币？",body:"<p>如果您希望收取他人的比特币，您需要给他们提供您的比特币地址。这么做可以有以下几种方法：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>给他们显示 Bread 应用的“收款”屏幕，让他们扫描您的二维码。</li>\n<li>点击二维码下方的“分享”按钮将您的地址通过电子邮件或者短信发送给他们。</li>\n<li>点击二维码将您的地址复制到设备内存中。然后您可以将您的地址粘贴到网站或其他应用中。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>收款屏幕上的比特币地址在每次收款后都会发生变化，但旧地址继续有效。</p>\n<p><strong>重要：</strong>如果比特币被汇往错误地址，则无法退还。在分享您的地址时，务必检查您提供的地址是否与二维码下方显示的地址完全一致（通常比较前 5 或 6 位字符就足以确认您是否在使用正确的地址）。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:08Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:29Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002803053,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo recibo bitcoines?",body:'<p>Si deseas recibir bitcoines de alguien, deberás darle tu dirección de Bitcoin. Hay varias maneras de hacerlo: </p>\n<ul>\n<li> Muéstrale la pantalla "Recibir dinero" en tu aplicación Bread y déjales escanear tu código QR.</li>\n<li>Pulsa el botón "Compartir" debajo del código QR para enviarle tu dirección por correo electrónico o mensaje de texto.</li>\n<li>Toca el código QR para copiar tu dirección a la memoria de tu dispositivo. Ahora puedes pegar la dirección en un sitio web u otra aplicación.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>La dirección de Bitcoin que aparece en la dirección de recepción cambiará cada vez que recibas dinero, pero las direcciones antiguas seguirán funcionando.</p>\n<p><strong>Importante:</strong>Si se envían bitcoines a una dirección incorrecta, no se pueden reembolsar. Cuando compartas tu dirección, asegúrate siempre de que la dirección que des sea la misma que se muestra en tu código QR (comparar los primeros 5 ó 6 dígitos suele ser suficiente para asegurarte de que estás usando la dirección correcta).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:07Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:27Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002803073,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come faccio a ricevere dei bitcoin?",body:'<p>Se vuoi ricevere dei bitcoin, dovrai fornire alla controparte il tuo indirizzo bitcoin. Puoi farlo in vari modi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Mostrando la schermata "Ricevi Denaro" della tua app Bread, così potranno usare il tuo codice QR.</li> \n<li>Premendo il pulsante "Condividi" presente sotto al codice QR, così potrai inviarlo tramite email o messaggio.</li>\n<li>Premendo sul codice QR per salvare l\'indirizzo nella memoria del tuo dispositivo. Successivamente potrai incollare il tuo indirizzo su un sito o su altre app.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>L\'indirizzo bitcoin mostrato come indirizzo di ricezione cambierà ogni volta che riceverai denaro, ma gli indirizzi precedenti continueranno a funzionare.</p>\n<p><strong>Importante: </strong>Non è possibile recuperare i bitcoin inviati ad un indirizzo sbagliato. Quando condividi il tuo indirizzo, assicurati che corrisponda sempre a quello mostrato sotto al tuo codice QR (tipicamente basta confrontare le prime 5-6 cifre per esserne sicuri).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:07Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:27Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002803093,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ビットコインを受け取る方法は?",body:"<p>ビットコインを受け取りたい場合には、あなたのビットコインを送信者に通知する必要があります:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>あなたのBreadアプリの「お金を受領」の画面を見せて、QRコードをスキャンしてもらってください。</li>\n<li>QRコード下の「共有」ボタンを押して、EメールまたはSMSメッセージであなたのアドレスを送信。</li>\n<li>QRコードをタップしてあなたのデバイス上にアドレスをコピー。これでウェブサイト内または他のアプリへとアドレスをペーストできるようになります。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>あなたの受信アドレス上に表示されるビットコインアドレスはお金を受領する度に代わりますが、以前のアドレスも継続して利用できます。</p>\n<p><strong>注意: </strong>ビットコインが間違ったアドレスに送信された場合の返金は不可能です。あなたのアドレスを共有する際には、アドレスがQRコード下に表示されているアドレスと同じものであることを常にご確認ください (アドレスが正しいものであることを確認する為には通常は最初の5・6桁を比べてみれば十分です)。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:07Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:28Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002791354,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je recevoir des bitcoins ?",body:"<p>Si vous souhaitez recevoir des bitcoins de la part de quelqu'un, il vous faudra lui donner votre adresse bitcoin. Il existe plusieurs façons de le faire :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Montrez-lui la page « Recevoir de l'argent » sur votre appli Bread et laissez-le scanner votre code QR.</li>\n<li>Appuyez sur le bouton « Partager » situé sous le code QR pour lui envoyer votre adresse par e-mail ou par SMS.</li>\n<li>Touchez le code QR pour copier votre adresse dans la mémoire de votre appareil. Vous pouvez désormais coller votre adresse sur un site web ou une autre appli.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>L'adresse bitcoin affichée sur votre adresse de réception changera à chaque fois que vous recevrez de l'argent, mais les anciennes adresses fonctionneront toujours.</p>\n<p><strong>Important : </strong>si des bitcoins sont envoyés à la mauvaise adresse, ils ne pourront pas être remboursés. En partageant votre adresse, vérifiez toujours que l'adresse que vous donnez est identique à celle affichée sous votre code QR (comparer les 5 ou 6 premiers chiffres est généralement suffisant pour vous assurer d'utiliser la bonne adresse).</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:07Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:27Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002803033,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie kann ich Bitcoins empfangen?",body:"<p>Wenn Sie Bitcoins von jemandem empfangen möchten, dann müssen Sie ihm oder ihr Ihre Bitcoin-Adresse geben. Dies kann auf verschiedene Arten geschehen:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Zeigen Sie der Person den „Geld empfangen“-Bildschirm in Ihrer Bread-App und lassen Sie sie Ihren QR-Code scannen.</li>\n<li>Drücken Sie den „Teilen“-Button unter dem QR-Code, um Ihre Adresse per E-Mail oder SMS zu versenden.</li>\n<li>Tippen Sie den QR-Code an, um Ihre Adresse in den Speicher Ihres Geräts zu kopieren. Sie können Ihre Adresse nun auf einer Webseite oder in eine andere App einfügen.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Die Bitcoin-Adresse, die als Ihre Empfangsadresse angezeigt wird, ändert sich jedes Mal, wenn Sie Geld empfangen, alte Adressen funktionieren allerdings weiterhin.\n</p>\n<p><strong>Wichtig: </strong>Bitcoins können nicht erstattet werden, falls sie an die falsche Adresse versendet wurden. Stellen Sie, wenn Sie Ihre Adresse teilen stets sicher, dass die Adresse, die Sie herausgeben, dieselbe ist wie die unter Ihrem QR-Code angezeigte (es reicht normalerweise aus, die ersten 5 oder 6 Stellen zu vergleichen, um sicher zu gehen, dass Sie die korrekte Adresse verwenden).</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:06Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:27Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002791334,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan modtager jeg bitcoin?",body:'<p> Hvis du gerne vil modtage bitcoin fra nogen, skal du give dem din bitcoin-adresse. Der er et par måder at gøre dette på:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Vis dem "Modtag penge"-skærmen i din Bread-app, og lad dem scanne din QR-kode.</li>\n<li>Tryk på knappen "Del" under QR-koden for at sende dem din adresse via e-mail eller besked.</li>\n<li> Tryk på QR-koden for at kopiere din adresse til enhedens hukommelse. Du kan nu indsætte din adresse på et websted eller i en anden app.</li>\n</ul>\n<p> Bitcoin-adressen vist på din modtagelsesadresse ændres hver gang du modtager penge, men gamle adresser vil fortsat fungere.</p>\n<p><strong>Vigtigt:</strong> Hvis bitcoin sendes til den forkerte adresse, kan de ikke refunderes. Når du deler din adresse, skal du altid kontrollere, at den adresse du udsender er den samme som den, der vises under din QR-kode (sammenligning af de første 5 eller 6 cifre er normalt nok til at sikre dig at du bruger den rigtige adresse).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:06Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:26Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001236574,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763394/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763394",source_id:115000763394,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How do I receive bitcoin?",body:'<p>If you would like to receive bitcoin from someone, you will need to give them your bitcoin address. There are a few ways to do this:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Show them the "Receive Money" screen in your Bread app, and let them scan your QR code.</li>\n<li>Press the "Share" button under the QR code to send them your address via email or text message.</li>\n<li>Tap the QR code to copy your address to your device\'s memory. You can now paste your address into a website or other app.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The bitcoin address shown on your receive address will change every time you receive money, but old addresses will continue to work.</p>\n<p><strong>Important: </strong>If bitcoin is sent to the wrong address, it can not be refunded. When sharing your address, always check to make sure the address you give out is the same as the one shown under your QR code (comparing the first 5 or 6 digits is usually sufficient to make sure you are using the correct address).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T18:53:13Z",updated_at:"2017-07-23T01:24:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115006314468,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115006314468-What-are-the-fees-for-buying-bitcoin-through-Bread-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115006314468-What-are-the-fees-for-buying-bitcoin-through-Bread-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001986188,created_at:"2017-04-24T21:53:40Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:22:10Z",name:"What are the fees for buying bitcoin through Bread?",title:"What are the fees for buying bitcoin through Bread?",body:'<p>Fees, when purchasing bitcoin through Bread, are different depending on the payment method used. Fees will be displayed under each payment method after choosing "buy bitcoin" from the Bread menu.</p>\n<p>When using a bitcoin ATM, fees can vary based on location and are often set by the local operator. Please see the ATM itself for details.</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:[],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002792614,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"經由 bread 錢包購買比特幣的費用為何？",body:"<p>當透過 bread 錢包購買比特幣時，費用會依使用的付款方式而有所不同。在由 bread 錢包選項選擇「購買比特幣」後，費用會顯現在每個付款方式下方。</p>\n<p>在使用比特幣 ATM 時，費用會依地點而有所不同，且通常是由當地營運單位設定。請查閱 ATM 上的細節。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:39Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:56Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002792574,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Vilka avgifter är förknippade med att köpa bitcoin via breadplånboken?",body:'<p>Avgifterna är olika beroende på vilken betalningsmetod som används när du köper bitcoin via breadplånboken. Avgifterna visas under varje betalningsmetod efter att "köp bitcoin" har valts från breadplånbokens meny.</p>\n<p>När du använder en bitcoin-uttagsautomat kan avgifterna variera beroende på plats och bestäms ofta av den lokala operatören. Vänligen se den aktuella uttagsautomaten för fler uppgifter.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:38Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:55Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002804353,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Quais são as taxas para comprar bitcoin através do Bread?",body:'<p>Quando compra bitcoin através do Bread, as taxas variam com base no método de pagamento usado. As taxas serão exibidas abaixo de cada método de pagamento após escolher "comprar bitcoin" no menu do Bread.</p>\n<p>Quando usa uma caixa multibanco de bitcoin, as taxas podem variar com base no local e são normalmente definidas pelo operador local. Consulte a caixa de bitcoin para mais detalhes.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:38Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:04Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002792594,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"通过 Bread 钱包购买比特币的手续费是多少？",body:"<p>通过 Bread 钱包购买比特币的手续费随您所采用的支付方式而不同。在 Bread 钱包菜单中选择“购买比特币”后，相应手续费将显示在每种支付方式的下方。</p>\n<p>当使用比特币 ATM 机时，手续费可能随地点而变化，并且经常是由当地运营商设定的。请查看 ATM 机了解详情。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:38Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:56Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002804373,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Какой сбор взимается за покупку биткоинов через кошелек Bread?",body:"<p>Сбор при покупке биткоинов через наш кошелек будут отличаться в зависимости от способа оплаты. Сбор будет указан под каждым способом оплаты после выбора пункта «Купить биткоины» из меню кошелька.</p>\n<p>При использовании биткоин-банкомата сбор может отличаться в зависимости от местоположения – обычно его устанавливает местный оператор банкомата. Все подробности должны быть указаны на самом банкомате.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:38Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:55Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002792514,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Quels sont les frais pour l'achat de bitcoin depuis Bread ?",body:"<p>Les frais lors de l'achat de bitcoin depuis Bread sont différents selon le mode de paiement utilisé. Les frais seront affichés sous chaque mode de paiement après avoir sélectionné « Acheter des bitcoins » dans le menu de Bread.</p>\n<p>En utilisant un distributeur automatique de bitcoin, les frais peuvent varier en fonction du lieu et sont souvent définis par l'opérateur local. Veuillez consulter le distributeur automatique pour les détails.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:37Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:04Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002792534,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Quali sono i costi di commissione per l'acquisto di bitcoin tramite Bread?",body:"<p>Le commissioni per l'acquisto di bitcoin tramite Bread variano a seconda del metodo di pagamento usato. Le commissioni verranno mostrate sotto a ciascun metodo di pagamento dopo che avrai selezionato \"acquista bitcoin\" dal menu di Bread.</p>\n<p>Quando usi un ATM bitcoin, le commissioni variano in base alla posizione e tipicamente dipendono dall'operatore locale. Consulta direttamente l'ATM per ulteriori dettagli.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:37Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:04Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002792554,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Wat zijn de kosten om bitcoin via Bread te kopen?",body:'<p> Kosten die je maakt wanneer je bitcoin bestelt via Bread, verschillen op basis van de betaalwijze. Kosten zullen weergegeven worden onder elke betaalmethode nadat je kiest voor "koop bitcoin" uit het Bread menu.</p>\n<p>Wanneer je een bitcoin geldautomaat gebruikt,\n kunnen kosten verschillen gebaseerd op de locatie en zijn vaak bepaald door de lokale verwerker. Bekijk de geldautomaat voor details.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:37Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:04Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002804333,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"Breadを通してビットコインを購入する際の料金は?",body:"<p>Breadを通してビットコインを購入する際の料金は支払い方法によって異なります。料金はBreadのメニューから「ビットコインを購入」を選択された後に、各支払いの下部に表示されます。</p>\n<p>ビットコインATMを使用された場合には、料金は所在地によって異なり、大抵の場合はその地域の運営業者により設定されています。詳細に関してはATM自体でご確認ください。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:37Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:22:10Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002792494,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie hoch sind die Gebühren, wenn ich Bitcoins über Bread kaufe?",body:"<p>Die Gebühren, die beim Kauf von Bitcoins über Bread anfallen, sind je nach verwendeter Zahlungsmethode unterschiedlich. Die Gebühren werden unter jeder Zahlungsmethode angezeigt, nachdem Sie im Bread-Menü „Bitcoins kaufen“ ausgewählt haben.</p>\n<p>Die bei der Benutzung eines Bitcoin-Geldautomaten anfallenden Gebühren können je nach Standort variieren und werden häufig vom örtlichen Betreiber festgelegt. Bitte sehen Sie für Details auf dem Geldautomaten selbst nach.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:36Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:03Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002804293,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvad er gebyrerne for at købe bitcoin gennem Bread?",body:'<p>Gebyrer, når du køber bitcoin gennem Bread, er forskellige afhængigt af den anvendte betalingsmetode. Gebyrer vil blive vist under hver betalingsmetode efter at have valgt "køb bitcoin" fra Bread-menuen.</p>\n<p> Når du bruger en bitcoin-pengeautomat, kan gebyrer variere afhængigt af lokationen og fastsættes ofte af den lokale operatør. Tjek venligst pengeautomaten selv for detaljer.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:36Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:02Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002804313,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cuáles son los cargos por comprar bitcoines a través de Bread?",body:'<p>Las tarifas, al comprar bitcoines a través de Bread, son diferentes dependiendo del método de pago utilizado. Las tarifas se mostrarán en cada método de pago tras seleccionar la opción "comprar bitcoines" del menú de Bread.</p>\n<p>Al utilizar un cajero de bitcoines, las tarifas pueden variar en función de la ubicación y a menudo las fija el operador local. Consulta el mismo cajero automático para más detalles.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:36Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:03Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115010661928,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115006314468/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115006314468",source_id:115006314468,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"What are the fees for buying bitcoin through Bread?",body:'<p>Fees, when purchasing bitcoin through Bread, are different depending on the payment method used. Fees will be displayed under each payment method after choosing "buy bitcoin" from the Bread menu.</p>\n<p>When using a bitcoin ATM, fees can vary based on location and are often set by the local operator. Please see the ATM itself for details.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-04-24T21:53:40Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:01:55Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115001714994,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115001714994-How-do-I-use-the-Request-an-Amount-screen-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115001714994-How-do-I-use-the-Request-an-Amount-screen-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!1,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977707,created_at:"2017-09-01T00:31:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:22Z",name:'How do I use the "Request an Amount" screen?',title:'How do I use the "Request an Amount" screen?',body:"<p>The QR code you use to receive money in Bread can contain only your bitcoin address, or it can also specify the amount of money that should be sent. If you use the “request an amount” feature, the amount of money you enter will be included in the QR code. When someone scans your QR code, the amount to send will automatically be filled out, so the sender doesn’t have to enter it themselves. This makes it easier to specify how much money should be sent, and prevent mistakes when trying to receive a specific amount of money.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:request-amount"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002793754,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何使用「請款」畫面？",body:"<p>你在 Bread 中用來收到款項的 QR 碼可以只包含你的比特幣位址，或也可以指明應被發送的金額。如果你使用「請款」功能，你輸入的金額將會被加入 QR 碼中。當有人掃描你的 QR 碼時，應發送的金額將會被自動填入，發款方不用自行填寫。這樣一來可輕易表明該發送多少金額，也預防發生錯誤，與約定款項不符。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:06Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002793734,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何使用“请求付款”屏幕？",body:"<p>您在 Bread 中用来收款的二维码可能仅包含您的比特币地址，或者它也可以规定应付款金额。如果您使用“请求付款”功能，您输入的金额将被包括在二维码中。当有人扫描您的二维码，付款金额会自动填入，因此付款方无需自己输入。这更便于规定应付款金额，并防止在试图收取特定金额款项时出错。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:05Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002805353,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:'Como uso o ecrã "Solicitar uma Quantia"?',body:'<p>O código QR que usa para receber dinheiro no Bread pode conter apenas o seu endereço de bitcoin ou pode também especificar o montante que deve ser enviado. Se usar a funcionalidade "solicitar uma quantia", a quantia de dinheiro que introduzir será incluída no código QR. Quando alguém ler o código, a quantia a enviar será automaticamente preenchida, por isso o remetente não tem de a introduzir manualmente. Isto faz com que seja mais fácil especificar a quantia a ser enviada e impedir erros ao tentar receber uma quantia específica de dinheiro.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:05Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002805373,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как использовать экран «Запросить платеж»?",body:"<p>QR-код, который вы используете для получения денег в Bread, может содержать либо только ваш биткоин-адрес, либо же еще и сумму, которую необходимо отправить. Если вы используете функцию «Запросить платеж», то введенная сумма будет включена в QR-код. Когда кто-то отсканирует ваш QR-код, то сумма будет автоматически введена, и отправителю не придется вводить ее самостоятельно. Так можно упростить процесс указания размера платежа и предотвратить ошибки при получении определенной суммы.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:05Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002805393,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:'Hur använder jag "begär ett belopp"-skärmen?',body:'<p>QR-koden du använder för att ta emot pengar i Bread kan antingen innehålla endast din bitcoin-adress, eller så kan den även ange hur mycket pengar som ska skickas. Om du använder funktionen "begär ett belopp", kommer beloppet du anger att inkluderas i QR-koden. När någon skannar din QR-kod, kommer beloppet som ska skickas automatiskt att fyllas i, så att avsändaren inte behöver ange det själv. Det gör det lättare att ange hur mycket pengar som ska skickas och förhindra misstag när man försöker ta emot viss summa pengar.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:05Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002805293,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je utiliser la page « Demander un montant » ?",body:"<p>Le code QR que vous utilisez pour recevoir de l'argent dans Bread peut contenir uniquement votre adresse bitcoin, ou préciser également la somme d'argent devant être envoyée. Si vous utilisez la fonctionnalité « Demander un montant », la somme d'argent que vous entrez sera intégrée au code QR. Lorsqu'une personne scanne votre code QR, le montant à envoyer est complété automatiquement, pour que l'expéditeur n'ait pas à l'entrer lui-même. Cela permet d'indiquer plus facilement la somme d'argent devant être envoyée, et évite les erreurs lors de la réception d'une somme d'argent spécifique.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002805313,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"「指定額をリクエスト」画面の使用方法は?",body:"<p>Breadで送金を受け取るために使用するQRコードにはあなたのビットコインアドレスのみが含まれるようにすることも可能ですが、QRコード内に受領を希望される金額が指定されるように設定することもできます。「指定額をリクエスト」機能を利用すると、あなたが指定する金額がQRコード内に含まれます。そのQRコードをスキャンされると、送信者側が金額を入力しなくても、指定された送金されるべき金額が自動的に入力されます。この機能は送金されるべき金額の指定を容易にし、一定の金額の受領を希望される際に起こりえるミスを防止します。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002805333,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:'Hoe gebruik ik het "Vraag een bedrag" scherm?',body:'<p>De QR-code die je gebruikt om geld in Bread te ontvangen kan slechts je bitcoin-adres bevatten, of het kan ook de hoeveelheid geld aangeven die verstuurd moet worden. Als je de "Vraag een bedrag" functie gebruikt, wordt de hoeveelheid geld die je invoert toegevoegd in de QR-code. Wanneer iemand jouw QR-code scant, wordt het te versturen bedrag automatisch ingevuld, zodat de verzender dit niet meer hoeft te doen. Dit maakt het makkelijker om te specificeren hoeveel geld je krijgt, en voorkomt fouten wanneer je een bepaalde hoeveelheid geld moet ontvangen.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002793714,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:'Come faccio ad usare la schermata "Richiedi un Importo"?',body:"<p>In Bread, il codice QR che usi per ricevere denaro può contenere o solo il tuo indirizzo bitcoin, oppure può indicare anche l'importo di denaro da inviare. Se usi la funzionalità di \"richiesta importo\", l'importo di denaro inserito verrà incluso nel codice QR. Quando qualcuno scansiona il tuo codice QR, l'importo da inviare verrà compilato in automatico, al posto del mittente. Così è più semplice chiarire quanto denaro inviare ed evitare errori quando servono degli importi di denaro specifici.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002805253,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie verwende ich den „Einen Betrag anfordern“-Bildschirm?",body:"<p>Der QR-Code, mit dem Sie in Bread Geld empfangen können, kann entweder nur Ihre Bitcoin-Adresse enthalten oder er kann zusätzlich den genauen Geldbetrag angeben, der versendet werden soll. Falls Sie das „Einen Betrag anfordern“-Feature verwenden, wird der von Ihnen eingegebene Betrag in den QR-Code eingebunden. Wenn jemand Ihren QR-Code scannt, wird der Betrag automatisch ausgefüllt, sodass der Absender ihn nicht selbst eingeben muss. Das macht es einfacher, festzulegen, wie viel Geld versendet werden soll und beugt Fehlern vor, wenn Sie versuchen, einen bestimmten Betrag zu empfangen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002805273,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo utilizar la pantalla “Solicitar una cantidad”?",body:'<p>El código QR que usas para recibir dinero en Bread puede contener solo tu dirección de Bitcoin, o puede además especificar la cantidad de dinero que se debe enviar. Si utilizas la función "solicitar una cantidad", el código QR incluirá también la cantidad de dinero que introduzcas. Cuando alguien escanee tu código QR, la cantidad a enviar se rellenará automáticamente, por lo que el remitente no tiene que introducirla. Esto facilita el especificar cuánto dinero se debe enviar y permite evitar errores al tratar de recibir una cantidad específica de dinero.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002805233,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:'Hvordan bruger jeg "Forespørg et beløb"-skærmen?',body:'<p>QR-koden du bruger til at modtage penge i Bread, kan kun indeholde din bitcoin-adresse, den kan også angive, hvor mange penge der skal sendes. Hvis du bruger "Forespørg et beløb" -funktionen, vil det beløb du skriver ind blive inkluderet i QR-koden. Når nogen scanner din QR-kode, vil beløbet der skal sendes automatisk blive udfyldt, så senderen ikke behøver at skrive det selv. Dette gør det lettere at angive, hvor mange penge der skal sendes, og forhindrer fejl når man prøver at modtage et bestemt beløb.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115002616014,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115001714994/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115001714994",source_id:115001714994,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:'How do I use the "Request an Amount" screen?',body:"<p>The QR code you use to receive money in Bread can contain only your bitcoin address, or it can also specify the amount of money that should be sent. If you use the “request an amount” feature, the amount of money you enter will be included in the QR code. When someone scans your QR code, the amount to send will automatically be filled out, so the sender doesn’t have to enter it themselves. This makes it easier to specify how much money should be sent, and prevent mistakes when trying to receive a specific amount of money.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-01T00:31:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-01T00:31:04Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115009773748,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115009773748-How-to-import-a-wallet-using-a-recovery-phrase.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115009773748-How-to-import-a-wallet-using-a-recovery-phrase",author_id:23725737767,comments_disabled:!1,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977747,created_at:"2017-06-29T19:07:27Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:55Z",name:"How to import a wallet using a recovery phrase",title:"How to import a wallet using a recovery phrase",body:"<p>When you launch Bread for the first time, you will be given the option to create a new wallet or to recover a wallet. If you have a 12 word recovery phrase from a previous wallet that you would like to import, select recover wallet and then enter the phrase. After that has completed, the wallet will need to sync in order to collect all the information it needs about your balance. Initial syncing can take many hours so please prepare to leave the app open for an extended period of time.</p>\n<p>If you wish to import a wallet using a recovery phrase but you already have an active account in Bread, you will need to follow the directions to wipe the wallet before beginning the process above. If the wallet you are wiping has funds, be sure to write down the 12 word recovery phrase for the existing wallet (which can be found in the Security Center) before loading the recovery phrase for the wallet you wish to import.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:[],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002804273,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"如何使用復原單字匯入錢包",body:"<p>當你第一次開啟 Bread 時，可選擇創建新錢包或復原錢包。如果你有想要匯入之先前錢包的 12 字復原碼，選擇復原錢包並輸入單字。完成之後，需要同步錢包來收集有關你的餘額之所有資訊。初步同步可能會持續好幾個小時，因此請做好要將 app 開啟很長一段時間的準備。</p>\n<p>如果你已有正在使用中的 Bread 帳戶，但又希望使用復原單字匯入錢包，在開始作業前你需要依照指示清除錢包。如果你要清除的錢包中有資金，請確認已寫下現有錢包的 12 個復原單字（可在安全中心中找到），然後再載入你想要匯入之錢包的復原單字。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:36Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:53Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002804233,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как мне импортировать кошелек при помощи фразы восстановления?",body:"<p>При первом запуске Bread вы сможете либо создать новый кошелек, либо же восстановить существующий. Если у вас есть фраза из 12-ти слов от предыдущего кошелька, который вы хотите импортировать, то начните восстановление кошелька и введите эту фразу. После этого кошелек нужно синхронизировать, чтобы собрать всю нужную информацию о вашем балансе. Начальная синхронизация может занять много часов, поэтому приготовьтесь оставить приложение открытым длительное время.</p>\n<p>Если вы хотите импортировать кошелек при помощи фразы для восстановления, но у вас уже есть активный аккаунт в Bread, то вам нужно будет следовать руководству по вайпу кошелька перед тем, как начать описанный выше процесс. Если в этом кошельке содержатся средства, то обязательно запишите фразу восстановления из 12-ти слов для существующего кошелька (ее можно найти в центре безопасности) перед загрузкой фразы восстановления кошелька, который вы хотите импортировать.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:35Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:52Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002792474,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"如何使用恢复码导入钱包？",body:"<p>首次启动 Bread 时，您可以选择新建一个钱包或恢复一个钱包。如果您希望导入原来的钱包并且持有包含 12 个词的恢复码，请选择恢复钱包，然后输入恢复码。完成该步骤后，需要对钱包进行同步以便收集有关钱包余额的所有必要信息。首次同步可能需要数小时之久，因此请准备让应用处于长时间开启状态。</p>\n<p>如果您希望使用恢复码导入一个钱包，但是您的 Bread 已经有一个活动账户， 那么您需要按照指示删除该钱包，然后才能够开始上述过程。如果您要删除的钱包里面存有资金，务必记下现有钱包对应的 12 个词恢复码（可以在安全中心找到），然后再载入您希望导入的钱包所对应的恢复码。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:35Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:53Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002804253,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Att importera en plånbok med hjälp av en återställningsfras",body:"<p>När du startar Bread för första gången får du möjlighet att skapa en ny plånbok eller att återställa en plånbok. Om du har en 12 ord lång återställningsfras från en tidigare plånbok som du vill importera, välj återställ plånbok och ange sedan frasen. Efter att importen slutförts måste plånboken synkronisera för att samla in all information som behövs om ditt saldo. Initial synkronisering kan ta många timmar, så var vänligen beredd på att lämna appen öppen under en längre tid.</p>\n<p>Om du vill importera en plånbok med hjälp av en återställningsfras, men redan har ett aktivt konto i Bread, måste du följa anvisningarna för att radera plånboken innan du påbörjar processen ovan. Om plånboken du raderar innehåller pengar, se till att skriva ned den 12 ord långa återställningsfrasen för den befintliga plånboken (som finns i Säkerhetscentralen) innan du läser in återställningsfrasen för plånboken du vill importera.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:35Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:53Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002804213,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como importar uma carteira usando uma frase de recuperação",body:"<p>Quando correr o Bread pela primeira vez, ser-lhe-á dada a opção de criar uma nova carteira ou recuperar uma carteira. Se tiver uma frase de recuperação de 12 palavras de uma carteira anterior que quiser importar, selecione recuperar carteira e introduza a frase. De seguida, a carteira terá de ser sincronizada para recolher todas as informações de que precisa sobre o seu saldo. A sincronização inicial poderá demorar muitas por isso prepare-se para deixar a aplicação aberta durante um intervalo de tempo longo.</p>\n<p>Se quiser importar uma carteira usando uma frase de recuperação mas já tem uma conta ativa no Bread, terá de seguir as instruções para eliminar a carteira antes de iniciar o processo acima. Se a carteira que vai eliminar tem fundos, certifique-se de tomar nota da frase de recuperação de 12 palavras para a carteira existente (que pode ser encontrada no Centro de Segurança) antes de carregar a frase de recuperação da carteira que deseja importar.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:35Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:52Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002792454,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"リカバリフレーズを使ってウォレットをインポートする方法",body:"<p>Breadを初めて起動する際には、新しいウォレットの作成またはウォレットの復元オプションを選択することができます。インポートをしたい以前のウォレットの12単語のリカバリフレーズが保管されている場合には、ウォレットの復元オプションを選択してリカバリフレーズを入力してください。復元完了後には、あなたの残高に関する全情報を収集する為にウォレットの同期を行う必要があります。初回の同期には何時間もかかる場合もあるので、長時間アプリを開いたままにできるように準備をしておきましょう。</p>\n\n\n<p>Bread内に既にアクティブのアカウントをお持ちで、リカバリフレーズを使用してウォレットのインポートをしたい場合には上記のプロセスを開始する前にウォレットをワイプする為の手順に従っていただく必要があります。ワイプを行うウォレットに資金が残っている場合には、インポートを希望するウォレット用のリカバリフレーズをロードする前に、12単語のリカバリフレーズ (セキュリティセンターでご覧いただけます) を必ず書き留めておきましょう。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:34Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:52Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002804133,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"Cómo importar un monedero con una frase de recuperación",body:"<p>Cuando inicias Bread por primera vez, se te dará la opción de recuperar un monedero existente o crear uno nuevo. Si tienes una frase de recuperación de 12 palabras del monedero anterior que desees importar, selecciona la opción Recuperar monedero y, a continuación, introduce la frase. A continuación el monedero tendrá que sincronizarse con el fin de recopilar toda la información que necesita sobre tu saldo. La sincronización inicial puede tardar muchas horas, así que prepárate para dejar la aplicación abierta durante un período prolongado.</p>\n<p>Si deseas importar un monedero con una frase de recuperación pero ya tienes una cuenta activa en Bread, entonces debes seguir las instrucciones para limpiar el monedero antes de comenzar el proceso anterior. Si el monedero que estás limpiando tiene fondos, asegúrate de escribir la frase de recuperación de 12 palabras para el monedero existente (que se puede encontrar en el Centro de seguridad) antes de cargar la frase de recuperación para el monedero que deseas importar.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:34Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:51Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002804153,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment importer un portefeuille à l'aide d'une phrase de récupération",body:"<p>En démarrant Bread pour la première fois, une option vous permettra de créer un nouveau portefeuille ou de récupérer un portefeuille. Si vous possédez la phrase de récupération à 12 mots d'un ancien portefeuille que vous souhaitez importer, sélectionnez « Récupérer un portefeuille » puis entrez la phrase. Une fois ceci effectué, le portefeuille devra être synchronisé afin de collecter toutes les informations nécessaires sur votre solde. La synchronisation initiale peut prendre plusieurs heures, alors préparez-vous à laisser l'appli ouverte pendant une longue période.</p>\n<p>Si vous souhaitez importer un portefeuille à l'aide d'une phrase de récupération mais que vous avez déjà un compte actif dans Bread, il vous faudra suivre les consignes pour effacer le portefeuille avant de commencer la procédure ci-dessus. Si le portefeuille que vous effacez contient des fonds, pensez à écrire la phrase de récupération à 12 chiffres du portefeuille existant (que vous trouverez dans le centre de sécurité) avant de charger la phrase de récupération du portefeuille que vous souhaitez importer.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:34Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:51Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002804173,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come importare un portafoglio usando una frase di recupero",body:"<p>Al primo avvio, Bread ti permetterà di creare un nuovo portafoglio o di ripristinarne uno esistente. Se hai la frase di recupero da 12 parole associata a un portafoglio esistente, seleziona \"recupera portafoglio\" ed inserisci la frase. Dopo aver completato la procedura, si avvierà il processo di sincronizzazione per recuperare tutte le informazioni necessarie sul tuo saldo. La prima sincronizzazione può impiegare diverse ore, quindi ti consigliamo di organizzarti così da poter lasciare l'app aperta per molto tempo.</p>\n<p>Se vuoi importare un portafoglio con una frase di recupero, ma hai già un conto attivo su Bread, dovrai seguire le istruzioni per eliminare il portafoglio prima di iniziare con il processo illustrato sopra. Se il portafoglio che stai eliminando ha dei fondi, ricordati di prendere nota della frase da 12 parole associata al portafoglio attuale (la trovi nel Centro di Sicurezza) prima di procedere con l'importazione del portafoglio che vuoi recuperare.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:34Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:52Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002804193,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe importeer ik een portemonnee met een herstelfrase",body:'<p>Wanneer je Bread voor de eerste keer opent,\n krijg je de optie om een nieuwe portemonnee te maken of een oude portemonnee te herstellen.\n Als je een 12-woorden herstelcode hebt van een vorige portemonnee die je graag wilt importeren,\n selecteer "herstel portemonnee" en voer dan de code in. Wanneer dat gebeurd is, zal de portemonnee gesynchroniseerd moeten worden om alle informatie te verzamelen over je saldo. Het synchroniseren kan veel tijd in beslag nemen, dus bereid je voor de app voor langere tijd open te houden.</p>\n<p>Als je graag een portemonnee importeert met een herstel-code maar je al een actief account in Bread hebt, moet je de aanwijzingen volgen om de portemonnee te wissen voordat je het proces hierboven begint. Als de portemonnee die je gaat wissen nog saldo heeft, zorg er dan voor dat je de 12-woorden herstelcode voor de bestaande portemonnee (die gevonden kan worden in het beveiligingscentrum) opschrijft voordat je de herstelcode voor de portemonnee die je wilt importeren gaat laden.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:34Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:52Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002792414,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Sådan importeres en tegnebog ved hjælp af en gendannelsessætning",body:'<p> Når du starter Bread for første gang, får du mulighed for at oprette en ny tegnebog eller for at gendanne en tegnebog. Hvis du har en 12-ordgendannelsessætning fra en tidligere tegnebog, som du gerne vil importere, skal du vælge "gendan tegnebog" og derefter indtaste sætningen. Efter du har gjort det, skal tegnebogen synkroniseres for at indsamle al den information den har brug for om din balance. Den første synkronisering kan tage mange timer, så vær klar på at appen skal være åben i længere tid.</p>\n<p> Hvis du ønsker at importere en tegnebog ved hjælp af en gendannelsessætning, men du allerede har en aktiv konto i Bread, skal du følge vejledningen for hvordan du sletter en tegnebog, før du starter processen ovenfor. Hvis tegnebogen du sletter indeholder penge, skal du skrive den 12-cifrede gendannelsessætning ned for den eksisterende tegnebog (som findes i sikkerhedscentret), inden du indlæser gendannelsessætningen for den tegnebog, du ønsker at importere.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:33Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:51Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002792434,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie man eine Geldbörse mittels einer Geheimantwort importiert",body:"<p>Wenn Sie Bread das erste Mal starten, erhalten Sie die Option, eine neue Geldbörse zu kreieren oder eine Geldbörse wiederherzustellen. Falls Sie eine aus 12 Wörtern bestehende Geheimantwort einer vorherigen Geldbörse kennen, die Sie importieren möchten, dann wählen Sie Geldbörse wiederherstellen aus und geben Sie anschließend den Satz ein. Danach muss sich die Geldbörse synchronisieren, um alle nötigen Informationen über Ihren Kontostand zu sammeln. Die anfängliche Synchronisation kann viele Stunden dauern, rechnen Sie also damit, die App für eine längere Zeit geöffnet zu lassen.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie eine Geldbörse mit Ihrer Geheimantwort wiederherstellen möchten, aber bereits ein aktives Konto in Bread besitzen, müssen Sie den Anweisungen zum Löschen der Geldbörse folgen, bevor Sie den obigen Prozess beginnen können. Falls die Geldbörse, die Sie löschen möchten, Geld enthält, dann notieren Sie auf jeden Fall die aus 12 Wörtern bestehende Geheimantwort der existierenden Geldbörse (welche im Sicherheitscenter zu finden ist), bevor Sie die Geheimantwort für die Geldbörse laden, die Sie importieren möchten.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:33Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:51Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115016609668,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115009773748/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115009773748",source_id:115009773748,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How to import a wallet using a recovery phrase",body:"<p>When you launch Bread for the first time, you will be given the option to create a new wallet or to recover a wallet. If you have a 12 word recovery phrase from a previous wallet that you would like to import, select recover wallet and then enter the phrase. After that has completed, the wallet will need to sync in order to collect all the information it needs about your balance. Initial syncing can take many hours so please prepare to leave the app open for an extended period of time.</p>\n<p>If you wish to import a wallet using a recovery phrase but you already have an active account in Bread, you will need to follow the directions to wipe the wallet before beginning the process above. If the wallet you are wiping has funds, be sure to write down the 12 word recovery phrase for the existing wallet (which can be found in the Security Center) before loading the recovery phrase for the wallet you wish to import.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-06-29T19:07:27Z",updated_at:"2017-08-29T01:19:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:23725737767}}},{id:115000763834,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000763834-How-do-I-get-started-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763834-How-do-I-get-started-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!1,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001986208,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:22:50Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:50Z",name:"How do I get started?",title:"How do I get started?",body:'<h3>Welcome to Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread connects directly to the bitcoin network. There are no accounts or usernames with Bread. Instead, you will have a "wallet" where you will store your money. It\'s just like the physical wallet you put your cash in, except that it exists only on the internet and holds digital money.</p>\n<p>If this is your first time using Bread, simply choose "Create New Wallet" to start.</p>\n<p>If you have used Bread before and would like to use the same wallet, choose "Recover Wallet" and prepare to enter the Paper Key for the wallet you would like to restore.</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:start-view"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002803973,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何開始？",body:"<h3>歡迎來到 Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread 與比特幣網路直接連接。在 Bread 中不需要帳號或用戶名。你會有一個可以存放金錢的「錢包」。它就像實體收納現金的錢包一樣，只是存在於網路上，並收納電子貨幣。</p>\n<p>如果你是第一次使用 Bread，只要選擇「創建新錢包」即可開始。</p>\n<p>如果你之前有使用過 Bread 並想要使用相同錢包，選擇「復原錢包」並準備輸入想要復原錢包之紙金鑰。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:30Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:47Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002792274,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何开始使用？",body:"<h3>欢迎使用 Bread！</h3>\n<p>Bread 与比特币网络直接相连。Bread 没有账户或用户名。作为替代，您将拥有一个可用来存钱的“钱包”。它就像您用来存放现金的实体钱包一样，只不过它仅存在于互联网上，而且里面保存的是数字货币。</p>\n<p>如果这是您第一次使用 Bread，只需选择“新建钱包”即可开始。</p>\n<p>如果您之前用过 Bread，并且希望继续使用原来的钱包，请选择“恢复钱包”并准备输入您希望恢复的钱包所对应的纸钥匙。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:30Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:47Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002792234,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como começo?",body:'<h3>Bem-vindo ao Bread!</h3>\n<p>O Bread liga-se diretamente à rede de bitcoin. Aqui não há contas ou nomes de utilizador. Em vez disso, tem uma "carteira" onde irá armazenar o seu dinheiro. É como uma carteira física onde põe o seu dinheiro, excepto que existe apenas na internet e contém dinheiro digital.</p>\n<p>Se esta for a primeira vez que usa o Bread, basta escolher "Criar Nova Carteira" para começar.</p>\n<p>Se já usou o Bread e gostaria de usar a mesma carteira, escolha "Recuperar Carteira" e introduza a Chave de Papel da carteira que quiser restaurar.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:29Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:47Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002792254,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как начать работу?",body:"<h3>Добро пожаловать в Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread подключается напрямую к биткоин-сети. В Bread нет аккаунтов или имен пользователя – вместо этого у вас есть «кошелек», где вы храните свои деньги. Это похоже на физический кошелек, где вы храните наличность, но он существует только в интернете и в нем хранится цифровая валюта.</p>\n<p>Если вы используете Bread впервые, то просто выберите «Создать новый кошелек», чтобы начать работу.</p>\n<p>Если вы уже работали с Bread и хотите использовать тот же кошелек, то выберите «Восстановить кошелек» и приготовьтесь ввести бумажный ключ того кошелька, который вы хотите восстановить.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:29Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:47Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002803933,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe begin ik?",body:'<h3>Welkom bij Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread verbindt direct met het bitcoin-netwerk.\n Er zijn geen accounts of gebruikersnamen met Bread. In plaats daarvan heb je een "portemonnee" waar je je geld opslaat. Het is precies zoals een echte portemonnee waar je je geld in bewaart, maar deze bestaat alleen op het internet en bevat digitaal geld.</p>\n<p>Als dit je eerste keer is dat je Bread gebruikt,\n kies "Maak nieuwe portemonnee" om te starten.</p>\n<p>Als je Bread al eerder gebruikt hebt en graag dezelfde portemonnee gebruikt, kies "Herstel portemonnee" en pak je Papiersleutel erbij voor de portemonnee die je wilt herstellen.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:29Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:46Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002803953,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur kommer jag igång?",body:'<h3>Välkommen till Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread ansluts direkt till bitcoin-nätverket. Det finns inga konton eller användarnamn i Bread. Istället får du en "plånbok" där du sparar dina pengar. Det fungerar precis som en fysisk plånbok man lägger pengar i, förutom att den endast finns på internet och innehåller digitala pengar.</p>\n<p>Om det här är första gången du använder Bread, välj helt enkelt "Skapa ny plånbok" för att börja.</p>\n<p>Om du har använt Bread förut och vill använda samma plånbok, välj "Återställ plånbok" och ange pappersnyckeln för plånboken du vill återställa.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:29Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:47Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002792194,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je démarrer ?",body:"<h3>Bienvenue sur Bread !</h3>\n<p>Bread se connecte directement au réseau bitcoin. Il n'y a aucun compte ni nom d'utilisateur avec Bread. Vous obtiendrez un « portefeuille » dans lequel stocker votre argent. Il fonctionne comme le portefeuille physique où vous rangez vos espèces, sauf qu'il n'existe que sur internet et contient de la monnaie électronique.</p>\n<p>Si vous utilisez Bread pour la première fois, il vous suffit de choisir « Créer un nouveau portefeuille » pour commencer.</p>\n<p>Si vous avez déjà utilisé Bread et souhaitez utiliser le même portefeuille, choisissez « Récupérer le portefeuille » et préparez-vous à saisir la clé papier du portefeuille que vous souhaitez restaurer.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:28Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:46Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002792214,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"使用を開始する方法は?",body:"<h3>Breadへようこそ!</h3>\n<p>Breadはビットコインネットワークへと直接接続します。Breadに使用されるアカウントやユーザーネームはありませんが、その代わりにあなたのお金を保管できる「ウォレット」を手にすることになります。このウォレットとは実際のお金を入れるお財布のようなものですが、ウォレットはインターネット上だけに存在し、デジタル通貨を保管することができます。</p>\n<p>Breadを今回初めて使用される場合には、「新しいウォレットを作成」を選択してスタートしましょう。</p>\n<p>Breadを以前に使用したことがあり、同じウォレットを使用したい場合には「ウォレットを復元」を選択して、復元したいウォレットへのペーパーキーを入力してください。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:28Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:46Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002803893,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Por dónde empiezo?",body:'<h3>¡Bienvenido a Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread se conecta directamente a la red de Bitcoin. En Bread no hay cuentas ni nombres de usuario. En su lugar, tendrás un "monedero" donde almacenar tu dinero. Es como un monedero físico en el que depositas tu dinero, excepto que solo existe en Internet y tiene dinero digital.</p>\n<p>Si es la primera vez que usas Bread, simplemente selecciona "Crear un nuevo monedero" para empezar.</p>\n<p>Si has usado Bread antes y quieres usar el mismo monedero, selecciona "Recuperar monedero" y prepárate para introducir la clave de papel para el monedero que desees restaurar.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:28Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:46Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002803913,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Da dove inizio?",body:'<h3>Benvenuto su Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread si collega direttamente alla rete bitcoin. Non servono account o nomi utente. Avrai un "portafoglio" dove potrai conservare i tuoi soldi. È proprio come un portafoglio per contanti, però esiste solo su internet e contiene soldi digitali.</p>\n<p>Se è la prima volta che usi Bread, seleziona "Crea Nuovo Portafoglio" per iniziare.</p>\n<p>Se hai già usato Bread in passato e vuoi usare lo stesso portafoglio, seleziona "Recupera Portafoglio" e prepara la Chiave Cartacea del portafoglio che vuoi ripristinare.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:28Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:46Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002792174,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie beginne ich?",body:"<h3>Willkommen bei Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread verbindet sich direkt mit dem Bitcoin-Netzwerk. Es gibt bei Bread keine Konten oder Nutzernamen. Stattdessen verfügen Sie über eine „Geldbörse“, in der Sie Ihr Geld aufbewahren. Sie ist genau wie die echte Geldbörse, in die Sie Ihr Bargeld hineintun, außer, dass sie nur im Internet existiert und digitales Geld enthält.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie Bread zum ersten Mal verwenden, wählen Sie zum Beginnen einfach „Neue Geldbörse erstellen“ aus.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie Bread schon einmal verwendet haben und gern die gleiche Geldbörse benutzen würden, wählen Sie „Geldbörse wiederherstellen“ und bereiten Sie sich darauf vor, den Paper Key für die Geldbörse einzugeben, die Sie wiederherstellen möchten.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:28Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:45Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002803873,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan kommer jeg i gang?",body:'<h3> Velkommen til Bread! </h3>\n<p> Bread er direkte forbundet til bitcoin-netværket. Der er ingen konti eller brugernavne med Bread. I stedet får du en "tegnebog" hvor du kan opbevare dine penge. Det er ligesom den fysiske tegnebog hvor du lægger penge i den, bortset fra at den kun findes på internettet og indeholder digitale penge.</p>\n<p> Hvis dette er første gang du bruger Bread, skal du bare vælge "Opret ny tegnebog" for at starte.</p>\n<p> Hvis du har brugt Bread før og gerne vil bruge den samme tegnebog, skal du vælge "Gendan tegnebog" og forberede dig på at indtaste papirnøglen for den tegnebog, du gerne vil gendanne.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:27Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:45Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001237114,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763834/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763834",source_id:115000763834,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How do I get started?",body:'<h3>Welcome to Bread!</h3>\n<p>Bread connects directly to the bitcoin network. There are no accounts or usernames with Bread. Instead, you will have a "wallet" where you will store your money. It\'s just like the physical wallet you put your cash in, except that it exists only on the internet and holds digital money.</p>\n<p>If this is your first time using Bread, simply choose "Create New Wallet" to start.</p>\n<p>If you have used Bread before and would like to use the same wallet, choose "Recover Wallet" and prepare to enter the Paper Key for the wallet you would like to restore.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:22:50Z",updated_at:"2017-08-29T01:19:24Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000757893,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000757893-Why-is-my-wallet-disabled-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757893-Why-is-my-wallet-disabled-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:16:30Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:47Z",name:"Why is my wallet disabled?",title:"Why is my wallet disabled?",body:"<p>If you enter an incorrect wallet PIN too many times, your wallet will become disabled for a certain amount of time. This is to prevent someone else from trying to guess your PIN by quickly making many guesses. If your wallet is disabled, wait until the time shown and you will be able to enter your PIN again.</p>\n<p>If you continue to enter the incorrect PIN, the amount of time you will have to wait in between attempts will increase. Eventually, the app will reset and you can start a new wallet.</p>\n<p>If you have the paper key for your wallet, you can use it to reset your PIN by choosing the appropriate option on the lock screen.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:wallet-disabled"],locales:{sv:{id:115002803833,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Varför är min plånbok avstängd?",body:"<p>Om du anger en felaktig plånboks-PIN för många gånger blir din plånbok avstängd under en viss tid. Detta för att förhindra att någon annan försöker gissa din PIN-kod genom att snabbt göra många gissningar. Om din plånbok blir avstängd, vänta tills den angivna tiden för att kunna ange din PIN igen.</p>\n<p>Om du fortsätter att ange den felaktiga PIN-koden, ökar den tid du måste vänta mellan försök. Så småningom kommer appen att nollställas och du kan starta en ny plånbok.</p>\n<p>Om du har pappersnyckeln för din plånbok kan du använda den för att återställa PIN-koden genom att välja det relevanta alternativet på låsskärmen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:27Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:44Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-tw":{id:115002803853,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"為何我的錢包失效了？",body:"<p>如果你輸入錯誤的錢包 PIN 碼太多次，你的錢包將會有一段時間無法使用。這是為了防止其他人快速多次猜測你的 PIN 碼。如你的錢包無法使用，待指定的時間過後你將得以再次輸入 PIN 碼。</p>\n<p>如果你持續輸入錯誤 PIN 碼，每次嘗試間所需等待的時間將會增加。最後，app 將會重設，你可以重建新的錢包。</p>\n<p>如果你有錢包的紙金鑰，你可以使用它來重設 PIN 碼，只要在鎖定畫面中選擇適當選項。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:27Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:45Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002792154,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"为什么我的钱包会被禁用？",body:"<p>如果您输入错误的钱包 PIN 码太多次，您的钱包将会被禁用一段时间。这是为了防止他人通过快速多次猜测尝试猜出您的 PIN 码。如果您的钱包被禁用，等所显示的时间过后，即可再次输入您的\nPIN 码。</p>\n<p>如果您继续输入错误的 PIN 码，两次尝试间必须等待的时间会随之延长。最终，应用将重置，您可以新建一个钱包。</p>\n<p>如果您有钱包的纸钥匙，您可以在锁定屏幕上选择相应选项，然后用它重置您的 PIN 码。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:27Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:45Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002803773,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Waarom is mijn portemonnee uitgeschakeld?",body:"<p>Als je een onjuiste PIN te vaak invoert, wordt je portemonnee afgesloten voor een bepaalde tijd.\n Dit voorkomt dat iemand anders je PIN raadt door snel vaak te raden. Als je portemonnee is afgesloten, wacht tot de aangegeven tijd verstreken is en dan kan je je PIN opnieuw invoeren.</p>\n<p>Als je de onjuiste PIN in blijft voeren, wordt de tijd die je moet wachten tussen pogingen steeds langer. Uiteindelijk zal de app resetten en kun je een nieuwe portemonnee aanmaken.</p>\n<p>Als je een Papiersleutel hebt voor je portemonnee, kun je je PIN resetten door de juiste optie te kiezen op het lockscherm.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:26Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:44Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002803793,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Porque é que a minha carteira está bloqueada?",body:"<p>Se introduzir um PIN incorreto demasiadas vezes, a sua carteira será bloqueada durante um determinado intervalo de tempo. Isto serve para impedir outras pessoas de tentarem adivinhar o seu PIN ao fazerem várias tentativas rápidas. Se a sua carteira for bloqueada, espere até passar o intervalo exibido e poderá introduzir novamente o seu PIN.</p>\n<p>Se continuar a introduzir o PIN incorreto, o intervalo de tempo que terá de esperar entre tentativas irá aumentar. Eventualmente, a aplicação irá reiniciar e poderá criar uma nova carteira.\n</p>\n<p>Se tiver a chave de papel da sua carteira, pode usá-la para repor o seu PIN ao escolher a opção apropriada no ecrã de bloqueio.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:26Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:44Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002803813,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Почему мой кошелек отключен?",body:"<p>Если вы введете неверный ПИН-код слишком много раз подряд, то ваш кошелек будет отключен на некоторое время, чтобы не дать злоумышленнику узнать ваш ПИН-код путем перебора. Если ваш кошелек отключен, то подождите указанное время, и вы сможете снова ввести свой ПИН-код.</p>\n<p>Если вы продолжите вводить неверный ПИН-код, то время между попытками ввода будет увеличиваться. В конечном итоге приложение будет сброшено, и вы сможете создать новый кошелек.</p>\n<p>Если у вас есть бумажный ключ для кошелька, вы можете сбросить свой ПИН-код при помощи соответствующей кнопки на экране блокировки.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:26Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:44Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002792134,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"なぜ私のウォレットは使用不可能になっているのでしょうか?",body:"<p>間違ったウォレットの暗証番号が何度も入力された場合には、あなたのウォレットは一定期間使用不可能にされます。この機能は他人が何度も番号を入力してあなたの暗証番号を推測することを防ぐ為のものです。ウォレットが使用不可能となった場合には、表示されている時間が過ぎるまで待つと再び暗証番号を入力することが可能になります。</p>\n<p>間違った暗証番号を何度も繰り返し入力するほど待たなければならない時間が長くなります。最終的にはアプリがリセットされ、新しいウォレットをスタートすることができます。</p>\n<p>あなたのウォレットへのペーパーキーが保管されている場合には、ロック画面でオプションを選択することによりペーパーキーを暗証番号のリセットに使用することができます。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:26Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:43Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002803733,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Warum ist meine Geldbörse deaktiviert?",body:"<p>Wenn Sie zu oft die falsche Geldbörsen-PIN eingeben, wird Ihre Geldbörse für einen bestimmten Zeitraum deaktiviert. Dies geschieht, um zu verhindern, dass jemand durch viele Versuche innerhalb kurzer Zeit Ihre PIN errät. Falls Ihre Geldbörse deaktiviert wird, warten Sie die angegebene Zeit ab und Sie können Ihre PIN erneut eingeben.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie weiterhin die falsche PIN eingeben, wird sich der Zeitraum zwischen Ihren Versuchen verlängern. Irgendwann wird sich die App zurücksetzen und Sie können eine neue Geldbörse beginnen.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie einen Paper Key für Ihre Geldbörse haben, können Sie diesen zum Zurücksetzen Ihrer PIN nutzen, indem Sie die entsprechende Option auf dem Sperrbildschirm auswählen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:25Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:43Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002803753,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Perché il mio portafoglio è stato disattivo?",body:"<p>Se inserisci più volte un PIN errato, il tuo portafoglio verrà disattivato per un certo periodo di tempo. Questa funzionalità impedisce ad altre persone di indovinare il tuo PIN provandone molti in rapida successione. Se il tuo portafoglio è disattivato, aspetta per il tempo richiesto e poi potrai inserire il tuo PIN.</p>\n<p>Se continuerai ad inserire PIN errati, il tempo di attesa tra i tentativi aumenterà. Dopo un certo numero di tentativi, l'app si ripristinerà e potrai creare un nuovo portafoglio.</p>\n<p>Se hai la Chiave Cartacea del tuo portafoglio, potrai usarla per ripristinare il tuo PIN selezionando l'apposita opzione presente nella schermata di blocco.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:25Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:43Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002792094,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Por qué está bloqueado mi monedero?",body:"<p>Si introduces un PIN de monedero incorrecto demasiadas veces, este se bloqueará durante cierto tiempo. Esto se hace para evitar que alguien intente adivinar tu PIN haciendo muchas conjeturas rápidamente. Si tu monedero está bloqueado, espera hasta la hora indicada y podrás volver a introducir tu PIN.</p>\n<p>Si continúas introduciendo el PIN incorrecto, aumentarás la cantidad de tiempo que tendrás que esperar entre intentos. Finalmente, la aplicación se reiniciará y podrás crear un nuevo monedero.</p>\n<p>Si tienes la clave de papel para tu monedero, puedes usarla para restablecer el PIN eligiendo la opción apropiada en la pantalla de bloqueo.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:25Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:43Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002792114,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Pourquoi mon portefeuille est-il désactivé ?",body:"<p>Si vous entrez un code de portefeuille incorrect un trop grand nombre de fois, votre portefeuille sera désactivé pendant un certain temps. Ceci permet d'éviter que quelqu'un n'essaye de deviner votre code en faisant de nombreux essais rapides. Si votre portefeuille est désactivé, patientez jusqu'au moment indiqué et vous pourrez de nouveau saisir votre code.</p>\n<p>Si vous continuez à saisir un code incorrect, la durée d'attente entre chaque essai augmentera. L'appli finira par se réinitialiser et vous pourrez créer un nouveau portefeuille.</p>\n<p>ISi vous possédez la clé papier de votre portefeuille, vous pouvez l'utiliser pour réinitialiser votre code en choisissant l'option appropriée sur l'écran de verrouillage.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:25Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:43Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002803713,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvorfor er min tegnebog deaktiveret?",body:"<p>Hvis du indtaster en forkert tegnebogskode for mange gange, bliver din tegnebog deaktiveret i en bestemt tidsperiode. Dette forhindrer en anden i at forsøge at gætte din PIN-kode ved hurtigt at indtaste mange gæt. Hvis din tegnebog er deaktiveret, skal du vente til den viste tid er ovre, du vil derefter kunne indtaste din pinkode igen.</p>\n<p> Hvis du fortsætter med at indtaste den forkerte PIN-kode, vil mængden af tid du skal vente mellem forsøgene, øges. Til sidst vil appen blive nulstillet, og du kan derefter oprette en ny tegnebog. </p>\n<p> Hvis du har papirnøglen til din tegnebog, kan du bruge den til at nulstille din pinkode ved at vælge den relevante indstilling på låseskærmen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:24Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:42Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001226873,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757893/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757893",source_id:115000757893,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"Why is my wallet disabled?",body:"<p>If you enter an incorrect wallet PIN too many times, your wallet will become disabled for a certain amount of time. This is to prevent someone else from trying to guess your PIN by quickly making many guesses. If your wallet is disabled, wait until the time shown and you will be able to enter your PIN again.</p>\n<p>If you continue to enter the incorrect PIN, the amount of time you will have to wait in between attempts will increase. Eventually, the app will reset and you can start a new wallet.</p>\n<p>If you have the paper key for your wallet, you can use it to reset your PIN by choosing the appropriate option on the lock screen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:16:30Z",updated_at:"2017-07-21T21:56:09Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:234758948,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/234758948-What-is-fingerprint-authentication-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234758948-What-is-fingerprint-authentication-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2016-11-14T23:03:48Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:45Z",name:"What is fingerprint authentication?",title:"What is fingerprint authentication?",body:"<h2>Touch ID on iPhone</h2>\n<p>Touch ID is available on any iPhone 5s or later, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2, or iPad mini 3 or later. If you have it enabled on your device, you can use your fingerprint to unlock your Bread and authorize transactions instead of entering your passcode. You will still be required to enter your passcode periodically for increased security.</p>\n<p>If Touch ID is not enabled on your device, you can enable it in your device's settings under \"Touch ID &amp; Passcode\".</p>\n<h2>Fingerprint Authorization on Android</h2>\n<p>Many Android devices feature a fingerprint reader. You can use your fingerprint to unlock your Bread and authorize transactions instead of entering your passcode. You will still be required to enter your passcode periodically for increased security.</p>\n<p>In order to use this feature in Bread, fingerprint authorization must be enabled on your device. See the phone manufacturer's manual for more information.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:enable-fingerprint-authentication"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002792074,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"什麼是指紋授權？",body:"<h2>iPhone 上的 Touch ID</h2>\n<p>Touch ID 在任何 iPhone 5 或更新、iPad Pro, iPad Air 2,  iPad mini 3 或更新的設備上皆可使用。如果你在裝置上開放此功能，將可以使用你的指紋解鎖 Bread 並授權交易，而不用使用密碼。你不時還是會需要輸入密碼來加強安全性。</p>\n<p>如果 Touch ID 在你的設備上未啟用，你可以在設備設定中的「Touch ID &amp；密碼」中開啟。</p>\n<h2> Android 上的指紋授權</h2>\n<p>許多 Android 設備上都有指紋辨識的功能。你可以使用指紋來解鎖 Bread 並授權交易，而不用使用密碼。你不時還是會需要輸入密碼來加強安全性。</p>\n<p>如要在 Bread 中使用此功能，你的設備需要開啟指紋授權。參閱手機製造商的手冊已獲得更多資訊。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:24Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:42Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002803673,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Vad är auktorisering med fingeravtryck?",body:'<h2>Touch ID på iPhone</h2>\n<p>Touch ID är tillgängligt på alla iPhone 5 eller senare, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2 eller iPad mini 3 eller senare. Om du har aktiverat det på din enhet kan du använda ditt fingeravtryck för att låsa upp din Bread och godkänna transaktioner, istället för att ange din lösenkod. Du kommer fortfarande att behöva ange din lösenkod regelbundet för ökad säkerhet.</p>\n<p>Om Touch ID inte är aktiverat på din enhet kan du aktivera det i enhetens inställningar under "Touch ID och lösenkod". </p>\n<h2>Auktorisering med fingeravtryck på Android </h2>\n<p>Många Android-enheter har en fingeravtrycksläsare. Du kan använda ditt fingeravtryck för att låsa upp din Bread och godkänna transaktioner istället för att ange din lösenkod. Du kommer fortfarande att behöva ange din lösenkod regelbundet för ökad säkerhet.</p>\n<p> För att kunna använda den här funktionen i Bread måste auktorisering med fingeravtryck vara aktiverat på din enhet. Se telefonens användarmanual för mer information.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:24Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:42Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002803693,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"什么是指纹认证？",body:"<h2>iPhone 上的 Touch ID</h2>\n<p>Touch ID 是 iPhone 5s 或更新机型、iPad Pro、iPad Air 2，或 iPad mini 3 或更新机型上提供的一项功能。如果您在您的设备上启用了该项功能，就可以使用您的指纹解锁您的 Bread 并授权交易，无需输入密码。不过您仍会被定期要求输入您的密码以加强安全。</p>\n<p>如果您的设备没有启用 Touch ID，您可以在设备设置中的“Touch ID 与密码”下启用该功能。</p>\n<h2>安卓上的指纹授权</h2>\n<p>很多安卓设备都有指纹识别器。您可以使用您的指纹解锁您的 Bread 并授权交易，无需输入密码。不过您仍会被定期要求输入您的密码以加强安全。</p>\n<p>为了在 Bread 中使用此功能，您必须在您的设备上启用指纹授权。请参见手机厂商的说明书了解更多信息。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:24Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:42Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002803593,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"指紋認証とは?",body:"<h2>iPhoneのTouch ID</h2>\n<p>Touch IDは5s以降の全てのiPhone、iPad Pro、iPad Air 2、iPad mini 3以降のiPadに搭載されています。デバイスのTouch IDが有効にされている場合には、パスコードを入力する代わりに指紋でBreadをロック解除して、取引を承認することができます。それでもセキュリティ強化の為に、定期的にパスコードの入力が要求されます。</p>\n<p>デバイスのTouch IDが有効にされていない場合には、デバイス設定内の 「Touch ID &amp; パスコード」にて有効化することができます。</p>\n<h2>Androidでの指紋認証</h2>\n<p>多くのAndroidデバイスにも指紋認証リーダーは搭載されています。指紋認証を利用してパスコードを入力する代わりに指紋でBreadをロック解除して、取引を承認することができます。それでもセキュリティ強化の為に、定期的にパスコードの入力が要求されます。</p>\n<p>この機能をBread内で使用する為には、デバイス上で指紋認証が有効化されている必要があります。詳細については携帯メーカー側のマニュアルをご覧ください。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:23Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:41Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002803613,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Wat is vingerprint authenticatie?",body:'<h2>Touch ID op iPhone</h2>\n<p> Touch ID is beschikbaar op elke iPhone 5s of nieuwer, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2 of iPad mini 3 en nieuwer. Als je hem hebt ingeschakeld op jouw apparaat kan je je vingerafdruk gebruiken om je Bread te openen en transacties te ondertekenen.\n Je zult nog steeds af en toe een PIN in moeten voeren voor de veiligheid.</p>\n<p> Als Touch ID niet ingeschakeld is op je apparaat, kun je het aanzetten via de instellen onder "Touch ID &amp; Passcode.</p>\n<h2> Vingerafdrukherkenning via Android</h2>\n<p> Veel Androidapparaten hebben een vingerafdrukscanner. Je kunt je vingerafdruk gebruiken om je Bread te openen en transacties te ondertekenen. Je zult nog steeds af en toe een PIN in moeten voeren voor de veiligheid.</p>\n<p> Om deze funcite in Bread te gebruiken, moet vingerafdrukherkenning aan staan op je apparaat.\n Controleer de telefoonhandleiding voor meer informatie.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:23Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:41Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002803633,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"O que é autenticação por impressão digital?",body:'<h2>Touch ID no iPhone</h2>\n<p>Touch ID está disponível no iPhone 5s ou superior, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2 ou iPad mini 3 ou superior. Se o tiver ativado no seu dispositivo, pode usar a sua impressão digital para desbloquear o seu Bread e autorizar transações em vez de introduzir o seu código. Ser-lhe-á solicitado que introduza o seu código periodicamente para uma segurança adicional.</p>\n<p>Se o Touch ID não estiver ativado no seu dispositivo, pode ativá-lo nas definições do seu dispositivo em "Touch ID e Código".</p>\n<h2>Autorização de Impressão Digital em Android</h2>\n<p>Muitos dispositivos Android possuem um leitor de impressões digitais. Pode usar a sua impressão digital para desbloquear o seu Bread e autorizar transações em vez de introduzir o seu código. Ainda assim terá de introduzir o seu código periodicamente para uma segurança adicional.</p>\n<p>Para usar esta funcionalidade no Bread, tem de ser ativada a autorização de impressão digital no seu dispositivo. Consulte o manual do fabricante para mais informações.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:23Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:41Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002803653,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Что такое аутентификация по отпечатку пальца?",body:"<h2>Touch ID на iPhone</h2>\n<p>Функция Touch ID доступна на любом iPhone 5s и выше, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2 или iPad mini 3 или выше. Если эта функция включена на вашем устройстве, то вместо кода вы можете использовать отпечаток пальца для разблокировки Bread и авторизации транзакций. Иногда вам все же нужно будет вводить код – для обеспечения дополнительной безопасности.</p>\n<p>Если Touch ID на вашем не включен, то вы можете включить эту функцию в настройках телефона в разделе «Touch ID и код-пароль».</p>\n<h2>Авторизация по отпечатку пальца на Android</h2>\n<p>На многих Android-устройствах есть сканер отпечатка пальца. Вместо кода вы можете использовать отпечаток пальца для разблокировки Bread и авторизации транзакций. Иногда вам все же нужно будет вводить код – для обеспечения дополнительной безопасности.</p>\n<p>Чтобы использовать эту функцию в Bread, авторизация по отпечатку пальца должна быть включена на вашем устройстве. Дополнительную информацию вы можете найти в руководстве производителя своего телефона.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:23Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:42Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002792014,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Was ist Fingerabdruck-Authentifizierung?",body:"<h2>Touch ID auf dem iPhone</h2>\n<p>Touch ID ist ab dem iPhone 5s, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2, dem iPad mini 3 oder aktuelleren Modellen verfügbar. Falls Sie die Funktion auf Ihrem Gerät aktiviert haben, können Sie Ihren Fingerabdruck dazu verwenden, Ihr Bread zu entsperren und Transaktionen zu autorisieren. Zur Erhöhung der Sicherheit werden Sie trotzdem von Zeit zu Zeit aufgefordert, Ihre PIN einzugeben.</p>\n<p>Falls Touch ID auf Ihrem Gerät nicht aktiviert ist, können Sie die Funktion in Ihren Geräteeinstellungen unter „Touch ID &amp; Kennwort“ aktivieren.</p>\n<h2>Fingerabdruck-Autorisierung in Android</h2>\n<p>Viele Android-Geräte verfügen über einen Fingerabdruckleser. Sie können statt Ihrem Kennwort Ihren Fingerabdruck dazu verwenden, Ihr Bread zu entsperren und Transaktionen zu autorisieren. Zum Zwecke erhöhter Sicherheit werden Sie trotzdem von Zeit zu Zeit aufgefordert, Ihre PIN einzugeben.</p>\n<p>Um dieses Feature in Bread zu verwenden, muss die Fingerabdruck-Autorisierung auf Ihrem Gerät aktiviert sein. Konsultieren Sie für mehr Informationen die Herstelleranleitung.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:22Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:40Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002792034,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Qu'est-ce que l'authentification par empreinte digitale ?",body:"<h2>Touch ID sur iPhone</h2>\n<p>Touch ID est disponible sur tous les appareils iPhone 5s et supérieur, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2, ou iPad mini 3 et supérieur. Si cette fonctionnalité est activée sur votre appareil, vous pouvez utiliser votre empreinte digitale pour déverrouiller votre Bread et autoriser des transactions au lieu de saisir votre code. Ce code vous sera toujours demandé de temps à autre pour plus de sécurité.</p>\n<p>Si Touch ID n'est pas activé sur votre appareil, vous pouvez l'activer dans les réglages de votre appareil dans la catégorie « Touch ID et code ».</p>\n<h2>Autorisation par empreinte digitale sur Android</h2>\n<p>De nombreux appareils Android disposent d'un lecteur d'empreinte digitale. Vous pouvez utiliser votre empreinte digitale pour déverrouiller votre Bread et autoriser des transactions au lieu de saisir votre code. Ce code vous sera toujours demandé de temps à autre pour plus de sécurité.</p>\n<p>Pour utiliser cette fonctionnalité dans Bread, l'autorisation par empreinte digitale doit être activée sur votre appareil. Consultez le mode d'emploi du fabricant de votre téléphone pour plus d'informations.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:22Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:40Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002803573,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Qué es la autenticación de huellas dactilares?",body:'<h2>Identificación táctil en el iPhone</h2>\n<p>La identificación táctil está disponible en cualquier iPhone 5 o posterior, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2 o iPad mini 3 o posterior. Si la tienes activada en tu dispositivo, puedes usar tu huella digital para desbloquear tu Bread y autorizar las transacciones en lugar de introducir tu código de acceso. Aún así, deberás introducir tu código de acceso periódicamente para aumentar la seguridad.</p>\n<p>Si la opción de identificación táctil no está activada en tu dispositivo, puedes activarla desde la configuración del mismo en "Touch ID & Passcode".</p>\n<h2>Autorización de huellas dactilares en Android</h2>\n<p>Muchos dispositivos Android cuentan con un lector de huellas dactilares. Puedes usar tu huella digital para desbloquear tu Bread y autorizar transacciones en vez de introducir el código de acceso. Aún así, deberás introducir el código de acceso periódicamente para aumentar la seguridad.</p>\n<p>Para utilizar esta función en Bread, la autorización de huella digital debe estar activada en tu dispositivo. Consulta el manual del fabricante del teléfono para obtener más información.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:22Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:40Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002792054,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Cos'è l'autenticazione con impronta?",body:'<h2>Touch ID su iPhone</h2>\n<p>Il Touch ID è disponibile su tutti gli iPhone 5s o superiori, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2 o iPad mini 3 o superiori. Se hai attivato questa funzionalità sul tuo dispositivo, potrai usare la tua impronta per sbloccare Bread e per autorizzare le transazioni, al posto del tuo codice. Per migliorare la sicurezza, ti verrà comunque periodicamente chiesto di inserire il codice.</p>\n<p>Se il Touch ID non è attivo sul tuo dispositivo, puoi abilitarlo andando nelle impostazioni del tuo dispositivo, nella sezione "Touch ID e codice".</p>\n<h2>Autorizzazione con Impronta Digitale su Android</h2>\n<p>Molti dispositivi Android dispongono di un lettore di impronte. Puoi usare la tua impronta al posto del codice per sbloccare Bread e per autorizzare le transazioni. Per migliorare la sicurezza, ti verrà comunque periodicamente chiesto di inserire il codice.</p>\n<p>Per poter utilizzare questa funzionalità di Bread, dovrai attivare le autorizzazioni per le impronte digitali sul tuo dispositivo. Consulta il manuale del tuo telefono per i dettagli.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:22Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:41Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002803553,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvad er fingeraftrykgodkendelse?",body:'<h2>Touch-ID på iPhone</h2>\n<p>Touch-ID er tilgængeligt på enhver iPhone 5 eller nyere, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2 eller iPad mini 3 eller nyere. Hvis du har aktiveret det på din enhed, kan du bruge dit fingeraftryk til at låse op for din Bread-konto og godkende transaktioner i stedet for at indtaste din adgangskode. Du skal stadig indtaste din adgangskode periodisk for at øge sikkerheden.</p>\n<p>Hvis Touch-ID ikke er aktiveret på din enhed, kan du aktivere det i enhedens indstillinger under "Touch-ID & adgangskode". </p>\n<h2>Fingeraftrykgodkendelse på Android</h2>\n<p>Mange Android-enheder har en fingeraftrykslæser. Du kan bruge dit fingeraftryk til at låse op for din Bread-konto og godkende transaktioner i stedet for at indtaste din adgangskode. Du skal stadig indtaste din adgangskode periodisk for at øge sikkerheden.</p>\n<p>For at kunne bruge denne funktion i Bread skal fingeraftrykgodkendelse være aktiveret på din enhed. Se telefonproducentens manual for at få flere oplysninger.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:21Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:40Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:251534108,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758948/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234758948",source_id:234758948,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"What is fingerprint authentication?",body:"<h2>Touch ID on iPhone</h2>\n<p>Touch ID is available on any iPhone 5s or later, iPad Pro, iPad Air 2, or iPad mini 3 or later. If you have it enabled on your device, you can use your fingerprint to unlock your Bread and authorize transactions instead of entering your passcode. You will still be required to enter your passcode periodically for increased security.</p>\n<p>If Touch ID is not enabled on your device, you can enable it in your device's settings under \"Touch ID &amp; Passcode\".</p>\n<h2>Fingerprint Authorization on Android</h2>\n<p>Many Android devices feature a fingerprint reader. You can use your fingerprint to unlock your Bread and authorize transactions instead of entering your passcode. You will still be required to enter your passcode periodically for increased security.</p>\n<p>In order to use this feature in Bread, fingerprint authorization must be enabled on your device. See the phone manufacturer's manual for more information.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-14T23:03:48Z",updated_at:"2017-08-29T01:19:23Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000749354,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000749354-What-is-the-security-center-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000749354-What-is-the-security-center-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T00:11:43Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:42Z",name:"What is the security center?",title:"What is the security center?",body:"<p>The Security Center allows you to manage additional security features for your Bread.</p>\n<h3>6-digit PIN</h3>\n<p>This PIN is used to unlock your wallet and send money. It prevents other people from accessing your Bread in case you let someone else use your phone.</p>\n<h3>Paper key</h3>\n<p>If you ever lose or upgrade your phone, you will need your Paper Key to restore your wallet on another device. It is not possible to recover your wallet if you lose both your phone and Paper Key, so write down your Paper Key and keep it safe!</p>\n<h3>Fingerprint / Touch ID</h3>\n<p>While the 6-digit PIN is required to secure your wallet, you can also use your device's fingerprint reader for convenience and added security. Using your fingerprint is quicker than entering a PIN, and if people are watching you unlock your wallet they won't be able to see what your PIN is.</p>\n<p>This option will only appear if your device has a fingerprint reader.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:security-center"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002791994,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"什麼是安全中心？",body:"<p>安全中心讓你得以管理 Bread 的額外安全功能。</p>\n<h3> 6 碼 PIN</h3>\n<p>此 PIN 碼是用來解鎖你的錢包及發送款項。當你讓其他人使用自己的手機時防止他們使用你的 Bread。</p>\n<h3>紙金鑰</h3>\n<p>如果你遺失或升級手機，你需要紙金鑰來在其他設備上復原你的錢包。如果你的手機及紙金鑰皆遺失了，將無法復原錢包，因此請將你的紙金鑰寫下並妥善保管！\n</p>\n<h3>指紋／Touch ID</h3>\n<p>除了使用 6 碼 PIN 來保全你的錢包外，你也可以使用設備的指紋辨識器來增添便利性及安全性。使用你的指紋比輸入 PIN 碼來的更快，且在其他人的目光下解鎖錢包時，他們就不會看到你的 PIN 碼。</p>\n<p>只有在你使用有指紋辨識器的裝置時，此選項才會出現。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:21Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:40Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002803533,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"什么是安全中心？",body:"<p>安全中心让您能管理 Bread 的附加安全功能。</p>\n<h3>6 位数 PIN 码</h3>\n<p>此 PIN 码用于开启您的钱包和付款。如果您让其他人使用您的手机，它可以防止其他人访问您的 Bread。</p>\n<h3>纸钥匙</h3>\n<p>如果您手机丢失或升级，您需要通过纸钥匙在其他设备上恢复您的钱包。如果您同时丢失手机和纸钥匙，那么就不可能找回您的钱包了，因此务必记下您的纸钥匙并妥善保管！</p>\n<h3>指纹/Touch ID</h3>\n<p>尽管必须使用 6 位数 PIN 码保护您的钱包，您也可以使用设备的指纹识别器以求方便或加强安全。使用您的指纹比输入 PIN 码更快捷，而且如果有人在看您解锁您的钱包，他们也无法看到您的 PIN 码是什么。</p>\n<p>这个选项只有在您的设备安装有指纹识别器时才会出现。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:21Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:39Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002791954,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"O que é o centro de segurança?",body:"<p>O Centro de Segurança permite-lhe gerir funcionalidades de segurança adicionais para o seu Bread.</p>\n<h3>PIN de 6 dígitos</h3>\n<p>Este PIN é usado para desbloquear a sua carteira e enviar dinheiro. Impede que outras pessoas acedam ao seu BREAD caso lhes deixe usar o seu telemóvel.</p>\n<h3>Chave de papel</h3>\n<p>Se perder ou trocar de telemóvel, irá precisar da sua Chave de Papel para restaurar a sua carteira noutro dispositivo. Não é possível recuperar a sua carteira se perder o seu telemóvel e a sua Chave de Papel, por isso tome nota da sua Chave de Papel e mantenha-a bem protegida!</p>\n<h3>Impressão Digital / Touch ID</h3>\n<p>Apesar de ser necessário o PIN de 6 dígitos para proteger a sua carteira, pode também usar o leitor de impressões digitais do seu dispositivo para maior conveniência e segurança. Usar a sua impressão digital é mais rápido do que introduzir um PIN e se alguém estiver a vê-lo desbloquear a sua carteira, não conseguirá descobrir o seu PIN.</p>\n<p>Esta opção irá aparecer apenas se o seu dispositivo tiver um leitor de impressões digitais.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:20Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:39Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002803493,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Wat is het beveiligingscentrum?",body:"<p>Het beveiligingscentrum staat het toe dat er meerdere beveiligingsopties voor je Bread gebruikt worden.</p>\n<h3>6-cijferige PIN</h3>\n<p>Deze PIN wordt gebruikt om je portemonnee te openen en geld te verzenden. Het zorgt ervoor dat anderen niet bij je Bread kunnen komen wanneer je je telefoon uitleent.</p>\n<h3>Papiersleutel</h3>\n<p>Als je ooit je telefoon verliest of upgradet, heb je je Papiersleutel nodig om je portemonnee te herstellen op een ander apparaat. Het is niet mogelijk om je portemonnee te herstellen als je je telefoon én je Papiersleutel verliest, dus schrijf deze Papiersleutel op en bewaar hem goed!</p>\n<h3> Vingerprint/Touch ID</h3>\n<p> Hoewel de 6-cijferige PIN nodig is om je portemonnee te beveiligen, kun je ook de vingerafdrukscanner van je apparaat gebruiken. Het gebruik van je vingerafdruk is sneller dan het invoeren van een PIN, en als mensen kijken terwijl jij je portemonnee opent, zullen ze niet zien wat je PIN is.</p>\n<p>Deze optie zal alleen te zien zijn wanneer je telefoon een vingerafdrukscanner heeft.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:20Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:39Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002791974,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Что такое центр безопасности?",body:"<p>В центре безопасности вы можете настроить дополнительные функции безопасности для своего кошелька Bread.</p>\n<h3>ПИН-код из 6-ти цифр</h3>\n<p>Этот ПИН-код нужен, чтобы разблокировать ваш кошелек и отправлять деньги. Он не дает другим людям получить доступ к Bread, если вы позволите кому-нибудь воспользоваться своим телефоном.</p>\n<h3>Бумажный ключ</h3>\n<p>Если вы потеряете или обновите свой телефон, то вам понадобится бумажный ключ, чтобы восстановить свой кошелек на другом устройстве. Если вы потеряете и телефон, и бумажный ключ, то восстановить кошелек будет невозможно, поэтому запишите свой бумажный ключ и храните его в безопасном месте!</p>\n<h3>Отпечаток пальца / Touch ID</h3>\n<p>Для защиты кошелька можно использовать не только ПИН-код из 6-ти цифр, но и сканер отпечатка пальца вашего телефона – для дополнительной защиты и удобства. Отсканировать отпечаток пальца быстрее, чем ввести ПИН-код, и если во время разблокировки кошелька за вами кто-то наблюдает, то он не сможет увидеть ваш ПИН-код.</p>\n<p>Эта опция появится только если на вашем устройстве есть сканер отпечатка пальца.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:20Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:39Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002803513,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Vad är säkerhetscentralen?",body:"<p>Säkerhetscentralen låter dig hantera ytterligare säkerhetsfunktioner för din Bread.</p>\n<h3>6-siffrig PIN</h3>\n<p>Den här PIN-koden används för att låsa upp din plånbok och skicka pengar. Den hindrar andra från att komma åt din Bread om du låter någon annan använda din telefon.</p>\n<h3>Pappersnyckel</h3>\n<p>Om du någonsin förlorar eller uppgraderar telefonen behöver du din pappersnyckel för att återställa din plånbok på en annan enhet. Det går inte att återställa din plånbok om du förlorar både din telefon och pappersnyckel, så skriv ner din pappersnyckel och håll den skyddad!</p>\n<h3>Fingeravtryck/Touch ID</h3>\n<p>Den 6-siffriga PIN-koden är nödvändig för att skydda din plånbok, men du kan även använda din fingeravtrycksläsare för ökad bekvämlighet och säkerhet. Att använda fingeravtryck är snabbare än att ange en PIN-kod och om någon ser dig låsa upp din plånbok kan de inte se vad din PIN-kod är.</p>\n<p>Det här alternativet visas endast om enheten har en fingeravtrycksläsare.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:20Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:39Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002791934,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"セキュリティセンターとは?",body:"<p>セキュリティセンターではあなたのBreadへの更なるセキュリティ対策を管理することができます。</p>\n<h3>6桁の暗証番号</h3>\n<p>この暗証番号はあなたのウォレットのロック解除をする為に使用されます。暗証番号はあなたの携帯電話が誰かに利用された場合にBreadへのアクセスを制御します。</p>\n<h3>ペーパーキー</h3>\n<p>携帯電話を失くしてしまったり、アップグレードした場合にウォレットを復元させるためにはペーパーキーが必要となります。携帯電話とペーパーキー両方を紛失してしまった場合にはウォレットを復元することが不可能となります。その為、ペーパーキーを書き留めて安全に保管しておきましょう!</p>\n<h3>指紋認証 / Touch ID</h3>\n<p>6桁の暗証番号がウォレットを安全に保管するために必要である一方で、利便性と更なるセキュリティ強化の為にお手持ちのデバイスの指紋認証リーダーを利用することもできます。指紋認証は暗証番号を入力するよりも速く行うことができ、誰かがあなたがウォレットのロック解除をしているのを目撃しても暗証番号が知られてしまうことはありません。</p>\n<p>このオプションはお手持ちのデバイスに指紋認証リーダーが搭載されている場合にのみ表示されます。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:20Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:38Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002791874,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Qué es el centro de seguridad?",body:"<p>El Centro de seguridad te permite administrar las funciones de seguridad adicionales para tu Bread.</p>\n<h3>PIN de 6 dígitos</h3>\n<p>Este PIN se utiliza para desbloquear tu monedero y enviar dinero. Evita que otras personas accedan a tu Bread en caso de que dejes utilizar tu teléfono a otra persona.</p>\n<h3>Clave de papel</h3>\n<p>Si pierdes o actualizas tu teléfono, necesitarás la clave de papel para restaurar tu monedero en otro dispositivo. No es posible recuperar el monedero si pierdes tanto tu teléfono como la clave de papel, ¡así que apunta la clave de papel y mantenla en un sitio seguro!</p>\n<h3>Identificación de huellas dactilares/identificación táctil</h3>\n<p>Aunque el PIN de 6 dígitos es necesario para mantener tu monedero seguro, también puedes usar el lector de huellas dactilares de tu dispositivo para mayor comodidad y seguridad. El uso de la huella digital es más rápido que tener que introducir un PIN y si la gente te está viendo desbloquear el monedero, no podrá ver tu PIN.</p>\n<p>Esta opción solo aparecerá si tu dispositivo tiene un lector de huellas dactilares.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:19Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:38Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002791894,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Qu'est-ce que le centre de sécurité ?",body:"<p>Le centre de sécurité vous permet de gérer des fonctionnalités de sécurité supplémentaires pour votre Bread.</p>\n<h3>Code à 6 chiffres</h3>\n<p>Ce code est utilisé pour déverrouiller votre portefeuille et envoyer de l'argent. Il empêche d'autres personnes d'accéder à votre Bread si vous laissez quelqu'un utiliser votre téléphone.</p>\n<h3>Clé papier</h3>\n<p>Si vous perdez ou changez votre téléphone, vous aurez besoin de votre clé papier pour restaurer votre portefeuille sur un autre appareil. Il n'est pas possible de récupérer votre portefeuille si vous perdez votre téléphone et votre clé papier, alors écrivez votre clé papier et gardez-la en sécurité !</p>\n<h3>Empreinte digitale / Touch ID</h3>\n<p>Bien que le code à 6 chiffres soit requis pour sécuriser votre portefeuille, vous pouvez aussi utiliser le lecteur d'empreinte digitale de votre appareil pour plus de praticité et de sécurité. Il est plus rapide d'utiliser votre empreinte digitale que de saisir un code, et si quelqu'un vous observe lors du déverrouillage du portefeuille, il ne pourra pas voir votre code.</p>\n<p>Cette option apparaîtra uniquement si votre appareil dispose d'un lecteur d'empreinte digitale.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:19Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:38Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002791914,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Cos'è il centro di sicurezza?",body:"<p>Il Centro di Sicurezza ti permette di gestire tutte le funzionalità di sicurezza del tuo Bread.</p>\n<h3>PIN a 6 cifre</h3>\n<p>Con questo PIN potrai sbloccare il tuo portafoglio e inviare denaro. Impedirà l'accesso a Bread da parte di altre persone, anche quando presti il tuo telefono.</p>\n<h3>Chiave Cartacea</h3>\n<p>Se decidi di cambiare il telefono o lo smarrisci, dovrai usare la tua Chiave Cartacea per ripristinare il tuo portafoglio su un nuovo dispositivo. Se smarrisci il telefono e la Chiave Cartacea non potrai più ripristinare il tuo portafoglio, quindi prendi nota della Chiave Cartacea e tienila al sicuro!</p>\n<h3>Impronta digitale / Touch ID</h3>\n<p>Il PIN a 6 cifre ti servirà per tenere al sicuro il tuo portafoglio, ma potrai migliorarne la comodità e sicurezza usando il lettore di impronte del tuo dispositivo. Con la tua impronta digitale potrai accedere in maniera più veloce rispetto al PIN, e se qualcuno ti osserva non potrà identificare il tuo PIN.</p>\n<p>Questa opzione sarà disponibile solo su dispositivi con un lettore di impronte digitali.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:19Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:38Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002803473,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Was ist das Sicherheitscenter?",body:"<p>Das Sicherheitscenter ermöglicht es Ihnen, zusätzliche Sicherheits-Features für Ihr Bread zu managen.</p>\n<h3>6-stellige PIN</h3>\n<p>Die PIN wird dazu verwendet, Ihre Geldbörse zu entsperren und Geld zu versenden. Falls Sie jemand anderen Ihr Handy benutzen lassen, hält sie Andere davon ab, auf Ihr Bread zuzugreifen.</p>\n<h3>Paper Key</h3>\n<p>Falls Sie Ihr Handy jemals verlieren oder durch ein neueres ersetzen, brauchen Sie den Paper Key, um Ihre Geldbörse auf einem anderen Gerät wiederherzustellen. Falls Sie sowohl Ihr Telefon als auch Ihren Paper Key verlieren, ist es nicht möglich, Ihre Geldbörse wiederzuerlangen, notieren Sie also Ihren Paper Key und bewahren Sie ihn gut auf!</p>\n<h3>Fingerabdruck / Touch ID</h3>\n<p>Während die 6-stellige PIN erforderlich ist, um Ihre Geldbörse zu sichern, können Sie der Einfachheit halber und für zusätzliche Sicherheit auch den Fingerabdruckleser Ihres Geräts verwenden. Die Verwendung Ihres Fingerabdrucks geht schneller als die PIN-Eingabe und falls jemand dabei zusieht, wie Sie Ihre Geldbörse entsperren, kann diese Person Ihre PIN nicht sehen.</p>\n<p>Diese Option erscheint nur, wenn Ihr Gerät über einen Fingerabdruckleser verfügt.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:18Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:37Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002803453,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvad er sikkerhedscentret?",body:"<p> Sikkerhedscenteret giver dig mulighed for at administrere yderligere sikkerhedsfunktioner for din Bread-konto. </p>\n<h3>6-cifret PIN</h3>\n<p> Denne PIN-kode bruges til at låse din tegnebog op og sende penge. Den forhindrer andre mennesker i at få adgang til din Bread-konto, hvis du lader andre bruge din telefon.</p>\n<h3>Papirnøgle</h3>\n<p>Hvis du mister eller opgraderer din telefon, skal du have din papirnøgle for at gendanne din tegnebog på en anden enhed. Det er ikke muligt at gendanne din tegnebog, hvis du mister både din telefon og papirnøglen, så skriv din papirnøgle ned og gem den et sikkert sted!</p>\n<h3>Fingeraftryk/Touch-ID</h3>\n<p>Mens den 6-cifrede PIN-kode er nødvendig for at sikre din tegnebog, kan du også bruge enhedens fingeraftrykslæser for nemhedens skyld og som ekstra sikkerhed. Brug af dit fingeraftryk er hurtigere end at indtaste en pinkode, og hvis folk kigger dig over skulderen når du låser din tegnebog op, kan de ikke se, hvad din pinkode er.</p>\n<p> Denne indstilling vises kun, hvis din enhed har en fingeraftrykslæser.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:18Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:37Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001214774,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000749354/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000749354",source_id:115000749354,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"What is the security center?",body:"<p>The Security Center allows you to manage additional security features for your Bread.</p>\n<h3>6-digit PIN</h3>\n<p>This PIN is used to unlock your wallet and send money. It prevents other people from accessing your Bread in case you let someone else use your phone.</p>\n<h3>Paper key</h3>\n<p>If you ever lose or upgrade your phone, you will need your Paper Key to restore your wallet on another device. It is not possible to recover your wallet if you lose both your phone and Paper Key, so write down your Paper Key and keep it safe!</p>\n<h3>Fingerprint / Touch ID</h3>\n<p>While the 6-digit PIN is required to secure your wallet, you can also use your device's fingerprint reader for convenience and added security. Using your fingerprint is quicker than entering a PIN, and if people are watching you unlock your wallet they won't be able to see what your PIN is.</p>\n<p>This option will only appear if your device has a fingerprint reader.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T00:11:43Z",updated_at:"2017-08-29T01:19:23Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000763694,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000763694-How-do-I-recover-my-wallet-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763694-How-do-I-recover-my-wallet-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:16:30Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:39Z",name:"How do I recover my wallet?",title:"How do I recover my wallet?",body:'<p>Every time you create a new wallet with Bread, you are provided with a "Paper Key," which is a list of 12 words that can be used to restore access to your wallet if you ever lose or upgrade your phone. Your wallet exists only on your phone, and the Paper Key is the only way to restore your wallet if you lose your phone.</p>\n<p>To recover your wallet, enter the 12 words, in order, from your Paper Key. </p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:recover-wallet"],locales:{"zh-cn":{id:115002791854,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何恢复我的钱包？",body:"<p>每次您通过 Bread 新建一个钱包，您都会获得一个包含一组 12 个词的“纸钥匙”，如果手机丢失或升级，可用它恢复钱包访问权限。您的钱包仅存于您的手机中，如果您手机丢失，纸钥匙是恢复您钱包的唯一途径。</p>\n<p>若要恢复您的钱包，请依序输入纸钥匙包含的 12 个词。 </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:18Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:37Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-tw":{id:115002803433,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何復原錢包？",body:"<p>每次你在 Bread 上創建新的錢包，將會收到「紙金鑰」，這是一串 12 字的清單，可在手機遺失或升級時用來重建錢包的存取權限。你的錢包只存在於你的手機上，紙金鑰是在遺失手機時唯一一個還原錢包的方式。</p>\n<p>如要復原你的錢包，依序輸入紙金鑰上的 12 個單字。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:18Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:37Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002791794,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe herstel ik mijn portemonnee?",body:"<p>Telkens wanneer je een nieuwe portemonnee met Bread maakt, krijg je een Papiersleutel. Dit is een lijst van 12 woorden die gebruikt kunnen worden om de toegang tot je portemonnee te herstellen als je ooit je telefoon verliest of upgradet.  Je portemonnee bestaat alleen op je telefoon, en je Papiersleutel is de enige manier waarop je je portemonnee kunt herstellen als je je telefoon verliest.</p>\n<p>Om je portemonnee te herstellen, voer je de 12 woorden op volgorde in, van je Papiersleutel.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:17Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:36Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002791814,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como recupero a minha carteira?",body:'<p>Sempre que cria uma nova carteira com o Bread, é-lhe fornecida uma "Chave de Papel", que é uma lista de 12 palavras que pode ser usada para restaurar o acesso à sua carteira se perder ou trocar de telemóvel. A sua carteira existe apenas no seu telemóvel e a Chave de Papel é a única forma de restaurar a sua carteira se perder o seu telemóvel.</p>\n<p>Para recuperar a sua carteira, introduza as 12 palavras,\n por ordem, da sua Chave de Papel. </p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:17Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:36Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002791834,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur återställer jag min plånbok?",body:'<p>Varje gång du skapar en ny plånbok med Bread, får du en "pappersnyckel", vilket är en lista med 12 ord som kan användas för att återställa åtkomst till din plånbok om du någonsin förlorar eller uppgraderar din telefon. Din plånbok existerar endast på din telefon, och pappersnyckeln är det enda sättet att återställa din plånbok om du förlorar din telefon.</p>\n<p>Ange de 12 orden från din pappersnyckel, i ordning, för att återställa din plånbok.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:17Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:36Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002803413,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как мне восстановить свой кошелек?",body:"<p>Каждый раз при создании нового кошелька в Bread вы получаете бумажный ключ из 12-ти слов, которые можно использовать для восстановления доступа к вашему кошельку, если по потеряете свой телефон или замените его на новый. Ваш кошелек существует только на вашем телефоне, и бумажный ключ – единственный способ восстановить кошелек, если вы потеряли свой телефон.</p>\n<p>Чтобы восстановить кошелек, введите 12 слов из вашего бумажного кошелька в верном порядке. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:17Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:36Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002791754,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je récupérer mon portefeuille ?",body:"<p>À chaque fois que vous créez un nouveau portefeuille avec Bread, vous recevez une « clé papier ». Il s'agit d'une liste de 12 mots qui peut être utilisée pour restaurer l'accès à votre portefeuille si vous perdez ou changez votre téléphone. Votre portefeuille n'existe que sur votre téléphone, et la clé papier est le seul moyen de restaurer votre portefeuille si vous perdez votre téléphone.</p>\n<p>Pour récupérer votre portefeuille, entrez les 12 mots de votre clé papier dans l'ordre. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:16Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:35Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002791774,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come faccio a recuperare il mio portafoglio?",body:"<p>Ogni volta che userai Bread per creare un nuovo portafoglio, ti verrà fornita una \"Chiave Cartacea\", cioè un elenco di 12 parole che potrai usare per ripristinare l'accesso al tuo portafoglio quando cambi o smarrisci il tuo telefono. Il tuo portafoglio esiste solo ed esclusivamente nel tuo telefono e, se perdi il telefono, la Chiave Cartacea è l'unico strumento per ripristinare il portafoglio.</p>\n<p>Per ripristinare il tuo portafoglio, inserisci le 12 parole, nell'ordine corretto, contenute nella tua Chiave Cartacea. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:16Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:35Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002803373,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo recupero mi monedero?",body:'<p>Cada vez que creas un monedero nuevo con Bread se te proporciona una "clave de papel" que es una lista de 12 palabras que se pueden utilizar para restaurar el acceso a tu monedero si alguna vez pierdes o actualizas tu teléfono. El monedero solo existe en tu teléfono y la clave de papel es la única manera de restaurarlo si pierdes tu teléfono.</p>\n<p>Para recuperar tu monedero, introduce las 12 palabras, en orden, de tu clave de papel.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:16Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:35Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002803393,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ウォレットを復元させる方法は?",body:"<p>Breadで新しいウォレットを作成する度に、12単語のリストから形成される「ペーパーキー」が提供されます。ペーパーキーはあなたの携帯電話を紛失してしまったり、アップグレードした場合にウォレットへのアクセスを復元する為に使用されます。あなたのウォレットはお手持ちの携帯電話上のみに存在し、携帯電話を紛失してしまった場合にはペーパーキーがあなたのウォレットを復元する為の唯一の方法となります。</p>\n<p>ウォレットを復元させる為には、ペーパーキーの12単語を正しい順番に入力してください。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:16Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:36Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002791734,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan gendanner jeg min tegnebog?",body:'<p> Hver gang du opretter en ny tegnebog med Bread, får du en "papirnøgle", som er en liste på 12 ord, der kan bruges til at gendanne adgangen til din tegnebog, hvis du nogensinde mister eller opgraderer din telefon. Din tegnebog findes kun på din telefon, og papirnøglen er den eneste måde at gendanne din tegnebog på, hvis du mister din telefon.</p>\n<p> For at gendanne din tegnebog skal du indtaste de 12 ord, i rækkefølge, fra din papirnøgle.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:15Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:35Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002803353,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie kann ich meine Geldbörse wiederherstellen?",body:"<p>Jedes Mal, wenn Sie mit Bread eine neue Geldbörse erstellen, wird Ihnen ein „Paper Key“ zugeteilt, der aus einer Liste von 12 Wörtern besteht und dazu verwendet werden kann, auf Ihre Geldbörse zuzugreifen, sollten Sie jemals Ihr Handy verlieren oder ersetzen. Ihre Geldbörse existiert ausschließlich auf Ihrem Handy und nur mit dem Paper Key können Sie Ihre Geldbörse wiederherstellen, falls Sie Ihr Handy verlieren.</p>\n<p>Geben Sie die 12 Wörter aus Ihrem Paper Key in der richtigen Reihenfolge ein, um Ihre Geldbörse wiederherzustellen. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:15Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:35Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001236974,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763694/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763694",source_id:115000763694,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How do I recover my wallet?",body:'<p>Every time you create a new wallet with Bread, you are provided with a "Paper Key," which is a list of 12 words that can be used to restore access to your wallet if you ever lose or upgrade your phone. Your wallet exists only on your phone, and the Paper Key is the only way to restore your wallet if you lose your phone.</p>\n<p>To recover your wallet, enter the 12 words, in order, from your Paper Key. </p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:16:30Z",updated_at:"2017-07-22T22:48:08Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000763654,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000763654-How-do-I-reset-my-PIN-with-my-paper-key-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763654-How-do-I-reset-my-PIN-with-my-paper-key-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:37Z",name:"How do I reset my PIN with my paper key?",title:"How do I reset my PIN with my paper key?",body:'<p>Every time you create a new wallet with Bread, you are provided with a "Paper Key," which is a list of 12 words that can be used to restore access to your wallet if you ever lose or upgrade your phone. You can also use your Paper Key to reset your wallet PIN if you forget it.</p>\n<p>Enter the 12 words from your Paper Key, in order, and you will be able to choose a new PIN.</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:reset-pin-paper-key"],locales:{"zh-cn":{id:115002791714,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何使用我的纸钥匙重置 PIN 码？",body:"<p>每次您通过 Bread 新建一个钱包，您都会获得一个包含一组 12 个词的“纸钥匙”，如果手机丢失或升级，可用它恢复钱包访问权限。您还可以在忘记钱包 PIN 码后使用纸钥匙重置 PIN 码。</p>\n<p>依序输入纸钥匙包含的 12 个词，您就能选择一个新的 PIN 码。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:15Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:34Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-tw":{id:115002803333,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何使用紙金鑰重設 PIN 碼？",body:"<p>每次你在 Bread 上創建新的錢包，將會收到「紙金鑰」，這是一串 12 字的清單，可在手機遺失或升級時用來重建錢包的存取權限。你也可在遺忘錢包 PIN 馬時使用紙金鑰來重設。</p>\n<p>依照順序輸入紙金鑰上的 12 個單字，即可選擇新 PIN 碼。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:15Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:34Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002791694,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как мне сбросить свой ПИН-код при помощи бумажного ключа?",body:"<p>Каждый раз при создании нового кошелька в Bread вы получаете бумажный ключ из 12-ти слов, которые можно использовать для восстановления доступа к вашему кошельку, если вы потеряете свой телефон или замените его на новый. Вы также можете использовать бумажный ключ, чтобы сбросить ПИН-код своего кошелька, если вы забудете его.</p>\n<p>Введите 12 слов из вашего бумажного кошелька в верном порядке, и вы сможете выбрать новый ПИН-код.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:14Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:34Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002803293,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe reset ik mijn PIN met mijn papiersleutel?",body:'<p>Telkens wanneer je een nieuwe portemonnee met Bread aanmaakt, krijg je een "Papiersleutel", wat een lijst is van 12 woorden die je kunt gebruiken om de toegang tot je portemonnee te herstellen als je ooit je telefoon verliest of upgradet. Je kunt je papiersleutel ook gebruiken om je PIN van je portemonnee te resetten als je deze vergeet.</p>\n<p>Voer de 12 woorden van je papiersleutel in, op volgorde, en dan kan je een nieuwe PIN kiezen.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:14Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002803313,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur återställer jag min PIN med min pappersnyckel?",body:'<p>Varje gång du skapar en ny plånbok med Bread, får du en "pappersnyckel", vilket är en lista med 12 ord som kan användas för att återställa åtkomst till din plånbok om du någonsin förlorar eller uppgraderar din telefon. Du kan även använda din pappersnyckel för att återställa PIN-koden för din plånbok om du glömmer den.</p>\n<p>Ange de 12 orden från din pappersnyckel, i ordning, och du kommer att kunna välja en ny PIN-kod.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:14Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:34Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002791674,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como repor o meu PIN com a minha chave de papel?",body:'<p>Sempre que cria uma nova carteira com o Bread, é-lhe fornecida uma "Chave de Papel", que é uma lista de 12 palavras que pode ser usada para restaurar o acesso à sua carteira se perder ou trocar de telemóvel. Pode também usar a sua Chave de Papel para repor o PIN da sua carteira se o esquecer.</p>\n<p>Introduza as 12 palavras da sua Chave de Papel, por ordem, e poderá escolher um novo PIN.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:14Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002803273,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo puedo restablecer el PIN con la clave de papel?",body:'<p>Cada vez que creas una cartera nueva con Bread, se te proporciona una "clave de papel" que es una lista de 12 palabras que se pueden utilizar para restaurar el acceso al monedero si alguna vez pierdes o actualizas tu teléfono. También puedes usar la clave de papel para restablecer el PIN del monedero si se te olvida.</p>\n<p>Introduce las 12 palabras de tu clave de papel, en orden, y podrás elegir un nuevo PIN.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:13Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:32Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002791614,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je réinitialiser mon code avec ma clé papier ?",body:"<p>À chaque fois que vous créez un nouveau portefeuille avec Bread, vous recevez une « clé papier ». Il s'agit d'une liste de 12 mots qui peut être utilisée pour restaurer l'accès à votre portefeuille si vous perdez ou changez votre téléphone. Vous pouvez aussi utiliser votre clé papier pour réinitialiser le code de votre portefeuille si vous l'oubliez.</p>\n<p>Entrez les 12 mots de votre clé papier dans l'ordre et vous pourrez choisir un nouveau code.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:13Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002791634,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come faccio a ripristinare il mio PIN usando la mia Chiave Cartacea?",body:"<p>Ogni volta che userai Bread per creare un nuovo portafoglio, ti verrà fornita una \"Chiave Cartacea\", cioè un elenco di 12 parole che potrai usare per ripristinare l'accesso al tuo portafoglio quando cambi o smarrisci il tuo telefono. Inoltre, potrai usare la tua Chiave Cartacea per ripristinare il PIN del tuo portafoglio nel caso lo dimenticassi.</p>\n<p>Ti basterà inserire le 12 parole della tua Chiave Cartacea, nell'ordine giusto, per creare un nuovo PIN.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:13Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002791654,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ペーパーキーを使用して暗証番号をリセットする方法は?",body:"<p>Breadで新しいウォレットを作成する度に、12単語のリストから形成される「ペーパーキー」が提供されます。ペーパーキーはあなたの携帯電話を紛失してしまったり、アップグレードした場合にウォレットへのアクセスを復元する為に使用されます。</p>\n<p>ペーパーキーの12単語を正しい順番に入力すると、新しい暗証番号を設定することができます。\n</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:13Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002803253,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan nulstiller jeg min pinkode med min papirnøgle?",body:'<p>Hver gang du opretter en ny tegnebog med Bread, får du en "papirnøgle", som er en liste på  12 ord, der kan bruges til at gendanne adgangen til din tegnebog, hvis du nogensinde mister eller opgraderer din telefon. Du kan også bruge din papirnøgle til at nulstille din tegnebogspinkode, hvis du glemmer den.</p>\n<p> Indtast de 12 ord fra din papirnøgle, i rækkefølge, derefter kan du vælge en ny pinkode.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:12Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:32Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002791594,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie kann ich meine PIN mit meinem Paper Key zurücksetzen?",body:"<p>Jedes Mal, wenn Sie mit Bread eine neue Geldbörse erstellen, wird Ihnen ein „Paper Key“ zugeteilt, welcher aus einer Liste von 12 Wörtern besteht und dazu verwendet werden kann, auf Ihre Geldbörse zuzugreifen, falls Sie jemals Ihr Telefon verlieren oder ersetzen. Mit Ihrem Paper Key können Sie auch Ihre Geldbörsen-PIN zurücksetzen, falls Sie sie vergessen.\n</p>\n<p>Geben Sie die 12 Wörter aus Ihrem Paper Key in der richtigen Reihenfolge ein und Sie können eine neue PIN festlegen.\n</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:12Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:32Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001236934,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763654/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763654",source_id:115000763654,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How do I reset my PIN with my paper key?",body:'<p>Every time you create a new wallet with Bread, you are provided with a "Paper Key," which is a list of 12 words that can be used to restore access to your wallet if you ever lose or upgrade your phone. You can also use your Paper Key to reset your wallet PIN if you forget it.</p>\n<p>Enter the 12 words from your Paper Key, in order, and you will be able to choose a new PIN.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:04Z",updated_at:"2017-07-23T00:01:56Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000757753,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000757753-Why-do-I-need-a-PIN-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757753-Why-do-I-need-a-PIN-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:06Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:34Z",name:"Why do I need a PIN?",title:"Why do I need a PIN?",body:"<p>Bread requires you to set a PIN to secure your wallet, separate from your device passcode. You will be required to enter this PIN to view your balance or send money, which keeps your wallet private even if you let someone use your phone or if your phone is stolen by someone who knows your device passcode.</p>\n<p><strong>Do not forget your wallet PIN!</strong> It can only be reset by using your Paper Key. If you forget your PIN and lose your Paper Key, your wallet will be lost.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:set-pin"],locales:{"zh-cn":{id:115002803233,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我为什么需要 PIN 码？",body:"<p>Bread 要求您在设备密码之外，单独设置一个 PIN 码以保护您的钱包。您必须输入此 PIN 码后才能够查看您的余额或付款，如此，即使您让别人使用您的手机，或者您的手机被某个知道您设备密码的人窃取，您的钱包依然安全无虞。</p>\n<p><strong>切勿忘记您的钱包 PIN 码！</strong>它只能用您的纸钥匙重置。如果您忘记了 PIN 码而且丢失了您的纸钥匙，您的钱包也将随之遗失。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:12Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:31Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-tw":{id:115002791574,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"為何我需要 PIN 碼？",body:"<p>Bread 要求你在裝置密碼之外設定 PIN 碼來保護你的錢包。當你要瀏覽餘額或發送款項時，需要輸入此 PIN 碼，這樣一來即可保障你錢包的私密性，以防有知道裝置密碼的人使用或偷了你的手機。</p>\n<p><strong>別忘記你的錢包 PIN 碼！</strong>它只能使用你的紙金鑰重新設定。如果你忘記了 PIN 碼又遺失了你的紙金鑰，你的錢包將無法使用。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:12Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:32Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002791494,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Waarom heb ik een PIN nodig?",body:"<p>Bread vraagt jou om om een PIN in te stellen om je portemonnee te beveiligen, apart van je wachtwoord voor je apparaat. Je moet deze PIN invoeren wanneer je je saldo wilt bekijken of geld wilt versturen, waardoor je je portemonnee privé houdt, zelfs wanneer je je telefoon uitleent of wanneer deze gestolen wordt door iemand die jouw wachtwoord kent.</p>\n<p><strong>Vergeet niet je PIN van je portemonnee!</strong> Hij kan alleen gereset worden door je Papiersleutel. Als je je PIN vergeet en je je Papiersleutel verliest, is je portemonnee verloren.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:11Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:31Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002791514,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Porque preciso de um PIN?",body:"<p>O Bread requer que defina um PIN para proteger a sua carteira, separadamente do código do seu dispositivo. Ser-lhe-á solicitado que introduza este PIN para ver o seu saldo ou enviar dinheiro, o que mantém a sua carteira privada mesmo que deixe alguém usar o seu telefone ou se o mesmo for roubado por alguém que sabe o código do seu dispositivo.</p>\n<p><strong>Não se esqueça do PIN da sua carteira!</strong> Apenas pode ser reposto usando a sua Chave de Papel. Se se esquecer do seu PIN e perder a sua Chave de Papel, a sua carteira será perdida.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:11Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:31Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002791534,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Зачем нужен ПИН-код?",body:"<p>Bread требует, чтобы вы установили ПИН-код для защиты своего кошелька, который бы отличался от кода для доступа к вашему устройству. Этот ПИН-код необходимо ввести, чтобы посмотреть баланс или отправить деньги, так что ваш кошелек будет в безопасности, даже если вы дадите кому-нибудь воспользоваться своим телефоном или же если телефон украдет кто-то, кто знает код доступа.</p>\n<p><strong>Не забудьте ПИН-код от кошелька!</strong> Его можно сбросить лишь используя ваш бумажный ключ. Если вы забудете ПИН-код и потеряете свой бумажный ключ, то ваш кошелек будет потерян.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:11Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:31Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002791554,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Varför behöver jag en PIN?",body:"<p>Bred kräver att du anger en PIN-kod, som skiljer sig från din koden till din enhet, för att skydda din plånbok. Du kommer att behöva ange denna PIN-kod för att se ditt saldo eller skicka pengar, vilket säkerställer att din plånbok är privat även om du låter någon använda din telefon eller om telefonen stulits av någon som känner till din koden till din enhet.</p>\n<p> <strong>Glöm inte din plånboks-PIN!</strong> Den kan endast återställas med hjälp av din pappersnyckel. Om du glömmer din PIN-kod och förlorar din pappersnyckel kommer din plånbok att gå förlorad.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:11Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:31Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002803213,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Perché mi serve un PIN?",body:"<p>Bread ti chiederà di creare un PIN (diverso dal codice di sblocco del tuo dispositivo) per proteggere il tuo portafoglio. Ogni volta che vorrai controllare il saldo o inviare denaro dovrai inserire il PIN, così il portafoglio rimarrà privato anche se presti il tuo telefono ad altre persone o se ti viene rubato da qualcuno che conosce il tuo codice di sblocco.</p>\n<p><strong>Non dimenticare il PIN del tuo portafoglio!</strong> Potrai ripristinarlo solo usando la tua Chiave Cartacea. Se dimentichi il PIN e smarrisci la Chiave Cartacea, non potrai più accedere al tuo portafoglio.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:10Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:30Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002791454,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Pourquoi ai-je besoin d'un code ?",body:"<p>Bread vous demande de définir un code pour sécuriser votre portefeuille, différent du mot de passe de votre appareil. Ce code vous sera demandé pour voir votre solde ou envoyer de l'argent, ce qui permet de protéger la confidentialité du portefeuille même lorsqu'une autre personne utilise votre téléphone ou si votre téléphone est volé par une personne qui connaît le mot de passe de votre appareil.</p>\n<p><strong>N'oubliez pas le code de votre portefeuille !</strong> Il pourra seulement être réinitialisé à l'aide de votre clé papier. Si vous oubliez votre code et perdez votre clé papier, votre portefeuille sera perdu.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:10Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:30Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002791474,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"なぜ暗証番号が必要なのでしょうか?",body:"<p>Breadではウォレットを安全に保管する為に暗証番号を設定する必要があります。口座を閲覧したり、送金を行う為にはこの暗証番号を入力しなければなりません。こうすることで、あなたの携帯電話のパスコードを知っている人にデバイスを貸したり、盗まれたりしてもウォレットは機密に保管されます。</p>\n<p><strong>ウォレットの暗証番号を忘れないように!</strong> ウォレットの暗証番号はペーパーキーを使用してのみリセットをすることが可能です。暗証番号を忘れてしまったり、ペーパーキーを紛失してしまったばあいには、ウォレットにアクセスすることが出来なくなります。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:10Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:30Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002803193,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Por qué necesito un PIN?",body:"<p>Bread requiere que establezcas un número PIN para proteger tu monedero, diferente del código de acceso a tu dispositivo. Se te pedirá que introduzcas este código para ver tu saldo o enviar dinero, lo que asegura la privacidad de tu monedero, incluso si permites que alguien use tu teléfono o si te lo roba alguien que conozca el código de acceso a tu dispositivo.</p>\n<p> <strong>¡No te olvides del PIN de tu monedero!</strong> Solo se puede restablecer con la clave en papel. Si olvidas tu PIN y pierdes la clave en papel, tu monedero se perderá.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:10Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:30Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002791434,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvorfor skal jeg have en PIN-kode?",body:"<p>Bread kræver at du angiver en PIN-kode, som skal være særskilt fra din enheds adgangskode, for at sikre din tegnebog. Du bliver bedt om at indtaste denne pinkode for at få vist din saldo og for at sende penge, hvilket gør din tegnebog privat, selvom du lader nogen bruge din telefon, eller hvis din telefon bliver stjålet af en, der kender din adgangskode til din enhed.</p>\n<p> <strong>Glem ikke din tegnebogskode!</strong> Den kan kun nulstilles ved hjælp af din papirnøgle. Hvis du glemmer din PIN-kode og mister din papirnøgle, vil din tegnebog gå tabt.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:09Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:29Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002803173,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wieso benötige ich eine PIN?",body:"<p>Bread erfordert das Festlegen einer PIN zur Sicherung Ihrer Geldbörse, unabhängig vom Zugangscode Ihres Geräts. Sie müssen diese PIN eingeben, um Ihren Kontostand einzusehen oder Geld zu versenden, sodass Ihre Geldbörse vertraulich bleibt, auch, wenn Sie jemand anderen Ihr Handy benutzen lassen oder falls Ihr Handy von jemandem gestohlen wird, der den Zugangscode zu Ihrem Gerät kennt.</p>\n<p><strong>Vergessen Sie Ihre Geldbörsen-PIN nicht!</strong> Sie kann nur unter Verwendung Ihres Paper Key zurückgesetzt werden. Falls Sie Ihre PIN vergessen und Ihren Paper Key verlieren, ist Ihre Geldbörse verloren.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:09Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:29Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001226653,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757753/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757753",source_id:115000757753,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"Why do I need a PIN?",body:"<p>Bread requires you to set a PIN to secure your wallet, separate from your device passcode. You will be required to enter this PIN to view your balance or send money, which keeps your wallet private even if you let someone use your phone or if your phone is stolen by someone who knows your device passcode.</p>\n<p><strong>Do not forget your wallet PIN!</strong> It can only be reset by using your Paper Key. If you forget your PIN and lose your Paper Key, your wallet will be lost.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:06Z",updated_at:"2017-07-23T00:17:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000757793,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000757793-Why-do-I-need-to-write-down-my-paper-key-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757793-Why-do-I-need-to-write-down-my-paper-key-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:08Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:29Z",name:"Why do I need to write down my paper key?",title:"Why do I need to write down my paper key?",body:'<p>Your Bread connects directly to the bitcoin network, where your wallet is stored. The "keys" to access your wallet are securely stored in your phone and nowhere else. Bread will provide you with a unique "Paper Key," which is a list of 12-words which can be used to recreate the keys to your wallet. If you ever lose or upgrade your phone, this "Paper Key" is required to regain access to your bitcoin.</p>\n<p>Please write down each word, in order, on a piece of paper. We recommend storing your Paper Key in a safe, safety deposit box at a bank, or wherever you might keep passports, birth certificates, or other important documents. Anyone who has your Paper Key can access your money, even if they don\'t have your wallet PIN, so keep it private and don\'t show it to others!</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:write-phrase"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002803013,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"為何我需要寫下自己的紙金鑰？",body:"<p>你的 Bread 直接與比特幣網路連接，你的錢包也儲存在此。得以存取錢包之「金鑰」別無他處安全地存放在你的手機中。Bread 會提供你一組獨特的「紙金鑰」，由 12 個單字所組成，這可用來重建你的錢包之金鑰。如果你弄丟或升級手機，需要此「紙金鑰」來重新存取你的比特幣。</p>\n<p>請在紙上依序寫下每一個單字。我們建議將你的紙金鑰存放於安全的銀行保險箱中，或是與你其他像是護照、出生證明等重要文件一同存放保管。任何取得你紙金鑰的人將可以使用你的金錢，就算他們沒有你的錢包 PIN 碼也一樣，因此請私下保管，不要給其他人看！</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:06Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:26Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002791314,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我为什么必须记下我的纸钥匙？",body:"<p>您的 Bread 与比特币网络直接相连，后者也是您的钱包所在地。打开您钱包的“钥匙”安全地存储在您的手机中，而且只存于此处。Bread 会给您提供一个唯一的“纸钥匙”，它包含一串 12 个词，可用于重建您的钱包钥匙。如果您手机丢失或升级，必须凭借这个“纸钥匙”才能重新调取您的比特币。</p>\n<p>请按顺序将每一个词记在纸上。我们建议将您的纸钥匙存放于银行安全保险箱中，或者跟您的护照、出生证明或其他重要文件存放在一起。任何持有您的纸钥匙的人，即使没有您的钱包 PIN 码，也可以调取您的钱款，因此务必妥当保管该钥匙，切勿向他人出示！</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:06Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:26Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002802953,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Waarom moet ik mijn Papiersleutel opschrijven?",body:'<p>Je Bread verbindt direct met het bitcoin-netwerk, waar je portemonnee is opgeslagen. De "sleutels" voor je portemonnee zijn veilig opgeborgen in je telefoon en nergens anders. Bread geeft jou een unieke "Papiersleutel"; een lijst van 12- woorden die gebruikt kunnen worden om de sleutels van je portemonnee na te maken. Als je ooit je telefoon verliest of upgradet, is deze "Papiersleutel" vereist om weer toegang tot je bitcoin te krijgen.</p>\n<p>Schrijf elk woord, op volgorde, op papier. We raden aan om je Papiersleutel te bewaren in een kluis, in een kluisje bij de bank of waar je je paspoorten, geboorteaktes en andere belangrijke documenten bewaart. Iedereen die je Papiersleutel heeft, heeft toegang tot je geld, zelfs als ze je PIN-code niet hebben, dus hou het privé en laat het niet zien aan anderen!</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:05Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002802973,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Porque é que tenho de anotar a minha chave de papel?",body:'<p>O seu Bread liga-se diretamente à rede de bitcoin, onde está armazenada a sua carteira. As "chaves" para aceder à sua carteira são guardadas de forma segura no seu telemóvel e em mais lado nenhum. O Bread irá fornecer-lhe uma "Chave de Papel" única, que é uma lista de 12 palavras que pode ser usada para recriar as chaves da sua carteira. Se perder ou trocar de telemóvel, esta "Chave de Papel" é necessária para recuperar o acesso às suas bitcoins.</p>\n<p>Por favor, anote cada palavra, por ordem, numa folha de papel. Recomendamos que armazene a sua Chave de Papel num cofre em casa ou no banco, ou onde guarda passaportes, certidões de nascimento ou outros documentos importantes. Qualquer pessoa que tenha a sua Chave de Papel consegue aceder ao seu dinheiro, mesmo que não tenha o PIN da sua carteira, por isso guarde-a bem e não a mostre a ninguém!</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:05Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002802993,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Varför behöver jag skriva ner min pappersnyckel?",body:'<p> Din Bread ansluts direkt till bitcoin-nätverket, där din plånbok är lagrad. "Nycklarna" för att komma åt din plånbok är säkert lagrade i din telefon och ingen annanstans. Bread ger dig en unik "pappersnyckel", vilket är en lista med 12 ord som kan användas för att återskapa nycklarna till din plånbok. Om du någonsin förlorar eller uppgraderar din telefon, krävs denna "pappersnyckel" för att få tillgång till dina bitcoin. </p>\n<p> Skriv ner varje ord, i ordning, på ett papper. Vi rekommenderar att du lagrar din pappersnyckel i ett kassaskåp, i en förvaringsbox på bank eller där du förvarar pass, personbevis eller andra viktiga dokument. Den som har din pappersnyckel kan få tillgång till dina pengar, även om de inte har din plånboks-PIN, så håll den privat och visa den inte för andra! </p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:05Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:26Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002791294,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Зачем мне записывать свой бумажный ключ?",body:"<p>Bread подключается напрямую к биткоин-сети, где хранится ваш кошелек. «Ключи» для доступа к вашему кошельку хранятся на вашем телефоне – и нигде больше. Bread предоставляет вам уникальный «бумажный ключ» – список из 12-ти слов, при помощи которых можно воссоздать ключи к вашему кошельку. Если вы потеряете свой телефон или замените его на новый, то «бумажный ключ» вам понадобится, чтобы получить доступ к своим биткоинам.</p>\n<p>Пожалуйста, запишите каждое слово на бумаге в указанном порядке. Мы рекомендуем хранить ваш бумажный ключ в сейфе, банковской ячейке или же в том месте, где вы храните паспорта, свидетельства о рождении и другие важные инструменты. Любой, кто получит доступ к вашему бумажному ключу, сможет получить доступ к вашим деньгам, даже если у него нет вашего ПИН-кода, поэтому держите его в секрете и не показывайте другим!</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:05Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:26Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002791214,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Por qué tengo que apuntar mi clave de papel?",body:'<p>Tu Bread se conecta directamente a la red de Bitcoin, donde se almacena tu monedero. Las "claves" para acceder al monedero se almacenan de forma segura en tu teléfono y en ninguna otra parte. Bread te proporcionará una "clave de papel" única, que consiste en una lista de 12 palabras que se pueden utilizar para recrear las claves de tu cartera. Si alguna vez pierdes o actualizas tu teléfono, esta "Clave de papel" es necesaria para recuperar el acceso a tu Bitcoin.</p>\n<p>Escribe cada palabra, en orden, en un trozo de papel. Te recomendamos que guardes la clave de papel en una caja fuerte, en la caja de seguridad de un banco o en el lugar donde guardes los pasaportes, los certificados de nacimiento u otros documentos importantes. Cualquier persona que tenga tu clave de papel puede acceder a tu dinero, incluso si no tiene el número PIN del monedero, así que mantenla en secreto y ¡no se la muestres a los demás!</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:24Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002791234,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Pourquoi dois-je écrire ma clé papier ?",body:"<p>Votre Bread se connecte directement au réseau bitcoin, où votre portefeuille est stocké. Les « clés » vous permettant d'accéder à votre portefeuille sont stockées en toute sécurité dans votre téléphone et nulle part ailleurs. Bread vous fournira également une « clé papier » unique. Il s'agit d'une liste de 12 mots qui peut être utilisée pour recréer les clés de votre portefeuille. Si vous perdez ou changez votre téléphone, cette « clé papier » est requise pour récupérer l'accès à vos bitcoins.</p>\n<p>Veuillez écrire chaque mot dans l'ordre sur une feuille de papier. Nous vous recommandons de stocker votre clé papier dans un coffre-fort chez vous ou à la banque, ou à l'endroit où vous rangeriez vos passeports, vos actes de naissance ou d'autres documents importants. Toute personne qui posséderait votre clé papier pourra accéder à votre argent, même si elle ne connaît pas votre code de portefeuille, alors protégez-la et ne la montrez à personne !</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002791254,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"なぜペーパーキーを書き留めておく必要があるのでしょうか?",body:"<p>あなたのBreadはあなたのウォレットが保管されているビットコインネットワークへと直接接続されます。ウォレットにアクセスする為の「キー」はあなたの携帯電話内だけに安全に保管されます。Breadではウォレットへのキーの再製へと使用可能な12単語のリストから形成されるユニークな「ペーパーキー」が提供されます。お手持ちの携帯電話を失くしてしまったり、アップグレードした場合には、あなたのビットコインへのアクセスを取り戻す為にこちらの「ペーパーキー」が必要になります。</p>\n<p>紙に各単語を正しい順番に書き留めていただくようお願いします。書き留められたペーパーキーは銀行内の金庫やパスポート、出生証明書など他の重要な書類を保管されている安全な場所に保管しておくことをお勧めします。\nあなたのペーパーキーを手にした誰もがウォレットの暗証番号無しでもあなたの資金にアクセスすることができるようになります。その為、ペーパーキーは機密に保管して、他人に見せることは無いようにしてください!</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002802933,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Perché devo prendere nota della mia Chiave Cartacea?",body:'<p>Il tuo Bread si collega direttamente alla rete bitcoin che contiene il tuo portafoglio. Le "chiavi" per accedere al tuo portafoglio sono archiviate in maniera sicura solo ed esclusivamente nel tuo telefono. Bread ti fornisce una "Chiave Cartacea" univoca, formata da 12 parole che possono essere utilizzate per ricreare le chiavi del tuo portafoglio. Se smarrisci o cambi il tuo telefono, dovrai fornire questa "Chiave Cartacea" per accedere nuovamente ai tuoi bitcoin.</p>\n<p>Ti invitiamo a scrivere, su un pezzo di carta, ogni parola, nell\'ordine corretto. Ti consigliamo di conservare la tua Chiave Cartacea in una cassaforte, in un deposito in banca o in qualsiasi luogo dove conserveresti i passaporti, i certificati di nascita e altri documenti importanti. Ricorda che chiunque abbia accesso alla tua Chiave Cartacea potrà accedere al tuo denaro, anche senza il PIN del tuo portafoglio, quindi tienila al sicuro e non farla vedere a nessuno!</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:04Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002802893,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvorfor skal jeg skrive min papirnøgle ned?",body:'<p> Dit Bread-konto forbindes direkte til bitcoin-netværket, hvor din tegnebog er gemt. "Nøglerne" for adgang til din tegnebog er sikkert gemt i din telefon og ingen andre steder. Bread vil give dig en unik "papirnøgle", som er en liste på 12 ord, som kan bruges til at gendanne nøglerne til din tegnebog. Hvis du nogensinde mister eller opgraderer din telefon, er denne "papirnøgle" nødvendig for at gendanne adgangen til dine bitcoin.</p>\n<p>Skriv venligst hvert ord i rækkefølge på et stykke papir. Vi anbefaler at gemme din papirnøgle i et pengeskab, en bankboks eller hvor du end måtte gemme dokumenter såsom pas, fødselsattest eller andre vigtige dokumenter. Enhver der har din papirnøgle, kan få adgang til dine penge, selvom de ikke har din tegnebogskode, så gem den et privat sted og vis den ikke til andre!</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:24Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002802913,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wieso muss ich meinen Paper Key aufschreiben?",body:"<p>Ihr Bread verbindet sich direkt mit dem Bitcoin-Netzwerk, wo Ihre Geldbörse gespeichert ist. Die „Schlüssel“, mit denen Sie auf Ihre Geldbörse zugreifen, sind sicher in Ihrem Handy gespeichert und nirgendwo sonst. Bread teilt Ihnen einen einzigartigen „Paper Key“ zu, der aus einer Liste von 12 Wörtern besteht und dazu verwendet werden kann, die Schlüssel zu Ihrer Geldbörse wiederherzustellen. Falls Sie jemals Ihr Handy verlieren oder sich ein aktuelleres zulegen, wird dieser „Paper Key“ benötigt, um erneut Zugriff auf Ihre Bitcoins zu erhalten.</p>\n<p>Bitte schreiben Sie jedes Wort in der richtigen Reihenfolge auf ein Stück Papier. Wir empfehlen, Ihren Paper Key in einem Tresor, einem Safe in einer Bank oder dort aufbewahren, wo Sie auch Reisepässe, Geburtsurkunden oder andere wichtige Dokumente lagern würden. Jeder, der Ihren Paper Key hat, kann auf Ihr Geld zugreifen, auch wenn er die PIN zu Ihrer Geldbörse nicht kennt, also halten Sie ihn geheim und zeigen Sie ihn niemand anderem!</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:24Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001226693,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757793/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757793",source_id:115000757793,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"Why do I need to write down my paper key?",body:'<p>Your Bread connects directly to the bitcoin network, where your wallet is stored. The "keys" to access your wallet are securely stored in your phone and nowhere else. Bread will provide you with a unique "Paper Key," which is a list of 12-words which can be used to recreate the keys to your wallet. If you ever lose or upgrade your phone, this "Paper Key" is required to regain access to your bitcoin.</p>\n<p>Please write down each word, in order, on a piece of paper. We recommend storing your Paper Key in a safe, safety deposit box at a bank, or wherever you might keep passports, birth certificates, or other important documents. Anyone who has your Paper Key can access your money, even if they don\'t have your wallet PIN, so keep it private and don\'t show it to others!</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:08Z",updated_at:"2017-07-23T01:27:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000757733,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000757733-How-do-I-confirm-my-Paper-Key-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757733-How-do-I-confirm-my-Paper-Key-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:27Z",name:"How do I confirm my Paper Key?",title:"How do I confirm my Paper Key?",body:'<p>It is very important that your Paper Key is written down correctly, and in the correct order. Enter the words requested to make sure everything is correct. For example, "Word #1" means the first word of your Paper Key, "Word #2" means the second word, etc.</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:confirm-phrase"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002791194,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何確認自己的紙金鑰？",body:"<p>將你的紙金鑰依照順序正確寫下非常重要。輸入指定的文字來確保完全正確。譬如說，「單字 #1」代表你紙金鑰上的第一個字，「單字 #2」代表第二個字等等。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:24Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002802873,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何确认我的纸钥匙？",body:"<p>务必以正确的顺序准确无误地记下您的纸钥匙，这点非常重要。按要求输入单词以确保一切都准确无误。例如，“词 #1”代表纸钥匙的第一个词，“词 #2”代表第二个词，以此类推。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:23Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002791174,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como confirmo a minha Chave de Papel?",body:'<p>É muito importante que a sua Chave de Papel seja anotada corretamente e pela ordem correta, Introduza as palavras solicitadas para se certificar de que está tudo correto. Por exemplo, "Palavra 1" significa a primeira palavra da sua Chave de Papel, "Palavra 2" significa a segunda palavra, etc.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:02Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:23Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002802793,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe bevestig ik mijn Papieren sleutel?",body:'<p>Het is heel belangrijk dat je Papieren sleutel juist is opgeschreven, en in de juiste volgorde. Voer de gevraagde woorden in om zeker te weten dat alles correct is. Bijv. "Woord #1" betekent het eerste woord van je Papieren sleutel, "Woord #2" betekent het tweede woord, etc.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:02Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:23Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002802833,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как мне подтвердить свой бумажный ключ?",body:"<p>Очень важно, чтобы вы правильно записали слова бумажного ключа в верном порядке. Введите требуемые слова, чтобы убедиться, что все записано правильно. Например, «Слово №1» означает первое слово вашего бумажного ключа, «Слово №2» – второе слово, и т.д.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:02Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:23Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002802853,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur bekräftar jag min pappersnyckel?",body:'<p> Det är väldigt viktigt att din pappersnyckel skrivs ner korrekt och i rätt ordning. Ange de efterfrågade orden för att se till att allt är korrekt. "Ord #1" betyder till exempel det första ordet i din pappersnyckel, "Ord #2" betyder det andra ordet osv. </p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:02Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:23Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002802713,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo puedo confirmar mi clave de papel?",body:'<p>Es muy importante que la clave de papel esté escrita correctamente y en el orden correcto. Introduce las palabras solicitadas para asegurarte de que todo está correcto. Por ejemplo, "Palabra 1" significa la primera palabra de tu clave de papel, "Palabra 2" significa la segunda palabra, etc.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:01Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:22Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002802733,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je confirmer ma clé papier ?",body:"<p>Il est très important que votre clé papier soit écrite correctement, et dans le bon ordre. Entrez les mots demandés pour vous assurer que tout soit correct. Par exemple, « Mot n°1 » correspond au premier mot de votre clé papier, « Mot n°2 » correspond au deuxième mot, etc.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:01Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:22Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002802753,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come verifico la correttezza della mia Chiave Cartacea?",body:'<p>È fondamentale aver preso nota della tua Chiave Cartacea in maniera corretta e nell\'ordine giusto. Inserisci le parole richieste per verificare che le informazioni siano corrette. Per esempio: "Parola #1" indica la prima parola della tua Chiave Cartacea, "Parola #2" indica la seconda etc.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:01Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:22Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002802773,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ペーパーキーを確認する方法は?",body:"<p>あなたのペーパーキーが正しく書き留められていること、そしてキーが正しい順序で書き留められていることは大変重要です。例えば「単語 #1」はあなたのペーパーキーの最初の単語という意味で、「単語 #2」は2番目の単語を指します。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:01Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:22Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002791134,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan bekræfter jeg min papirnøgle?",body:'<p> Det er meget vigtigt, at din papirnøgle er skrevet korrekt ned og i den rigtige rækkefølge. Indtast de forespurgte ord for at sikre, at alt er korrekt. For eksempel betyder "Ord # 1" det første ord i din papirnøgle, "Ord # 2" betyder det andet ord osv.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:21Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002791154,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie bestätige ich meinen Paper Key?",body:"<p>Es ist sehr wichtig, dass Ihr Paper Key korrekt und in der richtigen Reihenfolge aufgeschrieben wird. Geben Sie die erforderlichen Wörter ein, um sicherzustellen, dass alles korrekt ist. Zum Beispiel bezieht sich „Wort Nr. 1“ auf das erste Wort Ihres Paper Key, „Wort Nr. 2“ auf das zweite Wort, etc.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:22Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001226633,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757733/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757733",source_id:115000757733,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How do I confirm my Paper Key?",body:'<p>It is very important that your Paper Key is written down correctly, and in the correct order. Enter the words requested to make sure everything is correct. For example, "Word #1" means the first word of your Paper Key, "Word #2" means the second word, etc.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:00Z",updated_at:"2017-07-23T01:42:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000757773,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000757773-How-do-I-wipe-my-wallet-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757773-How-do-I-wipe-my-wallet-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:07Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:24Z",name:"How do I wipe my wallet?",title:"How do I wipe my wallet?",body:"<p>Bread can only have one wallet active at a time. If you choose to start a new wallet or restore an existing wallet, the currently active wallet must be erased first.</p>\n<p>If you erase your wallet without writing down its Paper Key, your money will be lost. To prevent this, you must first enter your Paper Key for the <strong>currently active</strong> wallet to make sure you have it written down correctly. The wallet will then be erased, and you can create a new wallet or restore a previous wallet.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:wipe-wallet"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002802693,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何清除我的錢包？",body:"<p>Bread 同時只能有一個有效錢包。如果你選擇開始一個新錢包，或回復既有錢包，須先刪除現在使用中的錢包。</p>\n<p>如果你在未寫下紙金鑰前就刪除錢包的話，裡面的錢將流失。為了防範此情形，你必須先輸入<strong>現在使用</strong> 錢包的紙金鑰，確保已將其正確寫下。該錢包將被移除，而你可建立新的，或回復先前的錢包。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:21Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002802673,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何删除我的钱包？",body:"<p>Bread 同一时间只能有一个活动的钱包。如果您选择新建一个钱包或恢复一个已有钱包，则必须先删除当前活动钱包。</p>\n<p>如果您没有记下钱包的纸钥匙就把钱包删除了，那么您的钱款随之丢失。为了防止发生这种情况，您必须首先输入<strong>当前活动</strong>钱包的纸钥匙以确保您已将其正确记下。随后该钱包将被删除，您可以新建一个钱包或恢复一个之前的钱包。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:21Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002791094,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe verwijder ik mijn portemonnee?",body:"<p>Bread kan slechts één portemonnee actief hebben per keer. Als je ervoor kiest om een nieuwe portemonnee te starten of een bestaande portemonnee te herstellen, moet de huidige actieve portemonnee eerst gewist worden.</p>\n<p>Als je je portemonnee wist zonder de papieren sleutel op te schrijven, is je geld verloren. Om dit te voorkomen moet je de Papieren sleutel voor de <strong>op dat moment actieve</strong> portemonnee invoeren om zeker te weten dat je het juist hebt opgeschreven. De portemonnee zal dan gewist worden, en je kunt een nieuwe portemonnee maken of de vorige herstellen. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002802633,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como elimino a minha carteira?",body:"<p>O Bread pode ter apenas uma carteira ativa de cada vez. Se escolher começar uma nova carteira ou restaurar uma existente, a carteira ativa no momento será eliminada primeiro.</p>\n<p>Se eliminar a sua carteira sem tomar nota da sua Chave de Papel, o seu dinheiro será perdido. Para impedir isto, deve primeiro introduzir a sua Chave de Papel da carteira <strong>atualmente ativa</strong> para garantir que a escreveu corretamente. A carteira será depois eliminada, e pode criar uma nova carteira ou restaurar uma anterior.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002791114,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur raderar jag min plånbok?",body:"<p>Bread kan bara ha en plånbok aktiv åt gången. Om du väljer att starta en ny plånbok eller återställa en existerande plånbok, måste den för tillfället aktiva plånboken raderas först.</p>\n<p>Om du raderar din plånbok utan att skriva ner dess pappersnyckel kommer dina pengar att gå förlorade. För att förhindra detta, måste du först ange din pappersnyckel för den <strong>nu aktiva</strong> plånboken för att säkerställa att du har skrivit ner den korrekt. Plånboken kommer sedan att raderas och du kan skapa en ny plånbok eller återställa en tidigare plånbok.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:21Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002802653,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как мне сделать вайп кошелька?",body:"<p>В Bread в один момент времени может быть активным только один кошелек. Если вы создадите новый кошелек или же восстановите существующий, то для начала вам нужно удалить текущий активный кошелек.</p>\n<p>Если вы удалите свой кошелек, не записав сначала его бумажный ключ, то ваши деньги будут потеряны. Чтобы этого не допустить, вы должны сначала ввести свой бумажный ключ для <strong>текущего активного</strong> кошелька, чтобы мы убедились, что вы его записали. Затем этот кошелек будет удален, и вы сможете либо создать новый кошелек, либо восстановить существующий.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002791034,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je effacer mon portefeuille ?",body:"<p>Bread peut seulement contenir un portefeuille actif à la fois. Si vous choisissez de créer un nouveau portefeuille ou de restaurer un portefeuille existant, le portefeuille actuellement actif doit d'abord être effacé.</p>\n<p>Si vous effacez votre portefeuille sans écrire sa clé papier, votre argent sera perdu. Pour éviter cela, vous devez d'abord entrer la clé papier de votre portefeuille <strong>actuellement actif</strong> pour vous assurer de l'avoir écrit correctement. Le portefeuille sera ensuite effacé, et vous pourrez créer un nouveau portefeuille ou restaurer un ancien portefeuille.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:58Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002791054,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come elimino il mio portafoglio?",body:"<p>Bread può avere solo un portafoglio attivo alla volta. Se decidi di creare un nuovo portafoglio o di ripristinarne uno esistente, devi prima eliminare il portafoglio attivo.</p>\n<p>Se non prendi nota della tua Chiave Cartacea prima di eliminare il portafoglio, non potrai più accedere ai tuoi soldi. Quindi, inserisci prima la Chiave Privata del portafoglio <strong>attivo al momento</strong>, così potrai verificare di averla scritta correttamente. Successivamente il portafoglio verrà eliminato e potrai creare un nuovo portafoglio o ripristinarne uno esistente.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:58Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002791074,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ウォレットをワイプする方法は?",body:"<p>Breadでは一度に一つのウォレットのみをアクティブにしておくことができます。新しいウォレットを開始したり、既存のウォレットの復元することを選択する場合には、まず現在アクティブとなっているウォレットを消去する必要があります。</p>\n<p>ペーパーキーを書き留めずにウォレットを消去した場合には、あなたの資金が失われてしまいます。こういった事態を妨げるために、キーが正しく書き留められていることを確認する為に、まず<strong>現在アクティブ</strong>となっているウォレットのペーパーキーを入力していただく必要があります。その後ウォレットは消去され、新しいウォレットの作成または以前のウォレットの復元が可能となります。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:58Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002802613,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo puedo vaciar mi monedero?",body:"<p>Bread solo puede tener un monedero activo a la vez. Si decides iniciar un monedero nuevo o restaurar uno existente, primero debes borrar el monedero activo.</p>\n<p>Si borras tu monedero sin apuntar la clave de papel, tu dinero se perderá. Para evitar esto, primero debes introducir la clave de papel para el <strong>monedero activo en uso</strong> para asegurarte de que la tienes apuntada correctamente. El monedero se borrará y podrás crear un nuevo monedero o restaurar uno anterior.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:58Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002791014,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan sletter jeg min tegnebog?",body:"<p>Bread kan kun have en atkiv tegnebog ad gangen. Hvis du vælger at oprette en ny tegnebog eller genoprette en eksisterende tegnebog, skal den aktuelt aktive tegnebog først slettes.</p>\n<p>Hvis du sletter din tegnebog uden at skrive dens papirnøgle ned, vil dine penge gå tabt. For at forhindre dette skal du først indtaste din papirnøgle til den<strong> aktuelt aktive</strong> tegnebog for at sikre, at du har skrevet den korrekt. Tegnebogen vil blive slettet, og du kan oprette en ny tegnebog eller gendanne en tidligere tegnebog.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:57Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002802593,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie lösche ich meine Geldbörse?",body:"<p>Nur eine Geldbörse kann jeweils in Bread aktiv sein. Falls Sie sich dazu entschließen, eine neue Geldbörse zu beginnen oder eine existierende Geldbörse wiederherzustellen, muss die momentan aktive Geldbörse zuerst gelöscht werden.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie eine Geldbörse löschen, ohne vorher ihren Paper Key zu notieren, ist Ihr Geld verloren. Um dies zu vermeiden, müssen Sie zunächst den Paper Key für Ihre <strong>momentan aktive</strong> Geldbörse eingeben, um sicherzustellen, dass Sie ihn korrekt notiert haben. Die Geldbörse wird anschließend gelöscht und Sie können eine neue Geldbörse erstellen oder eine vorherige wiederherstellen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:57Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001226673,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000757773/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000757773",source_id:115000757773,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How do I wipe my wallet?",body:"<p>Bread can only have one wallet active at a time. If you choose to start a new wallet or restore an existing wallet, the currently active wallet must be erased first.</p>\n<p>If you erase your wallet without writing down its Paper Key, your money will be lost. To prevent this, you must first enter your Paper Key for the <strong>currently active</strong> wallet to make sure you have it written down correctly. The wallet will then be erased, and you can create a new wallet or restore a previous wallet.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T19:13:07Z",updated_at:"2017-07-23T02:03:50Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000763374,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000763374-What-are-the-transaction-details-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763374-What-are-the-transaction-details-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977707,created_at:"2017-07-21T18:51:29Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:22Z",name:"What are the transaction details?",title:"What are the transaction details?",body:'<p>This screen shows details about the transaction:</p>\n<h3>Status</h3>\n<p>If the transaction status is "complete," then the transaction has successfully gone through. If this is a transaction you sent, the money is now in the wallet of the recipient. If this is a transaction you received, the money is now in your wallet, ready to be spent.</p>\n<p>If the status is not yet complete, this will show the current progress. If you are receiving the transaction, you will see an indicator once it is safe to spend the funds.</p>\n<h3>Memo</h3>\n<p>Here you can attach a note to the transaction to remind yourself what it was for. This memo will not be shared with anyone else and is only visible to you, but you can edit it at any time, even after the transaction has completed.</p>\n<h3>Amount</h3>\n<p>This shows detailed information about how much bitcoin was sent, how much it was worth at the time, and other details about your balance.</p>\n<h3>Other</h3>\n<p>At the bottom of this screen you will find additional technical details about the transaction. The bitcoin transaction ID can be used as proof that a payment was made.</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:transaction-details"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002790994,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"交易細節在哪裡？",body:"<p>此畫面顯示交易細節：</p>\n<h3>狀態</h3>\n<p>如果交易狀態為「完成」，此交易已順利完成。如你在此交易中為發款方，金額現在已交至收款方的錢包中。如你在此交易中為收款方，金額現在已在你的錢包中，準備好再次發送。\n</p>\n<p>如果狀態尚未顯示完成，將會顯示當下進度。如你在交易中為收款方，在可以安全花費該款項時你會看到指示符號。</p>\n<h3>備忘錄</h3>\n<p>在此你可貼上交易註記，提醒自己該交易的細節。此備忘錄除你之外其他人看不到，但你可在任何時刻編輯，就算是交易完成後也一樣。</p>\n<h3>金額</h3>\n<p>這裡顯示發出了多少比特幣、當時市值多少，以及其他關於你帳戶餘額的詳細資訊。</p>\n<h3>其他</h3>\n<p>在畫面最下方你會看到關於該交易的額外技術細節。比特幣交易 ID 可為付款已實際完成佐證。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:57Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002790914,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Wat zijn de transactiedetails?",body:'<p>Dit scherm toont details van de transactie: </p>\n<h3>Status</h3>\n<p>Als de transactiestatus "voltooid" is, is de transactie succesvol verlopen. Als jij de transactie hebt verstuurd, is het geld nu in handen van de ontvanger. Als het een transactie is die jij hebt ontvangen, is het geld nu in jouw handen, klaar om uitgegeven te worden.</p>\n<p>Als de status nog niet voltooid is, zal het de huidige voortgang weergeven. Als je een transactie ontvangt, krijg je een indicatie te zien van wanneer het veilig is om het geld uit te geven. </p>\n<h3>Memo</h3>\n<p>Hier kan je een notitie aan de transactie toevoegen om te kunnen zien waar hij voor was. Deze memo zal niet met iemand anders gedeeld worden en is alleen voor jou zichtbaar, maar je kunt hem op elk gewenst moment aanpassen, zelfs nadat de transactie voltooid is.</p>\n<h3>Bedrag</h3>\n<p>Dit geeft gedetailleerde informatie over hoeveel bitcoin verstuurd is, hoeveel het waard was op dat moment en andere details over je saldo.</p>\n<h3>Ander</h3>\n<p>Aan de onderkant van dit scherm vind je technische details over de transactie. De bitcoin-transactie-ID kan gebruikt worden als bewijs dat de betaling gemaakt is.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002790934,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Что такое подробности транзакции?",body:"<p>На этом экране будут показаны подробности транзакции:</p>\n<h3>Статус</h3>\n<p>Если статус транзакции – «завершена», то транзакция была проведена успешно. Если эту транзакцию отправлял вы, то значит деньги теперь находятся в кошельке получателя. Если это входящая транзакция, то значит деньги теперь в вашем кошельке и вы можете их потратить.</p>\n<p>Если статус транзакции не «завершена», то будет отображен текущий прогресс. Если вы получаете транзакцию, то вы увидите индикатор, когда вы сможете потратить эти средства.</p>\n<h3>Примечание</h3>\n<p>Здесь можно написать напоминание о том, что это за транзакция. Это примечание не будет видно другим и доступно только вам, и вы можете изменить его в любой момент, даже после завершения транзакции.</p>\n<h3>Сумма</h3>\n<p>Здесь показана подробная информация о том, сколько именно биткоинов было отправлено, сколько они стоили во время отправки и другие данные о вашем балансе.</p>\n<h3>Другое</h3>\n<p>В нижней части экрана вы найдете дополнительные технические данные транзакции. ID транзакции можно использовать как доказательство того, что оплата была совершена.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002790954,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Vilka är transaktionsdetaljerna?",body:'<p>Denna skärm visar uppgifter om transaktionen:</p>\n<h3>Status</h3>\n<p>Om transaktionsstatusen är "slutförd" har transaktionen gått igenom. Om det är en transaktion som du skickat, finns pengarna nu i mottagarens plånbok. Om det är en transaktion du mottagit, finns pengarna nu i din plånbok och är redo att spenderas.</p>\n<p>Om statusen är ännu ej slutförd visar detta aktuell status. Om du är den som tar emot transaktionen kommer du att se en indikator när det är säkert att använda pengarna.</p>\n<h3>Memo</h3>\n<p>Här kan du bifoga en anteckning till transaktionen för att påminna dig själv om vad den var för. Detta memo kommer inte att delas med någon annan och är bara synligt för dig, men du kan redigera det när som helst, även efter att transaktionen har slutförts.</p>\n<h3>Belopp</h3>\n<p>Detta visar detaljerad information om hur mycket bitcoin som har skickats, hur mycket det var värt vid det tillfället och andra uppgifter om ditt saldo.</p>\n<h3>Annat</h3>\n<p>I nederkanten av den här skärmen hittar du ytterligare tekniska uppgifter om transaktionen. Transaktions-ID för bitcoin-transaktionen kan användas som bevis för att betalning utförts.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002790974,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"什么是交易详情？",body:"<p>此屏幕显示交易详情：</p>\n<h3>状态</h3>\n<p>如果交易状态是“完成”，则交易已成功结束。如果您是交易付款方，则钱款现已进入收款人的钱包。如果您是交易收款方，则钱款现已进入您的钱包并可供支取。</p>\n<p>如果交易状态为尚未完成，则此处将显示当前进度。如果您是交易收款方，一旦可安全地支取资金，即可看到一个指示符号。</p>\n<h3>备忘录</h3>\n<p>在此您可以给交易添加备注，用于提醒自己此次交易的目的。此备忘录不会与其他人分享，仅您自己可见，但您可随时对它进行编辑，甚至在交易完成后亦可。</p>\n<h3>金额</h3>\n<p>此处显示比特币付出数量、它当时的价值等详细信息，以及您的余额等其他详情。</p>\n<h3>其他</h3>\n<p>在屏幕底部，您将看到有关该交易的附加技术详情。比特币交易编号可用作付款证明。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002802573,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Quais são os detalhes da transação?",body:'<p>Este ecrã mostra detalhes sobre a transação:</p>\n<h3>Estado</h3>\n<p>Se o estado da transação for "concluída", então a transação foi efetuada com sucesso. Se se tratar de uma transação em que enviou, o dinheiro está agora na carteira do destinatário. Se for uma transação em que recebeu, o dinheiro está agora na sua carteira, pronto a ser usado.</p>\n<p>Se o estado ainda não for concluído, isto irá mostrar o progresso atual. Se estiver a receber a transação, verá um indicador assim que for seguro gastar os fundos.</p>\n<h3>Nota</h3>\n<p>Aqui pode anexar uma nota à transação para lhe lembrar do seu motivo. Esta nota não será partilhada com mais ninguém e estará visível apenas para si, mas pode editá-la a qualquer altura, mesmo após a transação ser concluída.</p>\n<h3>Montante</h3>\n<p>Isto mostra informações detalhadas sobre quanto de bitcoin foi enviado, quanto valia na altura e outros detalhes sobre o seu saldo.</p>\n<h3>Outros</h3>\n<p>No fundo deste ecrã, irá encontrar detalhes técnicos adicionais sobre a transação. O ID da transação de bitcoin pode ser usado como prova de que foi feito um pagamento.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002802513,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Qué son los detalles de transacción?",body:'<p>Esta pantalla muestra los detalles de la transacción:</p>\n<h3>Estado</h3>\n<p>Si el estado de la transacción está "completo", entonces la transacción se ha realizado con éxito. Si se trata de una transacción saliente, el dinero estará ahora en el monedero del destinatario. Si se trata de una transacción entrante, el dinero estará ahora en tu monedero, listo para gastar.</p>\n<p>Si el estado aún no está completado, se mostrará el progreso actual. Si estás recibiendo la transacción, verás un indicador una vez que sea seguro gastar los fondos.</p>\n<h3>Nota</h3>\n<p> Aquí puedes adjuntar una nota a la transacción para recordar de lo que se trataba. Esta nota no se compartirá con nadie y solo tú podrás verla, pero podrás editarla en cualquier momento, incluso después de haber realizado la transacción.</p>\n<h3>Cantidad</h3>\n<p> Esto muestra información detallada sobre cuántos bitcoines se enviaron, cuánto costaban en ese momento y otros detalles sobre tu saldo.</p>\n<h3>Otros</h3>\n<p>En la parte inferior de esta pantalla encontrarás detalles técnicos adicionales sobre la transacción. El número de identificación de la transacción en bitcoines puede utilizarse como prueba de que se realizó un pago.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002802533,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Cosa sono i dettagli della transazione?",body:'<p>Questa schermata mostra i dettagli della transazione:</p>\n<h3>Stato</h3>\n<p>Se la transazione ha come stato "completa", vuol dire che è stata completata con successo. Se si tratta di una transazione in uscita, i soldi sono stati trasferiti nel portafoglio del destinatario. Se si tratta di una transazione in entrata, i soldi sono arrivati nel tuo portafoglio e possono essere usati.</p>\n<p>Se la transazione non è "completa", verrà mostrato il progresso attuale. Se sei il destinatario della transazione, un indicatore ti avviserà quando potrai usare i fondi.</p>\n<h3>Memo</h3>\n<p>Qui potrai aggiungere delle note per identificare la causale della transazione. Questo memo non verrà condiviso con nessun altro, sarai l\'unico a poterlo vedere e potrai modificarlo in qualsiasi momento, anche dopo il completamento della transazione.</p>\n<h3>Importo</h3>\n<p>Contiene le informazioni dettagliate sul quantitativo di bitcoin inviati, il valore al momento dell\'invio e altri dettagli sul tuo saldo.\n</p>\n<h3>Altro</h3>\n<p>Nella parte inferiore di questa schermata troverai tutti i dettagli tecnici riguardanti la transazione. L\'ID della transazione bitcoin è valido come prova di pagamento.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002802553,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"取引詳細とは?",body:"<p>この画面には取引の詳細が表示されます:</p>\n<h3>ステータス</h3>\n<p>取引ステータスが「完了」となっている場合には、その取引は完了されたということで、この取引が送金であった場合には、受領者のウォレット内に送信された金額が入金されて使用可能になったということです。</p>\n<p>ステータスが未完了となっている場合には、現在の進行状況が表示されます。あなたが取引の受領者側である場合には、資金が使用可能になり次第インジケーターが表示されます。</p>\n<h3>メモ</h3>\n<p>この欄には取引内容を覚えておくために、メモを付け加えることができます。このメモは誰とも共有されることはなく、あなただけに表示されます。メモがいつでも編集可能で、取引が完了後にも編集を行うことが出来ます。</p>\n<h3>金額</h3>\n<p>こちらには使用されたビットコインの金額、その時点での価値、あなたの残高に関する詳細が表示されます。</p>\n<h3>その他</h3>\n<p>この画面の最下部には取引の更なる技術的詳細が表示されます。ビットコイン取引IDは支払いが行われたという証明として使用することができます。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002790894,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"À quoi correspondent les détails de la transaction ?",body:"<p>Cette page affiche les détails de la transaction :</p>\n<h3>Statut</h3>\n<p>Si le statut de la transaction est « terminé », alors la transaction a été effectuée avec succès. S'il s'agit d'une transaction que vous avez envoyée, l'argent se trouve désormais dans le portefeuille du destinataire. S'il s'agit d'une transaction que vous avez reçue, l'argent se trouve désormais dans votre portefeuille, prêt à être dépensé.</p>\n<p>Si le statut n'est pas encore « terminé », la page affichera l'avancement en cours. Si vous recevez la transaction, vous verrez un indicateur lorsque vous pourrez dépenser les fonds en toute sécurité.</p>\n<h3>Note</h3>\n<p>Vous pouvez joindre une note à la transaction pour vous rappeler de son motif. Cette note ne sera partagée avec personne et n'est visible que pour vous, mais vous pouvez la modifier à tout moment, même lorsque la transaction a été effectuée.</p>\n<h3>Montant</h3>\n<p>Cette page affiche des informations détaillées sur la quantité de bitcoins envoyée, sa valeur au moment de l'envoi, et d'autres détails sur votre solde.</p>\n<h3>Autre</h3>\n<p>En bas de cet écran, vous trouverez des détails techniques supplémentaires sur la transaction. L'identifiant de la transaction en bitcoin peut être utilisé comme preuve de paiement.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002802473,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvad er transaktionsoplysningerne?",body:'<p>Denne skærm viser detaljer om transaktionen: </p>\n<h3>Status</h3>\n<p> Hvis statussen på transaktionen vises som "gennemført", er transaktionen gennemført. Hvis dette er en transaktion, du sendte, er pengene nu i modtagerens tegnebog. Hvis dette er en transaktion, du har modtaget, er pengene nu i din tegnebog, klar til at blive brugt.</p>\n<p> Hvis statussen endnu ikke er gennemført, vises de aktuelle fremskridt i transaktionen. Hvis du modtager transaktionen, vil du se en indikator, når det er sikkert at bruge pengene.</p>\n<h3>Memo</h3>\n<p> Her kan du vedhæfte en note til transaktionen for at minde dig selv om, hvad det var for. Dette notat vil ikke blive delt med andre og er kun synligt for dig, men du kan redigere det til enhver tid, selv efter transaktionen er afsluttet.</p>\n<h3>Beløb</h3>\n<p> Dette viser detaljerede oplysninger om, hvor mange bitcoin der blev sendt, hvor meget de var værd på det tidspunkt og andre detaljer om din saldo.</p>\n<h3>Andet</h3>\n<p>Nederst på denne skærm finder du yderligere tekniske detaljer om transaktionen. Bitcointransaktions-identifikationsnummeret kan bruges som bevis for, at en betaling blev foretaget.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:16Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002802493,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Worum handelt es sich bei den Transaktionsdetails?",body:"<p>Dieser Bildschirm zeigt die Transaktionsdetails an:</p>\n<h3>Status</h3>\n<p>Wenn der Transaktionsstatus „abgeschlossen“ anzeigt, dann war die Transaktion erfolgreich. Falls es sich um eine von Ihnen gesendete Transaktion handelt, dann befindet sich das Geld nun in der Geldbörse des Empfängers. Falls es sich um um eine von Ihnen empfangene Transaktion handelt, dann befindet sich das Geld nun in Ihrer Geldbörse und ist bereit zum ausgeben.</p>\n<p>Falls der Status noch nicht „abgeschlossen“ ist, wird hier der aktuelle Status angezeigt. Falls Sie der Empfänger dieser Transaktion sind, wird es Ihnen angezeigt, sobald das Geld sicher ausgegeben werden kann.</p>\n<h3>Notiz</h3>\n<p>Hier können Sie der Transaktion eine Notiz hinzufügen, um sich selbst daran zu erinnern, wofür sie war. Die Notiz wird niemandem mitgeteilt und ist nur für Sie sichtbar, Sie können sie aber jederzeit bearbeiten, selbst nach Anschluss der Transaktion.</p>\n<h3>Betrag</h3>\n<p>Hier werden detaillierte Informationen darüber angezeigt, wie viele Bitcoins versendet wurden, wie viel sie zum gegeben Zeitpunkt wert waren, sowie andere Details zu Ihrem Kontostand.\n</p>\n<h3>Sonstiges</h3>\n<p>Am unteren Rand dieses Bildschirms finden Sie zusätzliche technische Details dieser Transaktion. Die Bitcoin-Transaktions-ID kann als Nachweis genutzt werden, dass eine Zahlung getätigt wurde.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:16Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001236554,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000763374/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000763374",source_id:115000763374,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"What are the transaction details?",body:'<p>This screen shows details about the transaction:</p>\n<h3>Status</h3>\n<p>If the transaction status is "complete," then the transaction has successfully gone through. If this is a transaction you sent, the money is now in the wallet of the recipient. If this is a transaction you received, the money is now in your wallet, ready to be spent.</p>\n<p>If the status is not yet complete, this will show the current progress. If you are receiving the transaction, you will see an indicator once it is safe to spend the funds.</p>\n<h3>Memo</h3>\n<p>Here you can attach a note to the transaction to remind yourself what it was for. This memo will not be shared with anyone else and is only visible to you, but you can edit it at any time, even after the transaction has completed.</p>\n<h3>Amount</h3>\n<p>This shows detailed information about how much bitcoin was sent, how much it was worth at the time, and other details about your balance.</p>\n<h3>Other</h3>\n<p>At the bottom of this screen you will find additional technical details about the transaction. The bitcoin transaction ID can be used as proof that a payment was made.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T18:51:29Z",updated_at:"2017-08-29T01:19:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:234979507,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/234979507-How-do-I-import-a-wallet-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234979507-How-do-I-import-a-wallet-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977747,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:48:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:19Z",name:"How do I import a wallet?",title:"How do I import a wallet?",body:'<p>If you receive a QR code labeled as a "paper wallet" or "bitcoin private key", you can import it into Bread by tapping "Scan Private Key" and scanning the QR code.</p>\n<p>Any funds stored on the paper wallet/private key will be sent into your Bread, and will <strong>not</strong> remain on the paper wallet/private key.</p>\n<p>If you want to import a wallet created with Bread, use the "Start/Recover Another Wallet" function instead.</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:import-wallet"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002802453,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何匯入錢包？",body:"<p>如果你收到標示「紙錢包」或「比特幣私密金鑰」的 QR 碼，你可以藉由點擊「掃描私密金鑰」並掃描 QR 碼將其匯入 Bread 中。</p>\n<p>任何儲存於紙錢包／私密金鑰的資金將會發送至你的 Bread，且將 <strong>不會</strong> 再留存於紙錢包／私密金鑰上。</p>\n<p>如你想要匯入用 Bread 創建的錢包，就要使用「開始／回復另一個錢包」之功能。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:16Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002802433,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur importerar jag en plånbok?",body:'<p>Om du får en QR-kod märkt "pappersplånbok" eller "privat nyckel för bitcoin", kan du importera den till Bread genom att trycka på "Skanna privat nyckel" och skanna QR-koden.</p>\n<p>Alla tillgångar som lagrats i pappersplånboken/den privata nyckeln kommer att skickas till din Bread, och kommer <strong>inte</strong> att finnas kvar i pappersplånboken/den privata nyckeln.</p>\n<p>Om du vill importera en pappersplånbok som skapats med Bread, använd istället funktionen "Starta/Påbörja en annan plånbok".</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:53Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:16Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002790854,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como importo uma carteira?",body:'<p>Se receber um código QR identificado como "carteira de papel" ou "chave privada de bitcoin", pode importá-lo para o Bread ao tocar em "Ler Chave Privada" e ler o código QR.</p>\n<p>Todos os fundos armazenados na carteira de papel/chave privada serão enviados para o seu Bread, e <strong>não</strong> irão permanecer na carteira de papel/chave privada.</p>\n<p>Se quiser importar uma carteira criada com o Bread, use a função "Iniciar/Recuperar Outra Carteira".</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:53Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:15Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002790874,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何导入钱包？",body:"<p>如果您收到一个名为“纸钱包”或“比特币私钥”的二维码，您可以点击“扫描私钥”并扫描该二维码，即可将其导入 Bread。</p>\n<p>存在纸钱包/私钥中的所有资金都将被汇入您的 Bread，<strong>不会</strong>保留在纸钱包/私钥中。</p>\n<p>如果您想导入用 Bread 创建的钱包，请使用“创建/恢复其他钱包”功能。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:53Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:16Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002802413,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как мне импортировать кошелек?",body:"<p>Если вы получили QR-код, помеченный как «бумажный кошелек» или «закрытый биткоин-ключ», то вы можете импортировать его в Bread, нажав на «Отсканировать закрытый ключ» и отсканировав QR-код.</p>\n<p>Все средства, которые хранились на бумажном кошельке или кошельке с таким закрытым ключом, будут отправлены в ваш кошелек Bread, и <strong>не</strong> останутся на этом бумажном кошельке или кошельке с таким закрытым ключом.</p>\n<p>Если же вы хотите импортировать кошелек, созданный в Bread, то воспользуйтесь функцией «Создать или восстановить еще один кошелек».</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:53Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:15Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002790814,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come faccio ad importare un portafoglio?",body:'<p>Se ricevi un codice QR etichettato come "portafoglio cartaceo" o "chiave bitcoin privata", puoi importarla in Bread selezionando "Scansiona Chiave Privata" e inquadrando il codice QR.</p>\n<p>Tutti i fondi presenti sul portafoglio cartaceo/chiave privata verranno inviati al tuo Bread, e <strong>non</strong> saranno più disponibili sul portafoglio cartaceo/chiave privata.</p>\n<p>Se vuoi importare un portafoglio creato con Bread, usa la funzione "Avvia/Recupera un Altro Portafoglio".</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:15Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002790834,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ウォレットをインポートする方法は?",body:"<p>「ペーパーウォレット」または「ビットコインプライベートキー」とラベル付けされたQRコードを受け取られた場合には、「プリベートキーをスキャン」をタップしてQRコードをタップすることで、コードをBreadへとインポートすることができます。</p>\n<p>ペーパーウォレット/プライベートキー上に保管された資金はBreadへと送信され、ペーパーウォレット/プライベートキー上に残ることは<strong>ありません</strong>。</p>\n<p>Breadで作成されたウォレットへとインポートをご希望の場合には、「他のウォレットをスタート/復元」機能をご利用ください。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:15Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002802373,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je importer un portefeuille ?",body:"<p>Si vous recevez un code QR portant la mention « portefeuille papier » ou « clé privée bitcoin », vous pouvez l'importer dans Bread en touchant « Scanner la clé privée » puis en scannant le code QR.</p>\n<p>Tous les fonds stockés sur le portefeuille papier/clé privée seront envoyés sur votre Bread, et ne resteront <strong>pas</strong> dans le portefeuille papier/clé privée.</p>\n<p>Si vous souhaitez importer un portefeuille créé avec Bread, utilisez plutôt la fonction « Créer/Récupérer un autre portefeuille ».</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002802393,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe importeer ik een portemonnee?",body:'<p>Als je een QR-code ontvangt die gelabeld is als "papieren portemonnee" of "bitcoin privésleutel", kun je dit importeren in Bread door "Scan privésleutel" aan te klikken en de QR-code te scannen.</p>\n<p>Alle tegoeden in de papieren portemonnee/privésleutel zullen naar je Bread gestuurd worden en zullen <strong>niet</strong> in de papieren portemonnee/privésleutel blijven.</p>\n<p>Als je een portemonnee wilt importeren die gemaakt is met Bread, gebruik dan de "Start/Herstel een andere portemonnee" functie.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:15Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002790774,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie importiere ich eine Geldbörse?",body:"<p>Falls Sie einen als „Papiergeldbörse“ oder „Bitcoin-Privatschlüssel“ gekennzeichneten QR-Code erhalten, können Sie diesen in Bread importieren, indem Sie „Privatschlüssel scannen“ antippen und den QR-Code scannen.</p>\n<p>Jegliches in der Papiergeldbörse/auf dem Privatschlüssel gespeichertes Geld wird in Ihr Bread übertragen und verbleibt <strong>nicht</strong> in der Papiergeldbörse/auf dem Privatschlüssel.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie eine mit Bread erstellte Geldbörse importieren möchten, nutzen Sie stattdessen die Funktion „Eine andere Geldbörse erstellen/wiederherstellen“.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:51Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002790794,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo puedo importar un monedero?",body:'<p>Si recibes un código QR etiquetado como "monedero de papel" o "clave privada de Bitcoin", puedes importarlo a Bread pulsando "Escanear clave privada" y escanear el código QR.</p>\n<p>Todos los fondos almacenados en el monedero de papel o en la clave privada se enviarán a tu Bread y <strong>no</strong> permanecerán en el monedero de papel o en la clave privada.</p>\n<p>Si deseas importar un monedero creado con Bread, utiliza la función "Iniciar/Recuperar otro monedero".</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:51Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002802353,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan importerer jeg en tegnebog?",body:'<p>Hvis du modtager en QR-kode, der er mærket som en "paper wallet" eller "bitcoin private key", kan du importere den til Bread ved at trykke på "Scan privatnøgle" og scanne QR-koden.</p>\n<p>Alle midler, der er gemt på papirets tegnebog/private nøgle, vil blive sendt til din Bread-konto, og vil <strong>ikke</strong> fortsat blive på papirets tegnebog/private nøgle.</p>\n<p>Hvis du vil importere en tegnebog, der er oprettet med Bread, skal du bruge "Opret/gendan anden tegnebog"-funktionen i stedet.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:58:51Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:251724227,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979507/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234979507",source_id:234979507,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How do I import a wallet?",body:'<p>If you receive a QR code labeled as a "paper wallet" or "bitcoin private key", you can import it into Bread by tapping "Scan Private Key" and scanning the QR code.</p>\n<p>Any funds stored on the paper wallet/private key will be sent into your Bread, and will <strong>not</strong> remain on the paper wallet/private key.</p>\n<p>If you want to import a wallet created with Bread, use the "Start/Recover Another Wallet" function instead.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:48:56Z",updated_at:"2017-08-29T01:19:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:115000752694,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/115000752694-When-should-I-sync-the-blockchain-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000752694-When-should-I-sync-the-blockchain-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:0,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2017-07-21T07:28:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:18:16Z",name:"When should I sync the blockchain?",title:"When should I sync the blockchain?",body:"<p>Your Bread connects directly to the bitcoin network. This improves security and privacy, but also means sometimes your Bread can get out of sync with the network.</p>\n<p>Syncing with the blockchain can take a lot of time, and usually isn't necessary. If someone sent you money and it shows as confirmed in the blockchain yet it is not appearing in your wallet, your wallet may be out of sync. First check to make sure the address the money was sent to is correct.</p>\n<p>If you are trying to send money and constantly get error messages that your transaction was rejected, it could also mean your wallet is out of sync.</p>\n<p>In either of this cases, using this feature will rescan the blockchain to find your money and display it properly in your wallet.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:re-scan"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002790714,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該何時同步區塊鍊？",body:"<p>你的 Bread 直接與比特幣網路連接。這樣一來增進了安全性與隱私性，但也表示有時你的 Bread 可能會與網路不同步。</p>\n<p>與區塊鍊同步可能會花上很多時間，且通常非必要。如果有人發送金額給你並在區塊鍊上顯示已確認，但尚未出現在你的錢包中，你的錢包可能未同步。首先，確認金額送至的位址為正確的。</p>\n<p>如果你嘗試發款，但一直看到交易被拒絕的錯誤訊息，可能也代表你的錢包未同步。</p>\n<p>在此兩種情形下，使用此功能將重新掃描區塊練來找出你的錢，並妥善顯示於錢包中。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002802253,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"När bör jag synka blockkedjan?",body:"<p>Din Bread ansluter direkt till bitcoin-nätverket. Detta förbättrar säkerheten och integriteten, men innebär även att din Bread ibland kan vara osynkroniserad med nätverket.</p>\n<p>Att synka med blockkedjan kan ta mycket tid, och är vanligtvis inte nödvändigt. Om någon har skickat pengar till dig och det står som bekräftat i blockkedjan men ännu inte syns i plånboken, kan din plånbok vara osynkroniserad. Kontrollera först att adressen pengarna skickades till är korrekt.</p>\n<p>Om du försöker skicka pengar och för återkommande felmeddelanden om att din transaktion avvisades, kan det också betyda att din plånbok är osynkroniserad.</p>\n<p>I alla dessa fall kommer denna funktion att skanna om blockkedjan för att hitta dina pengar och visa dem korrekt i din plånbok.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002802273,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我应当在什么时候执行区块链同步操作？",body:"<p>您的 Bread 与比特币网络直接相连。这提高了安全性和隐私性，但也意味着有时您的 Bread 可能未与网络同步。</p>\n<p>区块链同步操作可能耗费很长时间，而且通常并没有这个必要。如果有人向您付款，并且显示为在区块链中已得到确认，然而这笔钱并未出现在您的钱包中，则您的钱包可能不同步。首先检查收款地址是否正确。 </p>\n<p>如果您尝试付款但不断收到出错消息，提醒您交易被拒绝，这也可能意味着您的钱包不同步。</p>\n<p>如果发生以上两种情况，使用此功能将会重新扫描区块链以找到您的钱款并将其正确地显示在您的钱包中。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002790674,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Quando devo sincronizar a blockchain?",body:"<p>O seu Bread liga-se diretamente à rede de bitcoin. Isto melhora a segurança e privacidade, mas também significa que às vezes o seu Bread pode ficar dessincronizado com a rede.</p>\n<p>Sincronizar com a blockchain pode demorar muito tempo e normalmente não é necessário. Se alguém lhe enviou dinheiro e estiver confirmado na blockchain mas ainda não aparece na sua carteira, a sua carteira poderá estar dessincronizada. Primeiro, verifique se o endereço para o qual foi enviado o dinheiro está correto.</p>\n<p>Se estiver a tentar enviar dinheiro e receber constantemente mensagens de erro a dizerem que a sua transação foi rejeitada, pode também significar que a sua carteira está dessincronizada.</p>\n<p>Em ambos os casos, usar esta funcionalidade irá reanalisar a blockchain para encontrar o seu dinheiro e mostrá-lo devidamente na sua carteira.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002790694,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Зачем мне синхронизировать блокчейн?",body:"<p>Ваш кошелек Bread подключается напрямую к биткоин-сети. Это улучшает безопасность и конфиденциальность, но при этом ваш кошелек Bread может рассинхронизироваться с сетью.</p>\n<p>Синхронизация с блокчейном может занять много времени, и обычно она необязательна. Если кто-то отправил вам деньги и транзакция отображается как подтвержденная в блокчейне, но не видна в вашем кошельке, то ваш кошелек может быть рассинхронизирован. Для начала проверьте, что деньги были отправлены на верный адрес.</p>\n<p>Если вы пытаетесь отправить деньги и постоянно получаете ошибку с комментарием, что ваша транзакция была отклонена, то это может значить, что ваш кошелек рассинхронизирован.</p>\n<p>В любой случае эта функция отсканирует блокчейн, найдет ваши средства и отобразит их в вашем кошельке.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002802233,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Wanneer moet ik de blockchain synchroniseren?",body:'<p>Je Bread verbindt automatisch met het bitcoin-netwerk. Dit verbetert de veiligheid en privacy, maar het betekent ook dat je Bread niet altijd gesynchroniseerd is met het netwerk.</p>\n<p>Het synchroniseren van de blockchain kan een hoop tijd in beslag nemen, en het is vaak niet nodig. Als iemand jou geld heeft gestuurd en het staat als "bevestigd" gelabeld in de blockchain terwijl het nog niet in je portemonnee te zien is,\n zou je portemonnee niet gesynchroniseerd kunnen zijn. Controleer eerst of het adres waar het geld naartoe gestuurd is, correct is.</p>\n<p>Als je geld probeert te versturen en je constant een foutmelding krijgt dat je transactie afgewezen is, kan het betekenen dat je portemonnee niet gesynchroniseerd is.</p>\n<p>In beide gevallen kan deze optie de blockchain nogmaals scannen om je geld te vinden en het op de juiste manier weer te geven in je portemonnee.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002790614,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wann sollte ich die Blockchain synchronisieren?",body:"<p>Ihr Bread verbindet sich direkt mit dem Bitcoin-Netzwerk. Dies verbessert die Sicherheit und Privatsphäre, kann aber manchmal auch zur Folge haben, dass Ihr Bread nicht mehr mit dem Netzwerk synchronisiert ist.</p>\n<p>Das Synchronisieren mit der Blockchain kann viel Zeit in Anspruch nehmen und ist normalerweise nicht notwendig. Falls Ihnen jemand Geld geschickt hat und es in der Blockchain als bestätigt angezeigt wird, aber noch nicht in Ihrer Geldbörse auftaucht, dann ist Ihre Geldbörse womöglich nicht synchronisiert.\nÜberprüfen Sie zuerst, ob die Adresse, an die das Geld versandt wurde, korrekt ist.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie versuchen, Geld zu versenden und ständig Fehlermeldungen erhalten, dass Ihre Transaktion abgewiesen wurde, könnte dies ebenfalls bedeuten, dass Ihre Geldbörse nicht synchronisiert ist.</p>\n<p>In beiden Fällen wird durch Nutzung dieses Features die Blockchain erneut gescannt, um Ihr Geld zu finden und es korrekt in Ihrer Geldbörse anzuzeigen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:11Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002790634,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Quand dois-je synchroniser la blockchain (chaîne de blocs) ?",body:"<p>Votre Bread se connecte directement au réseau bitcoin. Cela permet d'améliorer la sécurité et la confidentialité, mais cela signifie aussi que votre Bread peut parfois se désynchroniser du réseau.</p>\n<p>La synchronisation avec la blockchain (chaîne de blocs) peut prendre beaucoup de temps et n'est généralement pas nécessaire. Si quelqu'un vous a envoyé de l'argent et que l'envoi s'affiche comme confirmé sur la blockchain mais qu'il ne s'affiche pas dans votre portefeuille, votre portefeuille est peut-être désynchronisé. Vérifiez d'abord si l'adresse à laquelle l'argent a été envoyé est correcte.</p>\n<p>Si vous essayez d'envoyer de l'argent et recevez constamment des messages d'erreur vous indiquant que la transaction a été rejetée, cela peut signifier que votre portefeuille est désynchronisé.</p>\n<p>Dans l'un ou l'autre de ces cas, l'utilisation de cette fonctionnalité entraînera un nouveau balayage de la blockchain pour trouver votre argent et l'afficher correctement dans votre portefeuille.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002790654,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Quando devo sincronizzare la blockchain?",body:"<p>Il tuo Bread si collega direttamente alla rete bitcoin. Così facendo, la sicurezza e la privacy migliorano, ma purtroppo a volte Bread può perdere la sincronizzazione con la rete.</p>\n<p>La sincronizzazione con il blockchain può richiedere molto tempo, e di solito non è necessaria. Se qualcuno ti invia del denaro, con conferma sul blockchain, ma non appare sul tuo portafoglio, potrebbero esserci problemi di sincronizzazione. Ricordati di verificare che l'indirizzo d'invio del denaro sia corretto.</p>\n<p>Anche se provi ad inviare del denaro, ma ricevi continui messaggi d'errore per transazione rifiutata, potrebbero esserci problemi di sincronizzazione con il tuo portafoglio.</p>\n<p>In entrambi i casi, con questa funzionalità potrai effettuare una scansione completa del blockchain per trovare il tuo denaro e rettificare il saldo del tuo portafoglio.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:56:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115001819193,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cuándo debo sincronizar la cadena de bloques?",body:"<p>Tu Bread se conecta directamente a la red de Bitcoin. Esto mejora la seguridad y la privacidad, pero también significa que a veces tu Bread puede no estar sincronizado con la red.</p>\n<p>La sincronización con la cadena de bloques puede llevar mucho tiempo y, por lo general, no es necesaria. Si alguien te envió dinero y la transacción se muestra como confirmada en la cadena de bloques pero no aparece en tu monedero, es posible que este no esté sincronizado. Primero comprueba que la dirección a la que se envió el dinero es correcta.</p>\n<p> Si estás intentando enviar dinero y recibes constantemente mensajes de error que dicen que la transacción se rechazó, esto también podría significar que tu monedero no está sincronizado.</p>\n<p>En cualquiera de estos casos, el uso de esta función volverá a escanear la cadena de bloques para encontrar tu dinero y mostrarlo correctamente en tu monedero.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-08-10T00:52:23Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:11Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115001826314,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvornår bør jeg synkronisere blockchain?",body:"<p>Din Bread-konto forbindes direkte til bitcoin-netværket. Dette forbedrer sikkerheden og privatlivet, men betyder også, at der kan opstå tilfælde hvor din Bread-konto ikke synkronisere med netværket.</p>\n<p> Synkronisering med blockchain kan tage meget tid, og det er normalt ikke nødvendigt. Hvis nogen har sendt dig penge, og det vises som bekræftet i blockchain, men det ikke vises i din tegnebog, kan din tegnebog være ude af synkronisering. Kontroller først om adressen pengene blev sendt til er korrekt.</p>\n<p> Hvis du forsøger at sende penge og konstant får fejlmeddelelser om, at din transaktion blev afvist, kan det også betyde, at din tegnebog ikke er synkroniseret.</p>\n<p> I hver af disse tilfælde vil du ved hjælp af denne funktion kunne genscanne blockchain for at finde dine penge og vise det korrekt i din tegnebog.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-08-10T00:40:37Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:11Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115001816473,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ブロックチェーンはいつ同期させるべきでしょうか?",body:"<p>あなたのBreadはビットコインネットワークへと直接接続されます。これによりセキュリティとプライバシーが改善されますが、Breadのネットワークとの同期が一時的に失敗しまうこともあります。\n</p>\n<p>ブロックチェーンとの同期には長時間を要すことがあり、通常は不要です。あなたに送金が行われて、送金がブロックチェーン内で確認されているにも関わらず、ウォレットには表示されていない場合には同期が失敗している恐れがあります。まずは送金先のアドレスが正しいことをご確認ください。</p>\n<p>送信をしようとした時に取引が拒否されたというエラーメッセージが頻繁に表示される場合にはウォレットの同期が失敗している可能性があります。</p>\n<p>どちらの場合にも、この機能を使用することであなたの資金を検索する為にブロックチェーンが再スキャンされ、ウォレット上にも正しく表示されるようになります。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-08-09T23:09:50Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:115001219634,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/115000752694/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/115000752694",source_id:115000752694,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"When should I sync the blockchain?",body:"<p>Your Bread connects directly to the bitcoin network. This improves security and privacy, but also means sometimes your Bread can get out of sync with the network.</p>\n<p>Syncing with the blockchain can take a lot of time, and usually isn't necessary. If someone sent you money and it shows as confirmed in the blockchain yet it is not appearing in your wallet, your wallet may be out of sync. First check to make sure the address the money was sent to is correct.</p>\n<p>If you are trying to send money and constantly get error messages that your transaction was rejected, it could also mean your wallet is out of sync.</p>\n<p>In either of this cases, using this feature will rescan the blockchain to find your money and display it properly in your wallet.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-07-21T07:28:54Z",updated_at:"2017-08-29T01:19:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:235062488,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/235062488-How-can-I-send-bitcoin-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/235062488-How-can-I-send-bitcoin-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:1,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977707,created_at:"2016-11-17T23:18:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:03Z",name:"How can I send bitcoin?",title:"How can I send bitcoin?",body:'<p>To send money to someone you need to enter their <strong>bitcoin address</strong>. There are three different ways to enter this information depending on how you received it:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If you are presented with a QR code, press the "scan" button and scan the QR code.</li>\n<li>If you receive an address through email or text, copy the address to your device\'s clipboard and press the "paste" button.</li>\n<li>If you receive the address another way, tap the "To" label and use the keyboard to enter the address.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you have entered the payment address, tap the "Amount" label and enter the amount you wish to send. The button to the right will allow you to toggle the view between the amount of bitcoin to be sent or another currency.</p>\n<p>If you would like to save a note about this transaction, tap the "Memo" label. <strong>This note will only be visible to you</strong>, and will not be sent together with the transaction.</p>\n<p><strong>Important: </strong>If bitcoin is sent to the wrong address, it can not be refunded. When sending bitcoin, always check to make sure the address you are sending to is the same as the one that was given to you (comparing the first 5 or 6 digits is usually sufficient to make sure you are using the correct address).</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:send-bitcoin"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002804593,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"我該如何發送比特幣？",body:"<p>如要發款給某人，你需要輸入他們的 <strong>比特幣位址</strong>。根據收到位址的方式，共有三種不同方式來輸入此資訊：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如你收到的是 QR 碼，點擊「掃描」鍵並掃描 QR 碼。</li>\n<li>如你是由郵件或簡訊收到位址，複製位址到你設備的剪貼簿中，並點擊「貼上」鍵。</li>\n<li>如你是由其他方式收到位址，點擊「至」標籤，並使用鍵盤輸入位址。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>當你輸入付款位址後，點擊「金額」標籤並輸入你想發送的金額。右方的按鍵可讓你在要發送的比特幣或是其他貨幣間切換觀看。</p>\n<p>如你想要儲存關於此交易的筆記，點擊「備忘錄」標籤。<strong>這個筆記只有你能看到</strong>，並不會與交易內容一起送出。</p>\n<p><strong>重要：</strong>如果比特幣被送至錯誤位址，將無法退款。發送比特幣時，一定要檢查你發送的位址跟對方提供的位址相符（通常比對前 5 或 6 碼就可以確認你正使用對的位址）。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:45Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:01Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002804573,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"我如何用比特币付款？",body:"<p>若要给他人付款，您需要输入他们的<strong>比特币地址</strong>。地址信息存在三种不同的输入方式：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果他人向您出示一个二维码，点击“扫描”按钮并扫描该二维码。</li>\n<li>如果您通过电子邮件或短信收到一个地址，将该地址复制到您设备的剪贴板，并点击“粘贴”按钮。</li>\n<li>如果您通过其他途径收到地址，点击“地址”标签并使用键盘输入地址。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>一旦您已经输入支付地址，点击“金额”标签并输入您想要支付的金额。右侧按钮供您切换显示比特币金额或其他货币。</p>\n<p>如果您希望保存有关此次交易的备注信息，点击“备忘录”标签。<strong>此备注仅对您可见</strong>，并且不会随交易一同发出。</p>\n<p><strong>重要：</strong>如果比特币被汇往错误地址，则无法退还。在用比特币付款时，务必检查您输入的收款地址是否与收款人提供给您的地址完全一致（通常比较前 5 或 6 位字符就足以确认您是否在使用正确的地址）。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:44Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:01Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002792834,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como posso enviar bitcoin?",body:'<p>Para enviar dinheiro a alguém, tem de introduzir o seu <strong>endereço de bitcoin</strong>. Existem três formas diferentes de introduzir esta informação dependendo de como a recebeu:\n</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Se lhe for apresentado um código QR, pressione o botão "ler" e leia o código QR.</li>\n<li>Se receber um endereço por e-mail ou SMS, copie o endereço para a área de transferência do seu dispositivo e pressione o botão "colar".</li>\n<li>Se receber o endereço de outra forma, toque no identificador "Para" e use o teclado para introduzir o endereço.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Assim que tiver introduzido o endereço de pagamento, toque no identificador "Montante" e introduza o montante que deseja enviar. O botão à direita permite-lhe alternar a vista entre o montante de bitcoin a ser enviado ou outra moeda.</p>\n<p>Se quiser guardar uma nota sobre esta transação, toque no identificador "Nota". <strong>Esta nota ficará visível apenas para si</strong>, e não será enviada em conjunto com a transação.</p>\n<p><strong>Importante: </strong>Se enviar bitcoin para o endereço errado, não poderá ser reembolsado. Ao enviar bitcoin, verifique sempre se o endereço para o qual está a enviar é o mesmo que o que lhe foi dado (comparando os primeiros 5 ou 6 dígitos costuma ser suficiente para garantir que está a usar o endereço certo).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:44Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:00Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002792854,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как я могу отправить биткоины?",body:"<p>Чтобы отправить деньги кому-нибудь, вам нужно ввести <strong>биткоин-адрес</strong> получателя. Есть три разных способа ввести эту информацию – в зависимости от того, как именно вы ее получили:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Если вам показали QR-код, нажмите кнопку «Сканировать» и отсканируйте QR-код.</li>\n<li>Если вы получили адрес по эл. почте или СМС, скопируйте адрес в буфер обмена своего устройства и нажмите кнопку «Вставить».</li>\n<li>Если вы получили адрес другим способом, то нажмите на подпись «Кому» и введите адрес с клавиатуры.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>После ввода адреса нажмите на подпись «Сумма» и введите сумму, которую вы хотите отправить. Кнопка справа позволит вам переключаться между количеством биткоинов и эквивалентом в другой валюте.</p>\n<p>Если вы хотите добавить заметку об этой транзакции, то нажмите на подпись «Примечание». <strong>Это примечание будет видно только вам</strong> и не будет отправлено вместе с транзакцией.</p>\n<p><strong>Важно: </strong>если биткоины были отправлены на неправильный адрес, то их нельзя будет вернуть. Когда вы делитесь своим адресом, всегда проверяйте, совпадает ли он с адресом, который показан под вашим QR-кодом (обычно достаточно сравнить первые 5 или 6 символов, чтобы убедиться, что адрес верный).</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:44Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:00Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002792874,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur skickar jag bitcoin?",body:'<p>För att skicka pengar till någon måste du ange deras <strong>bitcoin-adress</strong>. Det finns tre olika sätt att ange denna information beroende på hur du mottog den:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Om du får en QR-kod, tryck på "skanna" och skanna QR-koden.</li>\n<li>Om du får en adress via e-post eller text, kopiera adressen till enhetens urklipp och tryck på "klistra in".</li>\n<li>Om du får adressen på ett annat sätt, tryck på "Till"-etiketten och använd tangentbordet för att ange adressen.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>När du har angett betalningsadressen trycker du på etiketten "Belopp" och anger det belopp du vill skicka. Knappen till höger gör att du kan växla mellan visning av beloppet som ska skickas i bitcoin eller i en annan valuta.</p>\n<p>Om du vill spara en anteckning om transaktionen trycker du på "Memo"-etiketten.<strong> Denna anteckning kommer endast att vara synlig för dig</strong> och kommer inte att skickas tillsammans med transaktionen.</p>\n<p><strong>Viktigt: </strong>Om bitcoin skickas till fel adress kan de inte återbetalas. När du skickar bitcoin, kontrollera alltid att den adress du skickar till är densamma som den som gavs till dig (att jämföra de första 5 eller 6 siffrorna är vanligtvis tillräckligt för att säkerställa att du använder rätt adress).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:44Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:01Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002804533,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment puis-je envoyer des bitcoins ?",body:"<p>Pour envoyer de l'argent à quelqu'un, vous devez entrer son <strong>adresse bitcoin</strong>. Il existe trois moyens différents d'entrer cette information selon la façon dont vous l'avez obtenue :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Si un code QR vous est présenté, appuyez sur le bouton « Scanner », puis scannez le code QR.</li>\n<li>Si vous avez reçu l'adresse par e-mail ou SMS, copiez l'adresse dans le presse-papiers de votre appareil et appuyez sur le bouton « Coller ».</li>\n<li>Si vous avez reçu l'adresse d'une autre façon, touchez l'étiquette « Pour » et utilisez le clavier pour entrer l'adresse.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Une fois que vous avez entré l'adresse de paiement, touchez l'étiquette « Montant » et entrez le montant que vous souhaitez envoyer. Le bouton à droite vous permettra de changer l'affichage entre le montant en bitcoins à envoyer ou une autre devise.</p>\n<p>Si vous souhaitez enregistrer une note sur cette transaction, touchez l'étiquette « Note ». <strong>Cette note ne sera visible que pour vous</strong> et ne sera pas envoyée avec la transaction.</p>\n<p><strong>Important : </strong>si des bitcoins sont envoyés à la mauvaise adresse, ils ne pourront pas être remboursés. Lorsque vous envoyez des bitcoins, vérifiez toujours que l'adresse à laquelle vous envoyez est identique à celle qui vous a été donnée (comparer les 5 ou 6 premiers chiffres est généralement suffisant pour vous assurer d'utiliser la bonne adresse).</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:43Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:59Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002804553,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"ビットコインを送金する方法は?",body:"<p>ビットコインを送金する為には、送金相手の <strong>ビットコインアドレス</strong>を入力していただく必要があります。この情報を入力するにはアドレスを入手した方法に応じて、3つの異なる方法があります:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>QRコードを提示された場合には、「スキャン」を押してQRコードをスキャンしてください。</li>\n<li>EメールまたはSMSメッセージでビットコインアドレスを入手した場合には、アドレスをデバイスのクリップボードへとコピーして「ペースト」ボタンを押してください。</li>\n<li>別の方法でビットコインアドレスを入手した場合には、「To」ラベルをタップしてキーボードでアドレスを入力してください。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>支払先のアドレスを入力したなら、「金額」ラベルをタップして送金したい金額を入力してください。右側のボタンで送金されるビットコインの金額と別の通貨間の表示を切り替えることが出来ます。</p>\n<p>この取引に関してのメモを保存したい場合には、「メモ」ラベルをタップしてください。<strong>このメモはあなただきに表示される</strong>もので、送金と共に送信されることはありません。</p>\n<p><strong>注意: </strong>ビットコインが間違ったアドレスへと送信された場合には、返金を受け取ることは不可能です。ビットコインを送金する際には、送金先のアドレスが通知されたアドレスと同じものであることを常にご確認ください。(アドレスが正しいものであることを確認する為には通常は最初の5・6桁を比べてみれば十分です)</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:43Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:00Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002792794,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come faccio ad inviare bitcoin?",body:"<p>Per inviare del denaro devi inserire l'<strong>indirizzo bitcoin</strong> del destinatario. Ci sono tre modi diversi per inserire questa informazione, a seconda di come la ricevi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Se ti viene fornito un codice QR, seleziona il pulsante \"scansiona\" e inquadra il codice QR.</li>\n<li>Se ricevi l'indirizzo via email o messaggio, basta copiare l'indirizzo negli appunti del tuo dispositivo e poi premere il pulsante \"incolla\".</li>\n<li>Se ricevi l'indirizzo in altro modo, premi sull'etichetta \"A\" e inserisci l'indirizzo usando la tastiera.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dopo aver inserito l'indirizzo di pagamento, premi sull'etichetta \"Importo\" e seleziona l'importo che vuoi inviare. Il pulsante a destra ti permetterà di vedere l'importo da inviare in bitcoin o in altra valuta.</p>\n<p>Se vuoi aggiungere degli appunti su questa transazione, premi sull'etichetta \"Memo\". <strong>Gli appunti saranno visibili solo a te</strong>, e non verranno inviati con la transazione.</p>\n<p><strong>Importante: </strong>È impossibile rimborsare i bitcoin inviati ad indirizzi sbagliati. Quando invii dei bitcoin, assicurati che l'indirizzo corrisponda a quello che ti è stato dato (tipicamente basta verificare la correttezza delle prime 5-6 cifre).</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:43Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:00Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002792814,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe kan ik bitcoin verzenden?",body:'<p>Om geld te versturen moet je hun <strong>bitcoinadres</strong> intypen. Er zijn drie verschillende manieren om deze informatie in te voeren, afhankelijk van hoe je deze hebt ontvangen:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Als je een QR-code hebt gekregen, klik op de "Scan" knop en scan de QR-code.</li>\n<li>Als je een adres hebt gekregen via e-mail of sms, kopieer het adres op het plakbord van je apparaat druk op de "Plakken" knop.</li>\n<li>Als je het adres op een andere manier hebt ontvangen, druk op het "Naar" label en gebruik het toetsenbord om het adres in te typen.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Als je het betalingsadres hebt ingetypt, druk op "bedrag" en voer het bedrag in wat je wilt versturen. De knop rechts zorgt ervoor dat je kunt switchen tussen de hoeveelheid bitcoin die verstuurd moet worden of een andere valuta.</p>\n<p>Als je een notitie over deze transactie wilt opslaan, klik op het "Memo" label. <strong>Deze notitie is alleen beschikbaar voor jou</strong>, en zal niet verstuurd worden met de transactie.</p>\n<p><strong>Belangrijk:</strong>Als bitcoin naar het verkeerde adres wordt gestuurd, kan dit niet ongedaan worden gemaakt. Wanneer je bitcoin verzendt, controleer dan dat het adres waarnaar het verzonden wordt hetzelfde is als het adres wat je hebt gekregen (de eerste 5 of 6 nummers controleren is vaak genoeg om het zeker te weten).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:43Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:00Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002804513,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo puedo enviar bitcoines?",body:'<p>Para enviar dinero a alguien, debes introducir su <strong>dirección de Bitcoin</strong>. Existen tres maneras diferentes de introducir esta información dependiendo de cómo la recibiste:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Si se te presenta un código QR, pulsa el botón "escanear" y escanea el código QR.</li>\n<li>Si recibes una dirección por correo electrónico o texto, copia la dirección en el portapapeles de tu dispositivo y pulsa el botón "pegar".</li>\n<li>Si recibes la dirección de otra manera, toca la etiqueta "Para" y usa el teclado para introducir la dirección.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Una vez que hayas introducido la dirección de pago, pulsa la etiqueta "Cantidad" e introduce la cantidad que desees enviar. El botón a la derecha te permitirá alternar entre la cantidad de bitcoines que quieres enviar u otra divisa.</p>\n<p>Si deseas guardar una nota sobre esta transacción, pulsa la etiqueta "Nota". <strong>Solo tú podrás ver esta nota</strong> y no se enviará junto con la transacción.</p>\n<p><strong>Importante:</strong> si se envían bitcoines a la dirección incorrecta, no se pueden reembolsar. Cuando envíes bitcoines, asegúrate siempre de que la dirección a la que los estés enviando sea la misma que la que se te ha dado (comparar los primeros 5 ó 6 dígitos suele ser suficiente para asegurarte de que estás usando la dirección correcta).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:42Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:59Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002792754,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan sender jeg bitcoin?",body:'<p> For at sende penge til nogen, skal du indtaste deres <strong>bitcoinadresse</strong>. Der er tre forskellige måder at indtaste disse oplysninger på, afhængigt af hvordan du har modtaget disse: </p>\n<ul>\n<li> Hvis du har modtaget en QR-kode, skal du trykke på "scan"-knappen og scanne QR-koden. </li>\n<li> Hvis du modtager en adresse via e-mail eller besked, skal du kopiere adressen til enhedens udklipsholder og trykke på knappen "Indsæt". </li>\n<li> Hvis du modtager adressen på anden måde, skal du trykke på "Til"-mærket og bruge tastaturet til at indtaste adressen.</li>\n</ul>\n<p> Når du har indtastet betalingsadressen, skal du trykke på "Beløb"-mærket og indtaste det beløb, du ønsker at sende. Knappen til højre giver dig mulighed for at skifte visning mellem antal bitcoin der skal sendes eller en anden valuta. </p>\n<p> Hvis du vil gemme en note om transaktionen, skal du trykke på "Memo"-mærket. <strong> Denne note vil kun være synlig for dig </strong>og vil ikke blive sendt sammen med transaktionen.</p>\n<p> <strong> Vigtigt: </strong>Hvis bitcoin sendes til den forkerte adresse, kan de ikke refunderes. Når du sender bitcoin, skal du altid kontrollere, at den adresse, du sender til, er den samme som den, der blev givet til dig (sammenligning af de første 5 eller 6 cifre er normalt nok til at sikre at du bruger den rigtige adresse).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:42Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:59Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002792774,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie kann ich Bitcoins versenden?",body:"<p>Um jemandem Geld zu schicken, müssen Sie die <strong>Bitcoin-Adresse</strong>des Empfängers eingeben. Es gibt drei verschiedene Wege, diese Information einzugeben, abhängig davon, auf welche Weise Sie diese erhalten haben:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Falls Ihnen ein QR-Code vorgelegt wird, drücken Sie den „Scannen“-Button und scannen Sie den QR-Code.</li>\n<li>Falls Sie eine Adresse per E-Mail oder SMS erhalten, kopieren Sie die Adresse in die Zwischenablage Ihres Geräts und drücken Sie den „Einfügen“-Button.</li>\n<li>Falls Sie die Adresse auf eine andere Weise erhalten, tippen Sie das „An“-Feld und geben Sie die Adresse über Ihre Tastatur ein.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nachdem Sie die Zahlungsadresse eingegeben haben, tippen Sie das „Betrag“-Feld an und geben Sie den Betrag ein, den Sie verschicken möchten.\nDer Button auf der rechten Seite ermöglicht es Ihnen, zwischen dem zu sendenden Betrag in Bitcoins oder der Ansicht in einer anderen Währung hin- und her zu wechseln.</p>\n<p>Falls Sie eine Notiz zu dieser Transaktion abspeichern möchten, tippen Sie auf das Feld „Notiz“. <strong>Diese Notiz ist nur für Sie sichtbar</strong> und wird nicht mit der Transaktion versendet.</p>\n<p><strong>Wichtig: </strong>Bitcoins, die an die falsche Adresse verschickt werden, können nicht erstattet werden. Überprüfen Sie beim Versenden von Bitcoins stets, dass die Adresse, an die Sie versenden, dieselbe ist wie die, die man Ihnen mitgeteilt hat (um sicherzustellen, dass Sie die korrekte Adresse verwenden, reicht es normalerweise aus, die ersten 5 oder 6 Stellen zu vergleichen).</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:42Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:08:59Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:252278328,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235062488/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/235062488",source_id:235062488,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How can I send bitcoin?",body:'<p>To send money to someone you need to enter their <strong>bitcoin address</strong>. There are three different ways to enter this information depending on how you received it:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If you are presented with a QR code, press the "scan" button and scan the QR code.</li>\n<li>If you receive an address through email or text, copy the address to your device\'s clipboard and press the "paste" button.</li>\n<li>If you receive the address another way, tap the "To" label and use the keyboard to enter the address.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you have entered the payment address, tap the "Amount" label and enter the amount you wish to send. The button to the right will allow you to toggle the view between the amount of bitcoin to be sent or another currency.</p>\n<p>If you would like to save a note about this transaction, tap the "Memo" label. <strong>This note will only be visible to you</strong>, and will not be sent together with the transaction.</p>\n<p><strong>Important: </strong>If bitcoin is sent to the wrong address, it can not be refunded. When sending bitcoin, always check to make sure the address you are sending to is the same as the one that was given to you (comparing the first 5 or 6 digits is usually sufficient to make sure you are using the correct address).</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-17T23:18:52Z",updated_at:"2017-08-29T01:19:26Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:234979447,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/234979447-Is-Bread-free-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234979447-Is-Bread-free-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:2,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977707,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:45:35Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:22:10Z",name:"Is Bread free?",title:"Is Bread free?",body:"<p>Bread's core product is and always will be 100% free and open source. Additional, opt-in features such as the ability to buy bitcoin may be offered through the app for a fee.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:[],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002804833,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"bread 錢包是免費的嗎？",body:"<p>Bread 錢包的核心產品永遠都是 100% 免費和開放資源的。額外的選擇性功能如購買比特幣則可在 app 中付費操作。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:51Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:06Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002804753,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Is Bread gratis?",body:"<p>Het kernproduct van Bread is 100% gratis en open bron. Daarbij kunnen opt-in functies zoals het kopen van bitcoin via de app gratis worden aangeboden.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:50Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:06Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002804773,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"O Bread é gratuito?",body:"<p>O produto principal do Bread é e sempre será 100% gratuito e open source. Funcionalidades adicionais e opcionais como a possibilidade de comprar bitcoin poderão ser proporcionados na aplicação por uma taxa.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:50Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:07Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002804793,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Бесплатный ли это кошелек?",body:"<p>Основной продукт компании всегда будет на 100% бесплатным, а код будет открыт. Кроме этого, дополнительные функции, например, возможность купить биткоины через приложение, могут быть доступными за дополнительную плату.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:50Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:06Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002804813,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Är breadplånboken gratis?",body:"<p>Breadplånbokens kärnprodukt är och kommer alltid att vara 100% gratis och öppen källkod. Ytterligare, valbara funktioner som förmågan att köpa bitcoin kan erbjudas för en avgift via appen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:50Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:06Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002793114,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"Bread 钱包是否免费？",body:"<p>Bread 钱包的核心产品是且始终将是 100% 免费和开源。此外，可能会通过此应用提供一些付费的可选功能，例如比特币购买功能。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:50Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:06Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002793074,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Bread est-il gratuit ?",body:"<p>Le produit de base de Bread est 100 % gratuit et open source et le restera toujours. Des fonctionnalités supplémentaires facultatives comme la possibilité d'acheter des bitcoins pourraient être proposées dans l'appli moyennant des frais.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:49Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:06Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002793094,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Bread è gratuito?",body:"<p>Il prodotto centrale di Bread sarà sempre gratuito al 100% ed open source. Funzionalità aggiuntive opzionali, come la possibilità di acquistare i bitcoin,  potrebbero essere presenti nell'app ad un costo.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:49Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:06Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002804713,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Es Bread gratis?",body:"<p>El producto principal de Bread es y siempre será 100 % gratuito y de código abierto. Se pueden ofrecer características adicionales como la posibilidad de comprar bitcoines a través de la aplicación por un cargo adicional. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:49Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:05Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002804733,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"Breadは無料なのでしょうか?",body:"<p>Breadの重要な機能性は100%無料かつオープンソースであり続けます。アプリを通してのビットコイン購入など追加的な任意機能は一定の料金で入手可能にされます。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:49Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:22:10Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002793054,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Er Bread gratis?",body:"<p>Breads kerneprodukt er og vil altid være 100% gratis og open source. Udover det tilbydes opt-in funktioner, såsom evnen til at købe bitcoin, via appen mod et gebyr.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:48Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:05Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002804693,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Ist Bread kostenlos?",body:"<p>Breads Hauptprodukt ist und wird stets 100 % kostenlos und Open Source sein. Zusätzlich können optionale Features, wie die Möglichkeit, Bitcoins zu kaufen, für eine Gebühr in der App angeboten werden.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:48Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:10:05Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:251724167,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234979447/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234979447",source_id:234979447,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"Is Bread free?",body:"<p>Bread's core product is and always will be 100% free and open source. Additional, opt-in features such as the ability to buy bitcoin may be offered through the app for a fee.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:45:35Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:01:57Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:235053348,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/235053348-What-is-the-fingerprint-touch-ID-spending-limit-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/235053348-What-is-the-fingerprint-touch-ID-spending-limit-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:2,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2016-11-17T20:09:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:06Z",name:"What is the fingerprint/touch ID spending limit?",title:"What is the fingerprint/touch ID spending limit?",body:"<p>Fingerprint authorization is a convenient shortcut to authorize payments and view your balance in Bread, but it is not a strong security solution. Security experts have proved it is possible to lift fingerprints from a stolen device and use them to trick that device's fingerprint reader into unlocking the device.</p>\n<p>To ensure the majority of your funds are safe in the event your phone is stolen, Bread sets a limit to the amount of money that can be sent with only a fingerprint. If you or anyone else tries to send more than that limit (accumulative), your wallet passcode will be required.</p>\n<p>You can change the limit by choosing Fingerprint Authorization Limit in the Bread settings.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:fingerprint-spending-limit"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002793034,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"什麼是指紋／touch ID 花費上限？",body:"<p>指紋授權是一個方便的捷徑，可讓你授權付款及觀看 bread 錢包中的餘額，但並不是最安全的方式。安全性專家已證實從偷來的設備上擷取指紋，並使用在其指紋辨識器上解鎖是可行的。</p>\n<p>為了確保在手機被偷的情形下你大部分的資金皆安全，bread 錢包設定了只用指紋就能發送的金額上限。如果你或其他人嘗試發送超過限制（累計計算），將會需要你錢包的密碼。</p>\n<p>你可以在 bread 錢包設定中選擇「指紋授權上限」改變此限制。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:48Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:04Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002804673,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"什么是指纹/Touch ID 开支限额？",body:"<p>指纹授权是授权支付和查看您 Bread 钱包余额的一种快捷方式，但它不是一种很可靠的安全解决方案。安全专家已证实，可以从失窃设备上提取指纹并用该指纹欺骗设备的指纹识别器解锁该设备。</p>\n<p>为了确保在手机失窃的情况下绝大部分资金依然能够安全无虞，Bread 钱包给单凭指纹付款的金额设置了一个上限。如果您或其他人试图付出超过该限额的资金（累计），则必须输入钱包密码。</p>\n<p>您可以在 Bread 钱包设置中选择指纹授权限额以更改该限额。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:48Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:04Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002792994,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Wat is de uitgavelimiet via vingerafdruk/touch ID?",body:"<p>Vingerafdrukauthorizatie is een gemakkelijke manier om betalingen goed te keuren en je saldo in Bread te bekijken, maar het is geen sterke veiligheidsoplossing. Veiligheidsexperts hebben bewezen dat het mogelijk is om vingerafdrukken van een gestolen apparaat te halen en deze te gebruiken om met deze afdrukken in te loggen op het apparaat.</p>\n<p>Om zeker te weten dat het overgrote deel van je saldo veilig is als je telefoon gestolen wordt, stelt Bread een limiet in op de hoeveelheid geld die verstuurd kan worden via een vingerafdruk. Als jij of iemand anders probeert om meer geld te versturen dan die limiet (accumulerend), wordt er om je PIN gevraagd.</p>\n<p>Je kunt de limiet aanpassen door Vingerafdrukauthorisatielimiet te kiezen in de instellingen van Bread.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:47Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002793014,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Qual é o limite de gastos da impressão digital/touch ID?",body:"<p>A autorização de impressão digital é um atalho conveniente para autorizar pagamentos e consultar o seu saldo no Bread, mas não é uma boa solução de segurança. Especialistas em segurança provaram que é possível retirar impressões digitais de um dispositivo roubado e usá-las para enganar o leitor de impressões digitais do dispositivo para o desbloquear.</p>\n<p>Para garantir que a maioria dos seus fundos estão seguros caso o seu telemóvel seja roubado, o Bread definiu um limite para a quantia de dinheiro que pode ser enviada com apenas uma impressão digital. Se você ou alguém tentar enviar mais do que o limite (cumulativamente), será solicitado o código da sua carteira.</p>\n<p>Pode alterar o limite ao escolher Limite de Autorização de Impressão Digital nas definições do Bread.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:47Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:20Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002804633,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Какой лимит у трат, совершаемых при помощи отпечатка пальца/Touch ID?",body:"<p>Авторизация по отпечатку пальца – это удобный способ авторизации платежей и просмотра баланса кошелька, но это не гарантия полной безопасности. Эксперты по безопасности выяснили, что можно снять отпечатки пальцев с украденного устройства и использовать их, чтобы обмануть сканер устройства и разблокировать его.</p>\n<p>Чтобы гарантировать безопасность большей части ваших средств даже в том случае, если телефон будет украден, в кошельке установлено ограничение на ту сумму, которую можно отправить при помощи отпечатка пальца. Если вы или кто-то другой попробует превысить установленный лимит отправки (суммы разных платежей суммируются), то потребуется ввод ПИН-кода.</p>\n<p>Вы можете изменить лимит при помощи опции «Лимит для авторизации по отпечатку пальца» в настройках кошелька.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:47Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:03Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002804653,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Vad är utgiftsgränsen för fingeravtryck/Touch ID?",body:"<p>Auktorisering med fingeravtryck är en bekväm genväg för att auktorisera betalningar och visa ditt saldo i breadplånboken, men det är inte en kraftfull säkerhetslösning. Säkerhetsexperter har visat att det är möjligt att få fram fingeravtryck från en stulen enhet och använda dem för att lura enhetens fingeravtrycksläsare att låsa upp enheten.</p>\n<p>För att säkerställa att de flesta av dina pengar är säkra i händelse av att din telefon blir stulen, anger bread-plånboken en gräns för hur mycket pengar som kan skickas endast med hjälp av fingeravtryck. Om du eller någon annan försöker skicka mer än den gränsen (ackumulativ) krävs lösenkoden för din plånbok.</p>\n<p>Du kan ändra gränsen genom att välja Gräns för auktorisering med fingeravtryck i breadplånbokens inställningar.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:47Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:03Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002792974,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Cos'è il limite di spesa per l'impronta/touch ID?",body:"<p>L'autorizzazione con impronta è una scorciatoia comoda per autorizzare i pagamenti e per vedere il saldo del tuo Bread, ma non è ottimale in termini di sicurezza. Diversi esperti del settore hanno dimostrato che è possibile prelevare le impronte presenti su un dispositivo rubato ed usarle per sbloccare il dispositivo tramite il lettore di impronte.</p>\n<p>Per garantire la sicurezza della maggior parte dei tuoi fondi anche in caso di furto del cellulare, il Bread impone un limite all'importo inviabile tramite impronta digitale. Se tu, o chiunque altro, prova ad inviare un importo superiore a tale limite (cumulativo), verrà richiesto il codice del portafoglio.</p>\n<p>Puoi modificare il limite nelle impostazioni del Bread, usando l'opzione Limite per Autorizzazione con Impronta.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:46Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002804613,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"指紋認証/touch IDによる支払い限度額は?",body:"<p>指紋認証による承認は支払い承認とBreadの残高確認への便利なショートカット方法です。しかしながら、完全に強固なセキュリティソリューションではありません。セキュリティの専門家により盗難されたデバイスから指紋を読み取り、指紋認証リーダーに応用させデバイスのロック解除が可能であることを証明されています。</p>\n<p>携帯電話が盗難されてしまった場合にもあなたの資金が安全に保管できるように、Breadには指紋認証により送金可能な限度額が設定されています。本人を含めて誰かが (合計)限度額以上を送信しようとした場合には、ウォレットのパスコード入力が必要となります。\n</p>\n<p>限度額はBreadの設定内で指紋認証承認限度額を選択することで変更することができます。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:46Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:05Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002792914,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Was ist das Fingerabdruck/Touch ID-Ausgabelimit?",body:"<p>Fingerabdruck-Autorisierung ist eine praktische Abkürzung, um Zahlungen zu autorisieren und Ihren Kontostand in Bread anzusehen, sie stellt allerdings keine starke Sicherheitslösung dar. Sicherheitsexperten haben bewiesen, dass es möglich ist, einem gestohlenen Gerät Fingerabdrücke zu entnehmen und mit diesen den Fingerabdruckleser des Geräts dazu zu verleiten, das Gerät zu entsperren.</p>\n<p>Um sicherzustellen, dass der Großteil Ihres Vermögens im Falle eines Handydiebstahls sicher ist, limitiert Bread den Geldbetrag, der mit nur einem Fingerabdruck versendet werden kann. Falls Sie oder jemand anderes versuchen, mehr Geld zu versenden, als das Limit (kumulativ) erlaubt, müssen Sie Ihr Geldbörsenkennwort eingeben.</p>\n<p>Sie können das Limit ändern, indem Sie „Fingerabdruck-Autorisierungslimit“ in den Bread-Einstellungen auswählen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:46Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002792934,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cuál es el límite de gasto cuando se usa la identificación de huellas dactilares/identificación táctil?",body:"<p>La autorización de huellas dactilares es un cómodo atajo para autorizar pagos y ver tu saldo en Bread, pero no es una solución de seguridad sólida. Los expertos en seguridad han demostrado que es posible levantar las huellas dactilares de un dispositivo robado y usarlas para engañar al lector de huellas dactilares de ese dispositivo para desbloquearlo.</p>\n<p>Para asegurar que la mayoría de tus fondos esté segura en caso de que te roben el teléfono, Bread establece un límite a la cantidad de dinero que se puede enviar con solo una huella dactilar. Si tu o cualquier otra persona intenta enviar más de ese límite (acumulativo), será necesario introducir el código del monedero.</p>\n<p>Puedes cambiar el límite seleccionando la opción Límite para autorización dactilar desde la configuración de Bread.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:46Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002792954,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Quelle est la limite de dépense par empreinte digitale/Touch ID ?",body:"<p>L'autorisation par empreinte digitale est un raccourci pratique pour autoriser des paiements et consulter votre solde dans Bread, mais ce n'est pas une solution de sécurité robuste. Des experts de la sécurité ont prouvé qu'il était possible de récupérer les empreintes digitales d'un appareil volé et de les utiliser pour forcer le lecteur d'empreinte digitale de l'appareil à déverrouiller l'appareil.</p>\n<p>Pour garantir la sécurité de la majorité de vos fonds en cas de vol de votre téléphone, Bread définit une limite à la somme d'argent pouvant être envoyée en utilisant seulement une empreinte digitale. Si vous ou une autre personne essayez d'envoyer plus que cette limite (cumulative), le code de votre portefeuille sera demandé.</p>\n<p>Vous pouvez modifier la limite en choisissant « Limite d'autorisation par empreinte digitale » dans les réglages de Bread.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:46Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:19Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002792894,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvad er forbrugsgrænsen for fingeraftryk/touch-ID?",body:"<p>Fingeraftryksautorisation er en praktisk genvej til at godkende betalinger og se din saldo i Bread, men det er ikke en stærk sikkerhedsløsning. Sikkerhedseksperter har bevist, at det er muligt at genbruge fingeraftryk fra en stjålet enhed og bruge dem til at narre enhedens fingeraftrykslæser til at låse enheden op. </p>\n<p> For at sikre at størstedelen af dine penge er sikret hvis din telefon bliver stjålet, fastsætter Bread en grænse for, hvor mange penge der kan sendes kun med et fingeraftryk. Hvis du eller nogen anden forsøger at sende mere end den grænse (akkumulerende), er din tegnebogskode påkrævet. </p>\n<p> Du kan ændre grænsen ved at vælge Fingeraftrykautorisationsgrænse i indstillingerne for Bread. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:45Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:252173648,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/235053348/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/235053348",source_id:235053348,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"What is the fingerprint/touch ID spending limit?",body:"<p>Fingerprint authorization is a convenient shortcut to authorize payments and view your balance in Bread, but it is not a strong security solution. Security experts have proved it is possible to lift fingerprints from a stolen device and use them to trick that device's fingerprint reader into unlocking the device.</p>\n<p>To ensure the majority of your funds are safe in the event your phone is stolen, Bread sets a limit to the amount of money that can be sent with only a fingerprint. If you or anyone else tries to send more than that limit (accumulative), your wallet passcode will be required.</p>\n<p>You can change the limit by choosing Fingerprint Authorization Limit in the Bread settings.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-17T20:09:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:01:57Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:234758088,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/234758088-Why-does-it-cost-money-to-send-a-transaction-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234758088-Why-does-it-cost-money-to-send-a-transaction-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!0,position:3,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977707,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:41:44Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T21:43:58Z",name:"Why does it cost money to send a transaction?",title:"Why does it cost money to send a transaction?",body:'<p>Bread does not charge any fees to send a transaction. However, the bitcoin network does require a fee, called a "transaction fee". This fee is calculated based on the amount of activity in your wallet, and is always displayed to you before you authorize a payment to be sent.</p>\n<p>Wallets that receive many small payments before trying to send one large transaction may be charged a higher transaction fee. If possible, combining the payments you receive into a smaller number of larger transactions can keep your transaction fees low.</p>',source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:transaction-fees"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002804933,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"為何發款交易要收費？",body:"<p>Bread 錢包在發送交易時不收任何費用。但是比特幣網路會收「交易費」。此費用依據你錢包的活動數量計算，且在你每次授權付款前皆會顯示。</p>\n<p>收到很多小額款項並接著發送大額交易的錢包可能會被收取更高的交易費。如果可以的話，合併收款至少量高額的交易能夠節省交易費。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:09Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002793254,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Почему за отправку транзакции необходимо платить?",body:"<p>Приложение не берет деньги за отправку транзакций, однако биткоин-сеть требует оплаты сбора, который называется «сбор за транзакцию». Этот сбор зависит от активности вашего кошелька и всегда отображается перед авторизацией платежа.</p>\n<p>Кошельки, которые до отправки одной крупной транзакции получали множество мелких платежей, будут платить более крупный сбор. При возможности комбинируйте платежи, которые вам нужно получить, в небольшое число крупных транзакций, чтобы ваши сборы за транзакцию были низкие.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:53Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:08Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002804873,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Porque é que custa dinheiro enviar uma transação?",body:'<p>O Bread não cobra taxas para enviar uma transação. No entanto, a rede de bitcoin requer uma taxa chamada "taxa de transação". Esta taxa é calculada com base na quantidade de atividade na sua carteira, e é-lhe sempre mostrada antes de autorizar o envio de um pagamento.</p>\n<p>Carteiras que recebem muitos pagamentos pequenos antes de tentar enviar uma transação grande poderão ter de pagar uma taxa de transação superior. Se for possível, combinar os pagamentos que recebe num número inferior de transações maiores poderá diminuir as suas taxas de transação.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:53Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:26Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002804893,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Varför kostar det pengar att genomföra en transaktion?",body:'<p>Breadplånboken tar inte ut några avgifter för att genomföra en transaktion. Bitcoin-nätverket tar dock ut en avgift, kallad "transaktionsavgift". Denna avgift beräknas utifrån aktiviteten i din plånbok och visas alltid innan du godkänner en betalning.</p>\n<p>Plånböcker som tar emot många små betalningar innan de försöker skicka en stor transaktion kan debiteras en högre transaktionsavgift. Om det är möjligt att kombinera betalningarna du tar emot till ett fåtal större transaktioner kan dina transaktionsavgifter hållas låga.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:53Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:08Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002804913,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"为什么付款交易要花钱？",body:"<p>Bread 钱包并不收取任何付款交易手续费。不过，比特币网络确实要收一笔名为“交易费”的手续费。此项手续费根据您钱包的活动量计算得出，并且总是在您授权支付前向您显示。</p>\n<p>如果钱包收入很多笔小额款项，然后试图付出一笔大额交易款项，那么可能被收取较高的交易费。可能的话，将您收入的付款合并为几笔较大数额的交易，这么做能够保持较低的交易费。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:53Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:09Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002793234,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"送金に料金がかかるのはなぜでしょう?",body:"<p>送金に対してBreadはいかなる課金も行うことはありません。しかし、ビットコインネットワークには「取引料金」と言う料金が必要とされます。この料金はあなたのウォレット内のアクティビティ数により計算され、常に支払いの送信を承認する前に表示されます。</p>\n<p>多額の送金を行う前に沢山の少額の支払いが受領されたウォレットには通常よりも高めの取引料金が課金される場合があります。可能であれば、受領する支払いを数回の多額の取引にまとめることで取引料金を下げておくことができます。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:10Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002804853,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Waarom kost het geld om een transactie te doen?",body:'<p>Bread brengt geen kosten in rekening om een transactie te versturen. Het bitcoinnetwerk brengt wel kosten in rekening;  "overschrijvingskosten". Deze kosten zijn berekend op basis van de hoeveelheid activiteit in je portemonnee en worden altijd weergegeven voordat je een betaling goedkeurt.</p>\n<p>Portemonnees die veel kleine betalingen ontvangen voordat ze één grote betaling verzenden kunnen hogere overschrijvingskosten berekend krijgen. Voeg de betalingen die je krijgt samen tot een kleiner aantal van grotere transacties wanneer mogelijk, zodat je overschrijvingskosten laag blijven.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:26Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002793174,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Por qué enviar una transacción cuesta dinero?",body:'<p>Bread no cobra honorarios por enviar una transacción. Sin embargo, la red de Bitcoin requiere una cuota, llamada "tarifa de transacción". Esta cuota se calcula en función de la cantidad de actividad en tu monedero y siempre se te muestra antes de que autorices el envío de un pago.</p>\n<p>Los monederos que reciben muchos pequeños pagos antes de intentar enviar una transacción grande pueden sufrir una tarifa de transacción más alta. Si es posible, combina los pagos que recibas en un número menor de transacciones más grandes ya que puede mantener tus tarifas de transacción más bajas.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002793194,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Pourquoi l'envoi d'une transaction est-il payant ?",body:"<p>Bread ne facture aucun frais pour envoyer une transaction. Cependant, l'utilisation du réseau bitcoin nécessite des frais, appelés « frais de transaction ». Ces frais sont calculés en fonction de l'activité dans votre portefeuille, et s'affichent toujours avant que vous n'autorisiez l'envoi d'un paiement.</p>\n<p>Les portefeuilles qui reçoivent de nombreux paiements de petites sommes avant d'envoyer une transaction importante pourraient devoir payer des frais de transaction plus élevés. Lorsque c'est possible, rassemblez les paiements que vous recevez en un plus petit nombre de transactions plus importantes pour limiter vos frais de transaction.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002793214,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Perché devo pagare per inviare una transazione?",body:"<p>Bread non richiede commissioni per inviare una transazione. Tuttavia, la rete bitcoin richiede una commissione, detta \"commissione di transazione\". Questa commissione è calcolata in basta ai livelli di attività del tuo portafoglio, e ti viene sempre mostrata prima dell'autorizzazione all'invio del pagamento.</p>\n<p>I portafogli che ricevono molti pagamenti piccoli prima di inviare una transazione più cospicua potrebbero incorrere in commissioni di transazione più elevate. Se è possibile, ti conviene combinare i pagamenti in entrata in transazioni più grandi per ridurre le commissioni di transazione.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:52Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002793134,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvorfor koster det penge at sende en transaktion?",body:'<p>Bread opkræver ikke gebyrer for at sende en transaktion. Bitcoin-netværket kræver imidlertid et gebyr, der kaldes et "transaktionsgebyr". Gebyret beregnes ud fra mængden af aktivitet i din tegnebog og vises altid, før du giver tilladelse til, at en betaling skal sendes. </p>\n<p> Tegnebøger der modtager mange små betalinger, før de forsøger at sende en stor transaktion, kan risikere at blive opkrævet et højere transaktionsgebyr. Hvis det er muligt, bør du kombinere de betalinger du modtager i et mindre antal større transaktioner. Dette kan holde dine transaktionsgebyrer lave.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:51Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:24Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002793154,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Warum kostet das Versenden einer Transaktion Geld?",body:"<p>Bread erhebt keine Gebühren für Transaktionen. Das Bitcoin-Netzwerk verlangt allerdings eine sogenannte „Transaktionsgebühr“. Diese Gebühr wird anhand der Aktivität in Ihrer Geldbörse errechnet und wird Ihnen stets angezeigt, bevor Sie eine Transaktion autorisieren.</p>\n<p>Geldbörsen, die vor dem Tätigen einer großen Transaktion viele kleine Zahlungen empfangen, wird möglicherweise eine höhere Transaktionsgebühr berechnet. Empfangene Zahlungen falls möglich zu einer kleineren Anzahl größerer Transaktionen zu kombinieren kann Ihre Transaktionsgebühren niedrig halten.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:51Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:25Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:251532928,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758088/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234758088",source_id:234758088,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"Why does it cost money to send a transaction?",body:'<p>Bread does not charge any fees to send a transaction. However, the bitcoin network does require a fee, called a "transaction fee". This fee is calculated based on the amount of activity in your wallet, and is always displayed to you before you authorize a payment to be sent.</p>\n<p>Wallets that receive many small payments before trying to send one large transaction may be charged a higher transaction fee. If possible, combining the payments you receive into a smaller number of larger transactions can keep your transaction fees low.</p>',outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:41:44Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:01:58Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:234758488,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/234758488-What-are-push-notifications-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234758488-What-are-push-notifications-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:3,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:52:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:14Z",name:"What are push notifications?",title:"What are push notifications?",body:"<p>If you enable push notifications, Bread will have the ability to notify you of wallet activity even when you don't have the Bread app open. If you would like to be notified immediately every time you receive a payment or some other action completes, turn on this feature. If you do not want to be notified at all unless you have the Bread app open, turn off push notifications.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:[],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002793434,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"什麼是推送通知？",body:"<p>如果你開啟推送通知，bread 錢包將得以在你未開啟 app 時也能通知你錢包動態。如果你希望在每次收到款項或是其他動作完成時都被即刻告知，請開啟此功能。如果你只想要在 bread 錢包開啟狀態下收到通知，請關閉推送通知。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:57Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002804993,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"什么是推送通知？",body:"<p>如果您启用推送通知，Bread 钱包将能够向您通报钱包活动情况，即使您未打开 Bread 钱包也如此。如果您希望在每次收到一笔支付款或完成某项其他操作时立即收到通知，请打开此功能。如果您只希望在打开 Bread 钱包应用时收取通知，那么请关闭推送通知。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002793394,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"O que são notificações push?",body:"<p>Se ativar as notificações push, o Bread terá a possibilidade de notificá-lo de atividades na carteira mesmo quando não tiver a aplicação do Bread aberta. Se quiser ser notificado imediatamente sempre que receber um pagamento ou que outra ação for concluída, ative esta funcionalidade. Se não quiser ser notificado a menos que tenha a aplicação aberta, desative as notificações push.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:29Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002793414,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Vad är push-aviseringar?",body:"<p>Om du aktiverar push-aviseringar har breadplånboken möjlighet att meddela dig om plånboksaktivitet även när du inte har breadplånboks-appen öppen. Om du vill bli underrättad omedelbart varje gång du får en betalning eller någon annan åtgärd slutförs, slå på den här funktionen. Om du inte vill bli underrättad alls såvida du inte har breadplånboks-appen öppen ska du stänga av push-aviseringar.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:11Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002804973,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Что такое push-уведомления?",body:"<p>Если вы включите push-уведомления, кошелек сможет уведомлять вас об активности в кошельке даже если приложение кошелька не открыто. Включите эту функцию, если вы хотите получать незамедлительные уведомления каждый раз, когда вы получаете платеж или происходит какое-то другое действие. Если вы не хотите получать уведомления, когда ваш кошелек не открыт, то отключите push-уведомления.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:56Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:11Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002793314,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"À quoi servent les notifications push ?",body:"<p>Si vous activez les notifications push, Bread pourra vous notifier de l'activité du portefeuille même lorsque vous ne laissez pas l'appli Bread ouverte. Si vous souhaitez être notifié immédiatement à chaque fois que vous recevez un paiement ou qu'une autre action est effectuée, activez cette fonctionnalité. Si vous ne souhaitez pas être notifié du tout sauf si l'appli Bread est ouverte, désactivez les notifications push.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:28Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002793334,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Cosa sono le notifiche push?",body:"<p>Se attivi le notifiche push, Bread potrà notificarti, in caso di attività sul portafoglio, anche quando l'app non è aperta. Attiva questa funzionalità se vuoi essere notificato immediatamente ogni volta che ricevi un pagamento o in caso di altre azioni. Se invece vuoi ricevere le notifiche solo quando l'app Bread è aperta, disattiva le notifiche push.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:29Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002793354,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"プッシュ通知とは?",body:"<p>プッシュ通知を有効にした場合には、Breadのアプリが開かれていない場合でもウォレットのアクティビティに関する通知が行われます。支払いを受け取ったり、他のアクションが完了された際に即座に通知を受けることを希望される場合には、この機能を有効にしてください。Breadアプリが開かれている場合以外は通知の受け取りを希望しない場合には、プッシュ通知をオフにしてください。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002793374,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Wat zijn pushnotificaties?",body:"<p>Wanneer je pushnotificaties aan zet, heeft Bread de mogelijkheid om je notificaties te sturen van activiteit van je portemonnee, zelfs wanneer je de Bread-app niet open hebt. Als je graag meteen een notificatie krijgt wanneer je een betaling ontvangt of een andere actie zich voltooit, zet deze functie aan. Als je niet graag notificaties krijgt notificaties krijgt tenzij je de Bread app open hebt, zet pushnotificaties uit.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:55Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:29Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002793274,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvad er push-notifikationer?",body:"<p> Hvis du aktiverer push-notifikationer, har Bread mulighed for at underrette dig om tegnebogsaktivitet, selvom du ikke har Bread-appen åben. Hvis du gerne vil blive underrettet straks, hver gang du modtager en betaling eller en anden handling gennemføres, skal du slå denne funktion til. Hvis du ikke vil have beskeder overhovedet, medmindre du har åbnet  Bread-appen, skal du slå push-notifikationer fra.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:27Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002793294,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Was sind Push-Benachrichtigungen?",body:"<p>Wenn Sie Push-Benachrichtigungen aktivieren, kann Bread Sie bezüglich Geldbörsenaktivitäten benachrichtigen, auch wenn Ihre Bread-App nicht geöffnet ist. Schalten Sie dieses Feature ein, falls Sie jedes Mal sofort benachrichtigt werden möchten, wenn Sie eine Zahlung erhalten oder eine andere Aktion vollzogen wird. Falls Sie gar nicht benachrichtigt werden wollen, außer wenn Sie die Bread-App geöffnet haben, schalten Sie Push-Benachrichtigungen aus.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:28Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002804953,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Qué son las notificaciones push?",body:"<p>Si activas las notificaciones push, Bread tendrá la capacidad de notificarte sobre la actividad en el monedero incluso cuando no tengas la aplicación de Bread abierta. Activa esta función si deseas recibir una notificación inmediata cada vez que recibas un pago o se complete cualquier otra acción. Si no quieres que se te notifique a menos que tengas abierta la aplicación de Bread, desactiva las notificaciones push.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:54Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:28Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:251533508,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234758488/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234758488",source_id:234758488,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"What are push notifications?",body:"<p>If you enable push notifications, Bread will have the ability to notify you of wallet activity even when you don't have the Bread app open. If you would like to be notified immediately every time you receive a payment or some other action completes, turn on this feature. If you do not want to be notified at all unless you have the Bread app open, turn off push notifications.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:52:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:01:58Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:234756748,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/234756748-How-does-Bread-show-my-balance-in-my-local-currency-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234756748-How-does-Bread-show-my-balance-in-my-local-currency-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:4,vote_sum:0,vote_count:2,section_id:115001977727,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:29:21Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:17Z",name:"How does Bread show my balance in my local currency?",title:"How does Bread show my balance in my local currency?",body:"<p>Money kept in Bread is always stored as bitcoin. Bread uses an exchange rate to show you an estimate of how much your bitcoin is worth in your local currency. When you send a transaction and enter the amount to send in your local currency, Bread uses the exchange rate to calculate how much bitcoin to send.</p>\n<p>It's possible people using other wallets are using different exchange rates, so the balance sent/received might be slight different than what other person sees.</p>\n<p>Since the exchange rate is always changing, the amount of money in your wallet as quoted in your local currency may change over time. However, your bitcoin balance will not change unless you send or receive bitcoin.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:["slug:display-currency"],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002793554,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"Bread 如何以當地貨幣顯示我的餘額？",body:"<p>在 Bread 內的款項皆會以比特幣存放。Bread 使用匯率來估算你的比特幣在當地貨幣中的市值。當你發送交易及使用當地貨幣輸入發款金額時，Bread 使用匯率來計算該送出多少比特幣。</p>\n<p>使用其他錢包的人可能會有不同的匯率，因此發款／收款的金額與對方看到的可能會有些微差距。</p>\n<p>因為匯率一直在改變，以當地貨幣顯示的你錢包內之資金可能會不時變動。不過你的比特幣餘額不會改變，除非有進行比特幣發款或收款。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002793494,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Como mostra o Bread o meu saldo na minha moeda local?",body:"<p>O dinheiro guardado no Bread é sempre armazenado como bitcoin. O Bread usa uma taxa de câmbio para lhe mostrar uma estimativa do valor de bitcoin na sua moeda local. Quando envia uma transação e introduz o montante a enviar na sua moeda, o Bread aplica a taxa de câmbio para calcular a quantia de bitcoin a enviar.</p>\n<p>É possível que pessoas que usem outras carteiras estejam a usar taxas de câmbio diferentes, por isso o saldo enviado/recebido poderá ser ligeiramente diferente do que a outra pessoa vê.</p>\n<p>Uma vez que a taxa de câmbio está sempre a mudar, o montante na sua carteira cotado na sua moeda local pode mudar com o tempo. No entanto, o seu saldo de bitcoin não será alterado a não ser que envie ou receba bitcoin.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002793514,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Hur visar Bread mitt saldo i min lokala valuta?",body:"<p>Pengar som förvaras i Bread lagras alltid som bitcoin. Bread använder en växelkurs för att visa en uppskattning av hur mycket dina bitcoin är värda i din lokala valuta. När du genomför en transaktion och anger beloppet som ska skickas i din lokala valuta använder Bread växelkursen för att beräkna hur mycket bitcoin som ska skickas.</p>\n<p>Det är möjligt att personer som använder andra plånböcker använder en annan växelkurs, vilket innebär att sänt/mottaget saldo kan vara aningen annorlunda än vad den andra personen ser.</p>\n<p>Eftersom växelkursen alltid ändras kan pengarna i din plånbok som anges i din lokala valuta ändras över tid. Ditt bitcoinsaldo förändras dock inte om du inte skickar eller tar emot bitcoin.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002793534,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"Bread 如何以我的本国货币显示我的余额？",body:"<p>Bread 中的资金始终以比特币的形式保存。Bread 使用一个汇率向您显示您的比特币按您本国货币计算大概值多少钱。当您发起一笔汇款交易并且以您本国货币输入汇款金额时，Bread 使用汇率计算要付出的比特币数额。</p>\n<p>使用其他钱包的人有可能在使用不同汇率，因此付出/收入的余额可能与他人所见略有出入。</p>\n<p>由于汇率始终在变化，以您本国货币报价的钱包金额可能随时间不停变化。不过，除非您付出或收入比特币，否则您的比特币余额不会变化。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002805093,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Hoe laat Bread mijn saldo in mijn valuta zien?",body:"<p>Geld opgeslagen via Bread is altijd opgeslagen als bitcoin. Bread gebruikt een wisselkoers om jou een schatting te tonen van hoeveel je bitcoin waard is in jouw valuta. Wanneer je een transactie verstuurt en het bedrag invoert in jouw valuta, gebruikt Bread de wisselkoers om uit te rekenen hoeveel bitcoin er verstuurd moet worden.</p>\n<p>Het is mogelijk dat mensen die andere portemonnees gebruiken andere wisselkoersen hebben, zodat het bedrag dat verstuurd/ontvangen is een beetje afwijkt van wat de andere persoon kan zien.</p>\n<p>Sinds de wisselkoers altijd verandert, verandert het bedrag in je portemonnee dat weergeven wordt in jouw valuta mettertijd. Je bitcoin-saldo zal niet veranderen tenzij je het ontvangt of verstuurt.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002805113,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Как Bread показывает мой баланс в моей валюте?",body:"<p>Деньги в Bread всегда хранятся в биткоинах. Bread использует курс обмена, чтобы показать вам, сколько стоят ваши биткоины в вашей валюте. Когда вы отправляете транзакцию и вводите сумму в своей валюте, Bread использует курс обмена, чтобы вычислить, сколько именно нужно отправить в биткоинах.</p>\n<p>Возможно, что люди, использующие другие кошельки, используют другие курсы обмена, поэтому отправленная и полученная сумма может быть разной у отправителя и получателя.</p>\n<p>Так как курс постоянно меняется, то баланс кошелька в вашей валюте может меняться со временем, однако ваш баланс в биткоинах не изменится, пока вы не отправите или не получите биткоины.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:59Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:14Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002793474,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Comment Bread affiche-t-il mon solde dans ma devise locale ?",body:"<p>L'argent conservé dans Bread est toujours stocké sous forme de bitcoins. Bread utilise un taux de change pour afficher une estimation de la valeur de vos bitcoins dans votre devise locale. Lorsque vous envoyez une transaction et entrez le montant à envoyer dans votre devise locale, Bread utilise le taux de change pour calculer le montant à envoyer en bitcoins.</p>\n<p>Il est possible que les utilisateurs d'autres portefeuilles utilisent des taux de change différents ; le solde envoyé/reçu peut donc être légèrement différent de celui affiché à l'autre personne.</p>\n<p>Puisque le taux de change évolue en permanence, la somme d'argent contenue dans votre portefeuille telle que convertie dans votre devise locale peut évoluer avec le temps. Cependant, votre solde de bitcoins ne changera pas sauf si vous envoyez ou recevez des bitcoins.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:58Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002805053,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Come fa Bread a mostrare il mio saldo in valuta locale?",body:"<p>Tutto il denaro contenuto in Bread è sempre in bitcoin. Bread utilizza i tassi di cambio per mostrarti una stima del valore del tuoi bitcoin nella valuta locale. Quando invii una transazione ed inserisci l'importo da inviare in valuta locale, Bread usa il tasso di cambio per calcolare quanti bitcoin inviare.</p>\n<p>Può capitare che persone con portafogli diversi usino tassi di cambio diverso, per questo l'importo ricevuto/inviato potrebbe essere leggermente diverso da quello mostrato alla controparte.</p>\n<p>Poiché i tassi di cambio variano continuamente, il saldo del tuo portafoglio, quando mostrato in valuta locale, potrebbe cambiare nel tempo. Tuttavia, il saldo in bitcoin cambia solo se invii o ricevi bitcoin.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:58Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002805073,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"Breadはどのようにして私の所在地の通貨で残高を表示させるのでしょうか?",body:"<p>Bread内に保管されている資金は常にビットコインとして保管されます。Breadでは保管されたビットコインのお住いの地域の通貨での金額を為替レートに基づき換算して推定表示します。送金または送金する金額をお住いの地域の通貨で入力する際には、為替レートに基づいて送信されるビットコインの額が計算されます。</p>\n<p>他のウォレットを利用している人は異なる為替レートを使用している場合があるので、相手側に表示される送金額/受領額は多少異なります。</p>\n<p>為替レートは常に変動しているので、あなたのウォレット内に表示されている金額は時間が経過するにつれて変動する場合があります。それでもビットコインを送信/受領しない限りは、あなたのビットコイン残高が変動することはありません。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:58Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:13Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002793454,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Cómo muestra Bread mi saldo en la divisa local?",body:"<p>El dinero guardado en Bread siempre se almacena como bitcoines. Bread utiliza un tipo de cambio para mostrarte una estimación de cuánto valen tus bitcoines en la moneda local. Cuando envías una transacción e introduces la cantidad a enviar en tu moneda local, Bread utiliza el tipo de cambio para calcular la cantidad de bitcoines a enviar. </p>\n<p>Es posible que las personas que usan otros monederos utilicen diferentes tipos de cambio, por lo que el saldo enviado/recibido puede diferir ligeramente del que vea la otra persona.</p>\n<p>Puesto que el tipo de cambio siempre fluctúa, la cantidad de dinero en tu monedero, tal como se cotiza en tu divisa local, puede cambiar con el tiempo. Sin embargo, tu saldo de bitcoines no cambiará a menos que envíes o recibas bitcoines.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:58Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002805013,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvordan viser Bread min saldo i min lokale valuta?",body:"<p>Penge opbevaret i Bread gemmes altid som bitcoin. Bread bruger en valutakurs for at vise dig et skøn over, hvor meget dine bitcoin er værd i din lokale valuta. Når du sender en transaktion og indtaster det beløb der skal sendes i din lokale valuta, bruger Bread valutakursen til at beregne, hvor mange bitcoin der skal sendes. </p>\n<p> Det er muligt, at folk der bruger andre tegnebøger, bruger forskellige valutakurser, hvilket gør at den afsendte/modtagne balance kan være lidt forskellig end den, den anden person ser. </p>\n<p> Da valutakurser altid ændrer sig, kan mængden af penge i din tegnebog, som citeret i din lokale valuta, ændre sig over tid. Din bitcoin-balance ændres dog ikke, medmindre du sender eller modtager bitcoin. </p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:57Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002805033,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wie zeigt Bread meinen Kontostand in meiner lokalen Währung an?",body:"<p>In Bread aufbewahrtes Geld wird stets als Bitcoins gespeichert. Bread verwendet einen Wechselkurs, um Ihnen den geschätzten Wert Ihrer Bitcoins in Ihrer lokalen Währung anzuzeigen. Wenn Sie eine Transaktion tätigen und den zu sendenden Betrag in Ihrer lokalen Währung eingeben, nutzt Bread den Wechselkurs, um zu berechnen, wie viele Bitcoins versendet werden.</p>\n<p>Es ist möglich, dass Menschen, die andere Geldbörsen verwenden, über andere Wechselkurse verfügen, daher kann der gesendete/empfangene Betrag leicht davon abweichen, was die andere Person sieht.</p>\n<p>Da sich der Wechselkurs ständig ändert, wird sich der in Ihrer lokalen Währung angezeigte Betrag in Ihrer Geldbörse mit der Zeit verändern.\nIhr Bitcoin-Kontostand verändert sich allerdings nicht, es sei denn, Sie versenden oder empfangen Bitcoins.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T08:59:57Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:12Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:251531308,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234756748/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234756748",source_id:234756748,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"How does Bread show my balance in my local currency?",body:"<p>Money kept in Bread is always stored as bitcoin. Bread uses an exchange rate to show you an estimate of how much your bitcoin is worth in your local currency. When you send a transaction and enter the amount to send in your local currency, Bread uses the exchange rate to calculate how much bitcoin to send.</p>\n<p>It's possible people using other wallets are using different exchange rates, so the balance sent/received might be slight different than what other person sees.</p>\n<p>Since the exchange rate is always changing, the amount of money in your wallet as quoted in your local currency may change over time. However, your bitcoin balance will not change unless you send or receive bitcoin.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:29:21Z",updated_at:"2017-08-10T01:17:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}},{id:234978567,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/234978567-Why-is-the-amount-sent-different-than-the-amount-received-.json",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234978567-Why-is-the-amount-sent-different-than-the-amount-received-",author_id:5388346437,comments_disabled:!0,draft:!1,promoted:!1,position:5,vote_sum:0,vote_count:0,section_id:115001977707,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:33:25Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:19Z",name:"Why is the amount sent different than the amount received?",title:"Why is the amount sent different than the amount received?",body:"<p>Money in your Bread is always held as bitcoin, and the value in your local currency is displayed as an estimate only. The exchange rate used to make this estimate is always fluctuating, and depending on when a transaction is sent or received the estimated value of the transaction can change. It is common for the estimated value of a transaction to be seen differently by the sender and receiver, however the amount of bitcoin sent should not change.</p>",source_locale:"en-us",locale:"en-us",outdated:!1,outdated_locales:[],label_names:[],locales:{"zh-tw":{id:115002793694,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/zh-tw",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-tw/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-tw",title:"為何發送的款項與收到的款項不一樣？",body:"<p>在你 bread 錢包中的款項皆會以比特幣存放，所顯示的當地貨幣市值僅為估計。用來估算的匯率會一直波動，交易的估計市值也會跟隨發款或收款時間而變動。在發款方及收款方所顯現的交易估計市值不同是很正常的，不過所發送的比特幣數量應不會改變。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:03Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},pt:{id:115002793654,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/pt",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/pt/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"pt",title:"Porque é que o montante enviado é diferente do recebido?",body:"<p>O dinheiro no seu Bread é sempre guardado em bitcoin, e o valor na sua moeda local é exibido apenas como estimativa. A taxa de câmbio usada para fazer esta estimativa está constantemente a flutuar e, dependendo de quando é enviada ou recebida uma transação, o valor estimado da transação pode mudar. É comum que o valor estimado de uma transação seja diferente entre o remetente e o destinatário, no entanto o montante de bitcoin enviado é o mesmo.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:02Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:35Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ru:{id:115002805193,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/ru",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ru/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"ru",title:"Почему отправленная сумма отличается от полученной суммы?",body:"<p>Деньги в вашем кошельке всегда хранятся в биткоинах, а сумма в вашей валюте является лишь приблизительной. Курс валют, с помощью которого вычисляется эта сумма, всегда меняется, и в зависимости от того, отправляете ли вы транзакцию или получаете, сумма транзакции может меняться. Часто сумма транзакции у отправителя и получателя может различаться, но количество отправленных биткоинов будет одинаковым.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:02Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:16Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"zh-cn":{id:115002793674,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/zh-cn",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/zh-cn/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"zh-cn",title:"为什么付出金额与收入金额不同？",body:"<p>Bread 钱包中的资金始终以比特币的形式持有，以您本国货币显示的价值仅为估计值。用于估计的汇率始终在波动，并且视交易款项付出或收入时间，交易的估计值可能变化。付款方和收款方看到不同的交易估计值是常见现象，不过所付出的比特币数额是不会变化的。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:02Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},sv:{id:115002805213,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/sv",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/sv/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"sv",title:"Varför skiljer sig det skickade beloppet från det mottagna beloppet?",body:"<p>Pengar i din breadplånbok lagras alltid som bitcoin, och värdet i din lokala valuta visas bara som en uppskattning. Växelkursen som används för att göra denna uppskattning varierar alltid och beroende på när en transaktion skickas eller mottas kan det uppskattade värdet för transaktionen ändras. Det är vanligt att det uppskattade värdet av en transaktion ses annorlunda av avsändaren och mottagaren, men mängden bitcoin som skickas ska inte ändras.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:02Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:17Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},it:{id:115002793594,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/it",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/it/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"it",title:"Perché l'importo inviato è diverso dall'importo ricevuto?",body:"<p>Il denaro contenuto nel tuo Bread è sempre in bitcoin e il valore in valuta locale è solo una stima. Il tasso di cambio utilizzato per effettuare tale stima varia continuamente, e il valore stimato di una transazione dipende da quando viene inviata o ricevuta. Capita spesso che il mittente e il destinatario di una transazione vedano stime diverse, ma l'importo in bitcoin non cambia.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:01Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:34Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},ja:{id:115002793614,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/ja",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/ja/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"ja",title:"送金された金額と受領された金額に差があるのはなぜでしょう?",body:"<p>あなたのBread内の資金は常にビットコインとして保管されてとり、お住いの地域の通貨で表示される金額は推定額に過ぎません。この推定に使用される為替レートは常に変動しており、いつ送金/受領が行われたかに応じて取引の推定金額は変動します。送金者側と受領者側に異なった推定取引金額が表示されるのはよく起こりえることですが、ビットコインの額自体は変動しません。</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:01Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:19:18Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},nl:{id:115002793634,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/nl",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/nl/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"nl",title:"Waarom is het verstuurde bedrag anders dan het ontvangen bedrag?",body:"<p>Geld in je breadportemonnee is altijd in bitcoin, en de waarde in jouw valuta is weergegeven als een schatting. De wisselkoers die voor deze schatting gebruikt wordt, verandert constant en afhankelijk van wanneer een transactie verstuurd of ontvangen is, verandert de waarde van de transactie. Het is gebruikelijk dat de geschatte waarde van een transactie anders is voor de ontvanger en de verzender, hoewel de hoeveelheid bitcoin die verzonden wordt, niet mag veranderen.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:01Z",updated_at:"2017-09-06T09:09:16Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},fr:{id:115002805173,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/fr",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/fr/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"fr",title:"Pourquoi le montant envoyé est-il différent du montant reçu ?",body:"<p>L'argent contenu dans votre Bread est toujours stocké en bitcoin, et la valeur dans votre devise locale s'affiche uniquement à titre d'estimation. Le taux de change utilisé pour faire cette estimation évolue en permanence, et la valeur estimée de la transaction pourra changer en fonction du moment de l'envoi ou de la réception. Il est courant que la valeur estimée d'une transaction s'affiche différemment pour l'expéditeur et le destinataire, mais le montant envoyé en bitcoin ne devrait pas changer.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:01Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:34Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},da:{id:115002793574,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/da",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/da/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"da",title:"Hvorfor er det sendte beløb forskelligt fra det modtagne beløb?",body:"<p>Penge i din Bread opbevares altid som bitcoin, og værdien i din lokale valuta vises kun som et skøn. Valutakursen der bruges til at foretage dette estimat, varierer altid, og afhængigt af hvornår en transaktion sendes eller modtages, kan den estimerede værdi af transaktionen ændres. Det er almindeligt at den estimerede værdi af en transaktion ses forskelligt for afsenderen og modtageren, men mængden af bitcoin der bliver sendt ændres ikke.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},de:{id:115002805133,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/de",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/de/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"de",title:"Wieso unterscheiden sich der versendete und der empfangene Betrag?",body:"<p>Das Geld in Ihrer Bread wird stets in Bitcoins gespeichert und der Wert in Ihrer lokalen Währung wird nur als Schätzwert angezeigt. Der Wechselkurs, der für diesen Schätzwert verwendet wird, fluktuiert ständig und je nachdem, wann eine Transaktion versendet oder empfangen wird, kann der geschätzte Wert der Transaktion variieren. Es kommt häufig vor, dass der geschätzte Wert einer Transaktion von Sender und Empfänger unterschiedlich gesehen wird, die Menge der gesendeten Bitcoins sollte sich hingegen nicht verändern.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:33Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},es:{id:115002805153,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/es",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/es/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"es",title:"¿Por qué la cantidad enviada es diferente a la cantidad recibida?",body:"<p>El dinero en tu Bread siempre se mantiene como bitcoines, y el valor en tu divisa local se muestra solamente como una estimación. El tipo de cambio utilizado para realizar esta estimación es siempre fluctuante y, en función de cuándo se envía o recibe una transacción, el valor estimado de la misma puede cambiar. Es común que el valor estimado de una transacción se vea de manera diferente por el remitente y el receptor, sin embargo, la cantidad de bitcoines enviada no debería cambiar.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2017-09-06T09:00:00Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:04:34Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437},"en-us":{id:251723147,url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/articles/234978567/translations/en-us",html_url:"https://bwsupport.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/234978567",source_id:234978567,source_type:"Article",locale:"en-us",title:"Why is the amount sent different than the amount received?",body:"<p>Money in your Bread is always held as bitcoin, and the value in your local currency is displayed as an estimate only. The exchange rate used to make this estimate is always fluctuating, and depending on when a transaction is sent or received the estimated value of the transaction can change. It is common for the estimated value of a transaction to be seen differently by the sender and receiver, however the amount of bitcoin sent should not change.</p>",outdated:!1,draft:!1,hidden:!1,created_at:"2016-11-14T22:33:25Z",updated_at:"2017-09-13T19:01:59Z",updated_by_id:5388346437,created_by_id:5388346437}}}]}});